    <Folder>
      <name>Dedicated Home Weekly</name>
      <Placemark>
        <name>🔥🔥 DT Joliet, IL
$2500 Sign On Bonus! </name>
        <description><![CDATA[🔴 Summer Retention Bonus | 5/18/26 – 8/15/26<br>Earn an extra $337.50/week for being available all week and pulling Dollar Tree loads.<br>• Payouts: 7/3/26 & 8/21/26<br>• Must be trained, onboarded, and actively pulling Dollar Tree loads by 7/27/26<br>• Must be employed at time of payout<br>• Shop time disqualifies weekly bonus payout eligibility                                                                                                                                                                  🔴 Key Requirements<br>• Local based driver must park trucks at either Markham Terminal or Dollar Tree Joliet DC, no parking at their homes.<br>• Drivers must bring two weeks’ worth of supplies to orientation<br>• Patience & strong customer service skills are essential for this role<br>• This is a physically demanding job requiring attention to safety due to stacked freight. Training will include safe unloading practices.<br>• Drivers must be flexible, as shifts and workdays vary based on delivery schedules.<br><br><br>🔴 Other Carriers on This Account<br>• Werner<br>• CR England<br><br>🔴 Job Details<br>• $2500 Sign On Bonus<br>• Training: 2 day ride along following DT driver. Paid at $150/day<br>• Home Time: Weekly for a 34-hour reset. Weekends are not guaranteed<br>• Freight: 100% touch freight unload<br>• Mileage: 800 – 1,000 average weekly<br>• Running Area: delivering to Dollar Tree stores in IL, WI, IN, MI, IA, and KY<br>• Tractors: Internationals and Freightliners<br>• Schedule: Drivers must be available Sunday through Saturday. Workdays vary depending on deliveries near the driver's home for their 34-hour reset.<br><br>🔴 Pay<br>• Average Weekly | annually: $1,500 - $1,700 | $75k-$100k annually<br>• Additional Pay: $245 for each unloaded trailer. $70 per backhaul. $25 per stop<br>• Top Performers: $2000+ weekly All in Pay - $1.80 (CPM + accessorial pay + stop pay)<br><br><br>CPM Structure: Experienced Based Pay<br>• 0-11 months: $0.82/mile<br>• 12-23 months: $0.83/mile<br>• 24-35 months: $0.84/mile<br>• 36+ months: $0.85/mile<br><br>🔴 Sign On Bonus Payout<br>$2500 Total Payout<br>1st Load $ 250<br>30 days $ 250<br>60 days $ 250<br>90 days $ 500<br>120 days $ 250<br>150 days $ 250<br>180 days $ 750<br><br>🔴 Bonus Eligibility<br>• U.S. Xpress reserves the right to modify or cancel the Sign-on bonus at any time with appropriate notice under applicable law.<br>• Nothing in this Sign-on Bonus changes the at-will nature of your employment, meaning you and U.S. Xpress may terminate the employment relationship at any time, with or without cause.<br>• You must be an active company driver on the day the bonus is paid.<br><br>🔴 Benefits<br>• Support staff on site to assist<br>• Paid Vacation:<br>o 1 week of vacation after 1 year.<br>o 2 weeks after 2 years.<br>o 3 weeks after 7 years.<br>o 4 weeks after 10 years<br><br>🔴Unload Account Videos:<br>https://vimeo.com/507100528/da4b42c25c     <br>https://vimeo.com/669499314<br><br>🔴Tagging Orientation site - Chicago<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: DT Joliet, IL<br>SIGN-ON BONUS: Y/N <br>Company: US Xpress 01<br>Updated 5.13.26]]></description>
