      <Placemark>
        <name>🔥🔥FD Front Royal VA
$2500 Sign On Bonus!! </name>
        <description><![CDATA[🔴 Key Requirements<br>• Patience & strong customer service skills are essential for this role<br>• Drivers must bring two weeks’ worth of supplies to orientation.<br>• Physical ability for live unloads.<br>• A double endorsement is preferred, but not required<br><br>🔴 Other Carriers on This Account<br>USA Truck (DB Schenker)<br><br>🔴 Job Details<br>• $2500 Sign on Bonus<br>• Training: 1 week ride along in truck with another FD driver paid at $150/day<br>• Home Time: Weekly for a 34-hour reset<br>• Freight: 100% touch freight, live unload at FD stores.<br>• Running Area: VA, NC, DC, PA, NH, OH, WV all within 700 miles of the Front Royal, VA DC<br>• Mileage: average 1100 miles per week, 1-6 stops per trailer<br>• Schedule: Runs include nights, weekends, and holidays as they fall within the driver’s schedule. A minimum of 3 loads is required per week.<br><br>🔴 Pay<br>• Average weekly: $1,300+ <br>• Top Performers: Top performers make $2,000 per week • Average $89k Annually<br>• Additional Pay: $250 full trailer unload. $125 per week for completing 3+ loads. $35 backhaul. All in Pay - $1.30 (CPM + accessorial pay)<br><br>CPM Structure: Experience Based<br>0 months: $0.60/mile<br>12 months: $0.61/mile<br>24 months: $0.63/mile<br>36 months: $0.65/mile<br>48 months: $0.70/mile<br>60 months: $0.71/mile<br>84 months: $0.72/mile<br>120+ months: $0.73/mile<br><br>🔴 Sign On Bonus Payout<br>$2500 Total Payout<br>1st Load $ 250<br>30 days $ 250<br>60 days $ 250<br>90 days $ 500<br>120 days $ 250<br>150 days $ 250<br>180 days $ 750<br><br>🔴 Bonus Eligibility<br>• U.S. Xpress reserves the right to modify or cancel the Sign-on bonus at any time with appropriate notice under applicable law.<br>• Nothing in this Sign-on Bonus changes the at-will nature of your employment, meaning you and U.S. Xpress may terminate the employment relationship at any time, with or without cause.<br>• You must be an active company driver on the day the bonus is paid.<br><br>🔴 Benefits<br>• Support staff on site 24/7 to assist<br>• Paid Vacation:<br>o 1 week of vacation after 1 year.<br>o 2 weeks after 2 years.<br>o 3 weeks after 7 years.<br>o 4 weeks after 10 years<br><br>🔴Unload Account Videos:<br>https://vimeo.com/507100528/da4b42c25c     <br>https://vimeo.com/669499314<br><br>🔴Tagging Orientation site - Shippensburg, Duncan<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>Dedicated Domicile- Family Dollar Front Royal<br>SIGN ON BONUS: Y/N<br>Company: US Xpress 01<br>Updated 5.13.26]]></description>
