$2000 Sign on Bonus!!</name>
        <description><![CDATA[🔴 Summer Retention Bonus | 5/18/26 – 8/15/26<br>Earn an extra $337.50/week for being available all week and pulling Dollar Tree loads.<br>• Payouts: 7/3/26 & 8/21/26<br>• Must be trained, onboarded, and actively pulling Dollar Tree loads by 7/27/26<br>• Must be employed at time of payout<br>• Shop time disqualifies weekly bonus payout eligibility                                                                                                                                                                  🔴 Key Requirements<br>• Patience & strong customer service skills are essential for this role<br>• Drivers must bring two weeks’ worth of supplies to orientation. Immediate dispatch to Warrensburg, MO upon hire.<br>• Secure parking is required for your truck & trailer.<br><br>🔴 Other Carriers on This Account<br>• Hogan<br>• CR England<br><br>🔴 Job Details<br>• $2000 Sign on Bonus<br>• Training: 1 week of ride-along training following DT driver at $150/day<br>• Home Time: Weekly for a 34-hour reset, 80% of that time is on weekends<br>• Freight: 100% touch freight.<br>• Running Areas: Delivery to Dollar Trees and occasionally Family Dollars in ND, SD, NE, KS, OK, AR, MO, IA, MN, WI, IL, KY, TN, IN<br>• Mileage: 1,550 average weekly<br>• Tractors: Internationals, Freightliners, Kenworths<br>• Schedule: Early morning start, multiple store deliveries per day<br><br>🔴 Pay<br>• Average weekly: $1,900<br>• Top Performers: Earn up to $2200 per week with 1,850 miles •$98k-$114k Annually<br>• Additional Pay: $240 unload pay, $25 stop pay, $50 backhaul pay All in Pay - $1.20 (CPM + accessorial pay + stop pay)<br><br>CPM Structure:<br>0–6 months: $0.70<br>6–12 months: $0.71<br>12–18 months: $0.72<br>8–24 months: $0.73<br>24–36 months: $0.74<br>36–48 months: $0.75<br>48–60 months: $0.76<br>60–72 months: $0.77<br>72–84 months: $0.78<br>84–96 months: $0.79<br>96+ months: $0.80<br><br>🔴 Sign On Bonus Payout<br>$2,000 Total<br>$500 after 1st load<br>$500 after 30 days<br>$1000 after 60 days<br><br>🔴 Bonus Eligibility<br>• U.S. Xpress reserves the right to modify or cancel the Sign-on bonus at any time with appropriate notice under applicable law.<br>• Nothing in this Sign-on Bonus changes the at-will nature of your employment, meaning you and U.S. Xpress may terminate the employment relationship at any time, with or without cause.<br>• You must be an active company driver on the day the bonus is paid.<br><br>🔴 Benefits<br>• Support staff on site 24/7 to assist<br>• Paid Vacation:<br>o 1 week of vacation after 1 year.<br>o 2 weeks after 2 years.<br>o 3 weeks after 7 years.<br>o 4 weeks after 10 years<br><br>🔴Unload Videos<br>https://vimeo.com/507100528/da4b42c25c     <br>https://vimeo.com/669499314    <br><br>🔴Tagging<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Domicile Terminal- DT Warrensburg<br>Region: All<br>Orientation Site: Closest Terminal<br>Company: US Xpress 01                                             Updated 5.13.26]]></description>
