$2500 Sign On Bonus!!</name>
        <description><![CDATA[🔴 Summer Retention Bonus | 5/18/26 – 8/15/26<br>Earn an extra $337.50/week for being available all week and pulling Dollar Tree loads.<br>• Payouts: 7/3/26 & 8/21/26<br>• Must be trained, onboarded, and actively pulling Dollar Tree loads by 7/27/26<br>• Must be employed at time of payout<br>• Shop time disqualifies weekly bonus payout eligibility                                                                                                                                                                  🔴 Key Requirements<br>• Patience & strong customer service skills are essential for this role<br>• Drivers must bring two weeks’ worth of supplies to orientation. Immediate dispatch to Windsor, CT upon hire for training.<br>• Secure parking is required for your truck & trailer. Drivers authorized to park at any DT store location or DC.<br>• Night, weekends, and holiday driving required.<br><br>🔴 Other Carriers on This Account<br>Werner<br><br>🔴 Job Details<br>• $2,500 Sign On Bonus<br>• Training: 1 – 3 of ride-along training following DT driver at $150/day<br>• Home Time: Weekly for a 34-hour reset, not guaranteed weekend hometime<br>• Freight: 100% touch freight, live unload at Dollar Tree stores, box by box with rollers, with occasional Family Dollar store deliveries.<br>• Running Area: Deliveries to CT, MA, NH, VT, NY, RI, ME within 1066 miles of Windsor, CT.<br>• Mileage: 900 weekly average with 3 loads<br>• Schedule: Night, weekends, and holiday driving required.<br><br>🔴 Pay<br>• Average weekly | annually: $1,600 - $1,850 weekly | $104,000 annually<br>• Additional Pay: $240 per fully unloaded trailer. $75 per backhaul. $250 for NYC borough deliveries (26 ft pup trailers)<br>• Top Performers: $2500 + per week All in Pay - $1.90 (CPM + accessorial pay)<br><br>CPM Structure: Experienced Based<br>0-11 months $0.73<br>1 - 2 years $0.74<br>2 - 3 years $0.75<br>3+ years $0.76<br><br>🔴 Sign On Bonus Payout<br>$2500 Total Payout<br>1st Load $ 250<br>30 days $ 250<br>60 days $ 250<br>90 days $ 500<br>120 days $ 250<br>150 days $ 250<br>180 days $ 750<br><br>🔴 Bonus Eligibility<br>• U.S. Xpress reserves the right to modify or cancel the Sign-on bonus at any time with appropriate notice under applicable law.<br>• Nothing in this Sign-on Bonus changes the at-will nature of your employment, meaning you and U.S. Xpress may terminate the employment relationship at any time, with or without cause.<br>• You must be an active company driver on the day the bonus is paid.<br><br>🔴 Benefits<br>• Support staff on site 24/7 to assist<br>• Paid Vacation:<br>1 week after 1 year of service<br>2 weeks after 2 years<br>3 weeks after 7 years<br>4 weeks after 10 years<br><br>🔴Account Videos:<br>https://vimeo.com/507100528/da4b42c25c<br>  https://vimeo.com/669499314 <br>🔴Tagging Orientation site - Shippensburg<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: DT Windsor<br>SIGN ON BONUS: Y/N<br>Company: US Xpress 01                                  Updated 5.13.26      ]]></description>
