er on the day the bonus is paid.<br><br>🔴 Benefits<br>• Support staff on site 24/7 to assist<br>• Paid Vacation:<br>o 1 week after 1 year of service<br>o 2 weeks after 2 years<br>o 3 weeks after 7 years<br>o 4 weeks after 10 years<br><br>🔴Unload Videos<br>https://vimeo.com/507100528/da4b42c25c     <br>https://vimeo.com/669499314<br><br>🔴Tagging Orientation Site - Jacksonville<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: DT Savannah<br>SIGN ON BONUS: Y/N<br>Company: US Xpress 01<br>Updated 5.13.26]]></description>
