        <description><![CDATA[🔴 Key Requirements<br>• Patience & strong customer service skills are essential for this role<br>• Drivers must bring two weeks’ worth of supplies to orientation.<br>• Physical ability for live unloads<br>• Account requires secure parking for truck and trailer while on home-time. Secure parking is on your own personal property or somewhere gated with two forms of security (guard or camera). No parking for home-time at FD stores, Walmart or other unsecure locations<br><br>🔴 Other Carriers On This Account<br>Werner<br><br>🔴 Job Details<br>• $2000 Sign on Bonus<br>• Training: ride along training after orientation paid at $150/day with driver in their tractor<br>• Home Time: Weekly for a 34-hour reset<br>• Freight: 100% touch freight, live unload at FD stores with rollers.<br>• Running area: FL, GA, AL, MS, LA<br>• Mileage: average 1600 miles and 3 loads per week<br>• Tractors: Internationals, Freightliners, Kenworths<br>• Schedule: Early AM deliveries; may include nights, weekends, and holidays. Between 1 – 6 stops per day.<br><br>🔴 Pay<br>• Average weekly | annually: $1,400 weekly+ <br>• Top Performers: average $1,800 per week • Earn $65k Annually with Top Earners averaging $93k+ Annually<br>• Additional Pay: $230 full trailer unload. $50 backhaul All in Pay - $.90 (CPM + accessorial pay) <br>CPM Structure: Experience Based Pay<br>0 months: $0.46/mile<br>12 months: $0.47/mile<br>24 months: $0.48/mile<br>36 months: $0.49/mile<br>48 months: $0.50/mile<br>60 months: $0.51/mile<br>72 months: $0.52/mile<br>84 months: $0.53/mile<br>96 months: $0.54/mile<br>108 months: $0.55/mile<br>120 months: $0.56/mile<br><br>🔴 Sign On Bonus Payout<br>$2,000 Total<br>$500 after 1st load<br>$500 after 30 days<br>$1000 after 60 days<br><br>🔴 Bonus Eligibility<br>• U.S. Xpress reserves the right to modify or cancel the Sign-on bonus at any time with appropriate notice under applicable law.<br>• Nothing in this Sign-on Bonus changes the at-will nature of your employment, meaning you and U.S. Xpress may terminate the employment relationship at any time, with or without cause.<br>• You must be an active company driver on the day the bonus is paid.<br><br>🔴 Benefits<br>• Support staff on site 24/7 to assist<br>• Paid Vacation:<br>1 week after 1 year of service<br>2 weeks after 2 years<br>3 weeks after 7 years<br>4 weeks after 10 years<br><br>🔴Unload Account Videos<br>https://vimeo.com/507100528/da4b42c25c       <br>https://vimeo.com/669499314<br><br>🔴 Tagging<br>Orientation Site - Jacksonville<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: FD Marianna<br>SIGN ON BONUS: Y/N<br>Company: US Xpress 01<br>Updated 5.13.26]]></description>
