      <Placemark>
        <name>🔥🔥Walmart Gordonsville VA Regional
$2500 Sign On Bonus!!</name>
        <description><![CDATA[DC Address 10417 James Madison Hwy, Gordonsville, VA 22942<br><br>🔴 Key Requirements<br>• Must prioritize safety, have exceptional customer service skills, and handle customer concerns with patience.<br>• Afternoons, Nights, Weekends, and Holidays required.<br><br>🔴 Restrictions<br>• No weekend-off schedules currently available for full-time drivers.<br><br>🔴 Job Details<br>• $2500 Sign on Bonus<br>• Training: 1 day of onsite training paid at $125. 3-4 day ride along paid at $50 per day.<br>• Home Time: home weekly. Consistent 48-hour resets on the same two days every week<br>• Freight: mixture or dry & refrigerated no touch, live unload grocery freight<br>• Running Area: Walmart locations in VA, NC, MD, DE, and WV<br>• Mileage: 1,600 – 1,700 miles per week. This will usually require 2 routes per working day (11-14 hour shift)<br>• Tractors: Assigned sleeper truck<br>• Schedule: Work 5 days on, 2 days off, with more shifts becoming available upon increased tenure at account. Afternoons, Nights, Weekends, and Holidays required.<br><br>🔴 Pay<br>• Average weekly: $1,300<br>• Top Performers: $1,500+ per week<br>• Additional Pay: $20 per stop<br><br>CPM Structure: Routes will pay Whichever is greater – Mileage pay or Minimum Mileage Band Pay<br><br>Experienced Based Pay<br>0-6 Months: $0.56/mile<br>6 Months-1 Year: $0.57/mile<br>1-2 Years: $0.58/mile<br>2-3 Years: $0.59/mile<br>3-5 Years: $0.60/mile<br>5-7 Years: $0.61/mile<br>7-10 Years: $0.62/mile<br>10+ Years: $0.63/mile<br><br>Mileage Band Pay<br>0-50 miles: $40<br>51-75 miles: $45<br>76-100 miles: $60<br>101-125 miles: $70<br>126-150 miles: $75<br>151-175 miles: $80<br>176-200 miles: $85<br>201-225 miles: $90<br><br>🔴 Sign On Bonus Payout<br>$2500 Total Payout<br>1st Load $ 250<br>30 days $ 250<br>60 days $ 250<br>90 days $ 500<br>120 days $ 250<br>150 days $ 250<br>180 days $ 750<br><br>🔴 Bonus Eligibility<br>• U.S. Xpress reserves the right to modify or cancel the Sign-on bonus at any time with appropriate notice under applicable law.<br>• Nothing in this Sign-on Bonus changes the at-will nature of your employment, meaning you and U.S. Xpress may terminate the employment relationship at any time, with or without cause.<br>• You must be an active company driver on the day the bonus is paid.<br><br>🔴 Benefits<br>• Support staff on site 24/7 to assist<br>• Paid Vacation:<br>o 1 week after 1 year of service.<br>o 2 weeks after 2 years.<br>o 3 weeks after 7 years.<br>o 4 weeks after 10 years.<br><br> 🔴Tagging<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED Dom Term: Wal-Mart Gordonsville<br>SIGN ON BONUS Y/N<br>Orientation Site: Closest Terminal<br>Updated 10.14.25]]></description>
