out cause.<br>• You must be an active company driver on the day the bonus is paid.<br><br>🔴 Benefits<br>• Support staff on site to assist<br>• Paid Vacation:<br>o 1 week of vacation after 1 year.<br>o 2 weeks after 2 years.<br>o 3 weeks after 7 years.<br>o 4 weeks after 10 years<br><br>🔴Unload Account Videos:<br>https://vimeo.com/507100528/da4b42c25c     <br>https://vimeo.com/669499314<br><br>🔴Tagging<br>Orientation site - Chicago<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: DT Joliet, IL<br>SIGN-ON BONUS: Y/N<br>Company: US Xpress 01<br>Updated 3.26.26]]></description>
