      <Placemark>
        <name>Kroger Shelbyville IN - $2500 Sign On Bonus! Local account home daily (ZIP 46176) Must have personal transportation to and from DC Daily. Must live in shaded area</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Job Details:<br>• Driver will work weekends and nights.<br>• Freight will need to be unloaded from trailer into back room of stores using a power jack.<br>• Kroger is a 24/7 operation and drivers will operate on various schedules and start days.<br>• Assigned start times Open shifts - 10pm-midnight or 2am-5am<br>• Required to work a 6th day during the week before a holiday.<br>• Runs will include nights, weekends, and holidays that fall within your workweek. The week before a holiday is also mandatory.<br>• Average 1400-1600 miles per week ________________________________________<br>Key Requirements:<br>• Must be willing to unload freight using a motorized pallet jack.<br>• Must be flexible with work schedule and available to work weekends and holidays.<br>• Slip seat operation requires drivers to commute with their personal vehicle to the distribution center. • Runs IL, OH, IN<br>________________________________________<br>Benefits:<br>• Home daily with 2 consecutive days off per week.<br>• Assigned start times.<br>• Family-oriented atmosphere with an experienced staff.<br>• 24/7 on-site staff, including an on-site mechanic (Monday, Wednesday, Friday & Saturday).<br>• Paid Vacation:<br>o 1 week of vacation after 1 year.<br>o 2 weeks after 3 years.<br>o 3 weeks after 7 years.<br>o 4 weeks after 15 years<br>• Paid training: 1-2 days of ride-along training at $100 per day.<br>________________________________________<br>Pay Structure:<br>• Average weekly pay: $1,600<br>• Annual earnings: Up to $83,000 ________________________________________<br>Experience-Based Pay:<br>• 0 Months: $0.56 per mile<br>• 12-36 Months: $0.58 per mile<br>• 37-60 Months: $0.60 per mile<br>• 61+ Months: $0.62 per mile<br><br>• Stop pay: $20<br>• Unload pay: $55 per trailer<br>• Breakdown pay: $15/hour<br>• Detention pay (after 2 hours): $15/hour <br>🔴 Sign On Bonus Payout<br>$2500 Total Payout<br>1st Load $ 500<br>30 days $ 500<br>60 days $ 250<br>90 days $ 250<br>120 days $ 250<br>150 days $ 250<br>180 days $ 500 <br>• Tagging<br>Job: DEDICATED OTR DRIVER DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Local<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Kroger Shelbyville, IN<br>SIGN ON BONUS: Y/N<br>Company: US Xpress 01<br>Updated 3.17.26]]></description>
