        <description><![CDATA[🔴 Key Requirements<br>• Must have personal transportation to & from the DC daily<br>• Must be available for nights, weekends, and holidays<br>• Must prioritize safety & have exceptional customer services skills<br>• Must ensure customers acknowledge your arrival at the store.<br><br>🔴 Job Details<br>• Training: 1 day of in-classroom training in which you’ll receive $50 and 2-3 days of ride-along training at $100 per day.<br>• Home Time: Home daily! On very rare occasions, you may stay out overnight in a hotel.<br>• Freight: 100% No-Touch Refrigerated Freight delivering to Walmart & Sam’s Club stores.<br>• Running Area: SC, NC, TN, and VA (within 300 miles of Walmart Henderson DC).<br>• Mileage: 1,250 average miles per week. 1-3 routes per day with 1-3 stops per trip (occasional 10-hour break on the road).<br>• Tractors: International, Freightliner, and Kenworth day cabs (slip seating).<br>• Schedule: Heavy freight days: Expect higher volumes on Wednesday, Thursday, Friday, and Saturday. Current schedule is a rotating schedule of 6 days worked/34-hour restart, then 5 days worked/2 days off. There are plenty of opportunities to make money! Night shifts with a start time between 8 PM - 11 PM including every weekend. (Most loads deliver at night for easier stocking & less traffic).<br><br>🔴 Pay<br>• Average weekly: $1,200 (must work full schedule)<br>• Annual Potential: Up to $70,000 <br>CPM Structure: Routes will pay Whichever is greater – Mileage pay or Minimum Mileage Band Pay<br><br>Mileage Band Pay<br>0-50 miles: $41<br>51-75 miles: $48<br>76-100 miles: $64<br>101-125 miles: $74<br>126-150 miles: $82<br>151-175 miles: $84<br>176-200 miles: $93<br>201-225 miles: $96<br>226+ miles: Paid per mile (see below)<br><br>Experienced Based Pay<br>0-11 Months $0.45<br>12 - 35 Months $0.47<br>36 - 59 Months $0.50<br>60 - 83 Months $0.51<br>84 - 119 Months $0.52<br>10+ Years $0.54<br>• Additional Pay: $20 stop pay<br><br>🔴 Sign On Bonus Payout<br>$2500 Total Payout<br>1st Load $ 250<br>30 days $ 250<br>60 days $ 250<br>90 days $ 500<br>120 days $ 250<br>150 days $ 250<br>180 days $ 750 🔴 Benefits<br>• Support staff on site 24/7 to assist<br>• Paid Vacation:<br>o 1 week of vacation after 1 year.<br>o 2 weeks after 3 years.<br>o 3 weeks after 7 years.<br>o 4 weeks after 15 years<br><br>🔴Tagging<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Local<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All Orientation Site: Duncan <br>DED Dom Term: Wal-Mart Henderson<br>SIGN ON BONUS Y/N<br>Company: US Xpress 01<br>Updated 5.12.26]]></description>
