ss may terminate the employment relationship at any time, with or without cause.<br>• You must be an active company driver on the day the bonus is paid.<br><br>🔴 Benefits<br>• Support staff on site 24/7 to assist<br>• Paid Vacation:<br>o 1 week after 1 year of service<br>o 2 weeks after 2 years<br>o 3 weeks after 7 years<br>o 4 weeks after 10 years<br><br>🔴 Tagging<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Local<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED Dom Term: Wal-Mart Gordonsville<br>SIGN ON BONUS Y/N<br>Orientation Site: Closest Terminal Updated 4.9.25 ]]></description>
