ature of your employment, meaning you and U.S. Xpress may terminate the employment relationship at any time, with or without cause.<br>• You must be an active company driver on the day the bonus is paid.<br><br>🔴 Benefits<br>• 25/7 dispatch support<br>• Paid Vacation:<br>o 1 week of vacation after 1 year.<br>o 2 weeks after 3 years.<br>o 3 weeks after 7 years.<br>o 4 weeks after 15 years<br><br>🔴 Tagging<br>Orientation Site – THL/Ellenwood<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Staples Terre Haute<br>SIGN ON BONUS: Y/N<br>Company: US Xpress 01]]></description>
