g in this Sign On or Performance Bonus changes the at-will nature of your employment, meaning you and U.S. Xpress may terminate the employment relationship at any time, with or without cause.<br>• You must be an active company driver on the day the bonus is paid.<br><br>🔴 Trainer Opportunity<br>• To maximize your earnings, consider joining our trainer program<br>• Earn an additional $250 per week while a student is on your truck<br>• Receive up to $1,000 in bonuses once your student upgrades<br>• That’s an opportunity to earn up to $20,000 more per year if you have 1 year OTR experience and have been employed with us for 30 days as a safe driver.<br><br>🔴 Benefits<br>• Get 24/7 access operations support, no matter the time or day.<br>• Paid Vacation:<br>o 1 week after 1 year of service<br>o 2 weeks after 3 years<br>o 3 weeks after 7 years<br>o 4 weeks after 15 years<br><br>🔴Tagging<br>Orientation Site: Dallas<br>Job: First Seat Driver<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: OTR<br>Acct: OTR<br>Region: All<br>Dedicated Domicile: Dallas<br>South Florida: Y/N<br>Company: US Xpress 01                                    Updated 3.17.26]]></description>
