      <Placemark>
        <name>OTR COMPANY DRIVERS ONLY. JACKSONVILLE BASED $2000 Sign on Bonus!!!</name>
        <description><![CDATA[🔴 Job Details<br>• Home Time: 12 days out, 2 days home. This balance gives you the opportunity to stay productive on the road while still having regular time to recharge at home. We know how important that reset is, and we make sure you get it.<br>• Freight: 100% no-touch freight, with 50-60% drop & hook and 40-50% live unload. No Forced NYC Dispatch: You won’t be required to go into NYC or its five boroughs.<br>• Mileage: On average, drivers typically run around 2,000 miles per week, though this can vary depending on Hours of Service (HOS) and overall availability. Our top performers—about 30% of our fleet—consistently run between 2,300-3,000+ miles per week. Average LOH is 400 miles<br>• Running Area: Covering all 48 states, with most freight running east of I-35—but we go where the freight takes us. We have a suggestive dispatch. Loads are recommended with your area’s freight and your best financial and safety interests in mind<br>• Tractors: Drive in 2021 or newer Freightliner Cascadias or Kenworths.<br><br>🔴 Pay<br>• Top 20% of our OTR Drivers at the JAX Terminal earn $1525 Weekly<br>• Additional Pay: $12.50 per hour detention pay after the second hour unless a higher amount is required by state or local law. $100 layover/breakdown pay per day unless a higher amount is required by state or local law.<br>• Performance Bonus: Earn up to an additional 3 CPM based on safety, mileage, and productivity, starting the first of the month following your hire date. Must be an active OTR driver at the time of bonus payout to qualify.                                                   <br>🔴 Sign On Bonus Payout<br>1st load $500.00<br>Month 1 $500.00<br>Month 2 $500.00<br>Month 3 $500.00<br>Total $2,000.00                                                                                                                         <br>🔴 Bonus Eligibility<br>• U.S. Xpress reserves the right to modify or cancel the Performance Bonus any time with appropriate notice under applicable law.<br>• Nothing in this Performance Bonus changes the at-will nature of your employment, meaning you and U.S. Xpress may terminate the employment relationship at any time, with or without cause.<br>• You must be an active company driver on the day the bonus is paid.<br> <br>🔴 Trainer Opportunity<br>• To maximize your earnings, consider joining our trainer program<br>• Earn an additional $250 per week while a student is on your truck<br>• Receive up to $1,000 in bonuses once your student upgrades<br>• That’s an opportunity to earn up to $20,000 more per year if you have 1 year OTR experience and have been employed with us for 30 days as a safe driver.<br><br>🔴 Benefits<br>• Get 24/7 access operations support, no matter the time or day.<br>• Paid Vacation:<br>o 1 week after 1 year of service<br>o 2 weeks after 3 years<br>o 3 weeks after 7 years<br>o 4 weeks after 15 years                    <br>________________________________________<br>For full pay details, click here:         : https://tinyurl.com/3fe73c78<br><br><br>*Tagging*<br>Orientation Site: Jacksonville<br>Job: First Seat Driver<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: OTR<br>Acct: OTR<br>Region: All<br>Dedicated Domicile: Jacksonville<br>South Florida: Y/N<br> Updated 11.1.2024]]></description>
