      <Placemark>
        <name>OTR Teams Drive Across All 48 States – $5000 Split Sign-On Bonus!</name>
        <description><![CDATA[🔴 Job Details<br>• $5,000 Split Sign On Bonus<br>• Home Time: Home Time That Works for You – Whether you prefer longer hauls for maximum earnings or need a schedule that fits your lifestyle, we’ll work with you.<br>• Freight: 100% No Touch Freight; 80% drop & hook<br>• Mileage: 5,000+ Miles Per Week on Average<br>• Running Area: All 48 States<br>• Tractors: 2021 or Newer Freightliner Cascadia<br><br>🔴 Pay<br>• Additional Pay: $150 split / $75 per driver Hazmat Loads. $12.50/hour after the second hour split per driver for Detention Pay. $100 layover & Breakdown Pay<br><br>CPM Structure: Experienced Based<br>Split/Per Driver<br>3 months 0.72 / 0.36<br>6 months 0.74 / 0.37<br>9 months 0.76 / 0.38<br>12 months 0.78 / 0.39<br>24+ months .80 / .40<br><br>Tenure Pay starting at 24 Months With USX<br>24 Months 0.03 = Earning Potential 0.43<br>36 Months 0.04 = Earning Potential 0.44<br>48+ Months 0.05 = Earning Potential 0.45<br><br>• Utilization Bonus: Experienced teams with tenure frequently earn this! This pays out on ALL miles based on monthly performance. Our top teams hit the top bonus level! That’s an extra 14 CPM split – every mile, every load!<br><br>20000-21999 .02/.01<br>22000-23999 .06/.03<br>24000-25999 .10/.05<br>26000+ .14/.07<br><br>🔴 Sign On Bonus Payout<br>$5000 Split / $2500 Per Driver<br>$500 / $250 after 1st load<br>$500 / $250 after 30 days<br>$500 / $250 after 3 months<br>$1000 / $500 after 6 months<br>$1000 / $500 after 9 months<br>$1500 / $750 after 1 year<br><br>🔴 Bonus Eligibility<br>• U.S. Xpress reserves the right to modify or cancel the Sign-on bonus at any time with appropriate notice under applicable law.<br>• Nothing in this Sign-on Bonus changes the at-will nature of your employment, meaning you and U.S. Xpress may terminate the employment relationship at any time, with or without cause.<br>• You must be an active company driver on the day the bonus is paid.<br><br>🔴 Benefits<br>• Industry-leading pay package<br>• Support staff on site 24/7 to assist<br>• Paid Vacation:<br>o 1 week after 1 year of service<br>o 2 weeks after 3 years<br>o 3 weeks after 7 years<br>o 4 weeks after 15 years<br><br>🔴 Tagging<br>Orientation Site: Closest Terminal<br>Job: First Seat Driver<br>Solo/Team: Team<br>Area: OTR<br>Acct: OTR<br>Region: All<br>Dedicated Domicile: Closest Terminal<br>South Florida: Y/N<br>Company: US Xpress 01<br>Last Update 4.20.26<br>  ]]></description>
