$4000 Sign On Bonus!]]></name>
        <description><![CDATA[🔴 Job Details<br>• $4000 Sign on Bonus<br>• Home Time: Drivers are home Saturday & Sunday for 34 hour reset. Drivers who choose to remain out instead of returning home for their reset may run additional weekend freight to earn extra miles and pay.<br>• Freight: Combination of live loads and preloaded trailers.<br>• Running Area: Drivers primarily run within their region, with occasional routes outside the area to maximize miles—all while maintaining consistent weekly home time for a 34-hour reset. Typical running area ranges from Northern NC up to Maine, and as far west as Eastern Ohio. Combination of live unloads and pre-loaded trailers. Willing to drive in NYC is a plus but<br>not required. Running area for the fleet can be anywhere from VA to ME.<br>• Mileage: 1500 miles average per week depending on HOS and availability. 400-mile average length of haul<br>• Tractors: 2021 or newer Freightliner Cascadia or Kenworth<br><br><br>🔴 Pay<br>• Additional Pay: $20 1st stop/ $35 2nd stop/ $50 3rd+ stop. $65 Long Island delivery. $12.50 per hour detention pay after 2 hours. Per diem program is not available for regional fleet drivers.<br>• Performance Bonus: Earn up to an additional 3 CPM based on safety, mileage, and productivity, starting the first of the month following your hire date. Must be an active OTR driver at the time of bonus payout to qualify.<br>• Top 20% of our Regional Drivers at the SHP Terminal earn $1700  Weekly<br>**Per diem program is not available for regional fleet drivers<br><br>CPM Structure: Experienced Based<br>3–11 months: $0.80 per mile<br>1 year: $0.81 per mile<br>2 years: $0.82 per mile<br>3 years: $0.83 per mile<br>4 years: $0.84 per mile<br>5 years: $0.85 per mile<br><br>🔴 Sign On Bonus Payout<br>$4000 Total Payout<br>1st load $500.00<br>Month 1 $500.00<br>Month 2 $500.00<br>Month 3 $500.00<br>Month 4 $500.00<br>Month 5 $500.00<br>Month 6 $1,000.00<br><br>🔴 Bonus Eligibility<br>• U.S. Xpress reserves the right to modify or cancel the Sign-on or Performance bonus at any time with appropriate notice under applicable law.<br>• Nothing in this Sign-on or Performance Bonus changes the at-will nature of your employment, meaning you and U.S. Xpress may terminate the employment relationship at any time, with or without cause.<br>• You must be an active company driver on the day the bonus is paid.<br><br>🔴 Benefits<br>• Support staff on site 24/7 to assist<br>• Paid Vacation:<br>o 1 week after 1 year of service<br>o 2 weeks after 3 years<br>o 3 weeks after 7 years<br>o 4 weeks after 15 years<br><br>🔴Tagging<br>Orientation Site: SHIPPENSBURG PA, Springfield<br>Job: First Seat Driver<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: OTR<br>Region: Northeast<br>Sign on Bonus: Y/N<br>Dedicated Domicile: SHIPPENSBURG<br>South Florida: Y/N<br>Company: US Xpress 01<br>Updated 3.17.26]]></description>
