      <Placemark>
        <name>🚛🏠Ohio Valley Fleet $4000 Sign On Bonus!!!</name>
        <description><![CDATA[🔴 Key Requirements<br>• Strong trip-planning skills are essential for success on this fleet.<br><br>🔴 Job Details<br>• $4000 Sign on Bonus<br>• Summary: The Ohio Valley Fleet offers the consistency of a dedicated lane while operating under our OTR Division. Designed to get drivers home weekly for a 34-hour reset, balancing steady miles with reliable home time.<br>• Home Time: Get home some time Saturday for your 34 hour reset with the opportunity to get through the house once a week for a 10 hour break<br>• Freight: 100% no-touch freight with 80% drop & hook on one end, 20% live load/unload on opposite<br>• Operating Area: Intra-Ohio lanes OR power lanes running in and out of Ohio into the Southeast and Northeast (No NYC) Must have the flexibility to run either<br>• Tractors: Late-model 2021 or newer Freightliner Cascadias or Kenworths<br><br>🔴 Pay<br>• Weekly Minimum Pay: $1,400 minimum. Must be available for 5.5 days to run, must meet on-time delivery expectations, no service failures, and complete 34 hour reset weekly as scheduled<br>• Average Annual Earnings: $78,000<br>• Additional Pay: $12.50 per hour after the 2nd hour detention pay; $100/day layover and breakdown pay.<br><br><br>🔴 Sign On Bonus<br>1st load $500.00<br>Month 1 $500.00<br>Month 2 $500.00<br>Month 3 $500.00<br>Month 4 $500.00<br>Month 5 $500.00<br>Month 6 $1,000.00<br>Total $4,000.00<br><br>🔴 Bonus Eligibility<br>• U.S. Xpress reserves the right to modify or cancel the Sign-on bonus at any time with appropriate notice under applicable law.<br>• Nothing in this Sign-on Bonus changes the at-will nature of your employment, meaning you and U.S. Xpress may terminate the employment relationship at any time, with or without cause.<br>• You must be an active company driver on the day the bonus is paid.<br><br>🔴 Benefits<br>• Support staff on site 24/7 to assist<br>• Paid Vacation<br><br>🔴Tagging<br>Orientation Site: Springfield USX Terminal<br>Job: First Seat Driver<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: OTR<br>Region: OHVALFLEET<br>Dedicated Domicile: Springfield USX Terminal<br>South Florida: Y/N<br>Company: US Xpress 01<br>Sign On Bonus: Y]]></description>
