      <name>Owner Operator-Dedicated</name>
      <Placemark>
        <name>DT Warrensburg MO</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Owner Operator<br><br>🔴 Key Requirements<br>• Must have 6 months of experience in the last 3 years<br>• NC residents: must carry workers’ compensation insurance. USX can facilitate this insurance coverage on the contractor’s behalf with a private insurer.<br>• Contractor brings gear to orientation; immediate route assignment provided<br>• Homeward redirection available if gear is left behind<br><br>🔴 Restrictions<br>• Hiring area excludes: CA, NY, IL, NJ, CT, WA, OR, MA, MD, PA<br>• Contractors do not receive orientation pay<br><br>🔴 Dedicated Account Details:<br>• Training: 1 week ride along with current driver at $150/day<br>• Home Time: Contractors will get a full 34 hour reset based on the needs of the customer, delivery days, and market.<br>• Freight: Each load is multi stop and can have as many as 4 stops per trailer and loaded with average of 3500 pieces total load and is 100% contractor touch unload.<br>• Mileage: Each contractor can average 1700 miles per week and expect to pull at least 3 loads per week.<br>• Running Area: This account operates in ND, SD, NE, KS, OK, AR, MO, IA, MN, WI, IL, KY, TN, IN.<br><br>🔴 Truck & Lease Info<br>• No money down | No credit check | Walkaway lease<br>• Current fleet mix is:<br>o 2022–2027 Freightliners<br>o 2022–2024 Kenworths<br>o 2026-2027 Kenworths<br>o 2025–2027 Volvos<br>o 2022-2023 trucks offer a mix of tractors with or without APUs. All 2024-2027 trucks do not have APUs.<br>• Lease terms: 2-5 years<br>• Up to 600,000 miles in maintenance coverage, subject to exclusions.<br>• ATBS Pre-Fund Call Required for contractors who choose the mileage contract<br>• Be prepared with current monthly expenses to build a cash-flow plan tailored to your business.<br>O Truck Pricing Summary: https://tinyurl.com/yyemactj<br>🔴 Costs<br>• Bobtail Coverage: $8.35/week per unit<br>• Bobtail Plus: $7.42/week per unit (deductible reduced to $250)<br>• Occupational Accident: $40.45/week per worker<br>• Physical Damage: $1.07 per $1,000 per week<br><br>🔴 Pay<br>• Average weekly | annually: $3,600 weekly | $187,000 annually before expenses<br>• Actual earnings vary based on miles run, freight availability, operating expenses, market conditions, and individual performance.<br>• $1.20 per mile + fuel surcharge<br>$275 unload pay<br>$25 stop pay<br>$50 backhaul<br><br>🔴 Advantages<br>• Option for contractor to purchase lower-cost insurance coverage facilitated by U.S. Xpress.<br>• Become a trainer to increase compensation potential<br>• Pet policy: $500 pet fee, split into easy $50 weekly payments.<br><br>🔴 Tagging<br>IC Job: First Seat Driver (FSD)<br>Solo/Team: solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: DT Warrensburg<br>SIGN ON BONUS: N<br>LEASE EQUIPMENT TYPE:<br>Company: US Xpress 01 ORIENTATION SITE: ]]></description>
