        <name>FD Front Royal VA</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Independent Contractors<br><br>🔴 Key Requirements<br>• Patience & strong customer service skills are essential for this role<br>• Physical ability for live unloads.<br>• A double endorsement is preferred, but not required<br>•Must have 6 months of experience in the last 3 years<br>• NC residents: must carry workers’ compensation insurance. USX can facilitate this insurance coverage on the contractor’s behalf with a private insurer.<br>• Contractor brings gear to orientation; immediate route assignment provided<br>• Homeward redirection available if gear is left behind<br><br>🔴 Restrictions<br>• Contractors do not receive orientation pay<br>• NO-CA, NY, IL, NJ, CT, WA, OR, MA, MD, PA<br><br>🔴 Dedicated Account Details<br>• Training: 1 week ride along with current driver at $150 per day – deferral offered<br>• Home Time: Contractors will get a full 34 hour reset based on the needs of the customer, delivery days, and market.<br>• Freight: 100% touch freight, live unload at FD stores. Each load is multi stop and can have as many as 5 stops per trailer. Backhauls required if assigned to load.<br>• Running Area: VA, NC, DC, PA, NH, OH, WV all within 700 miles of the Front Royal, VA DC<br>• Mileage: average 1200-1300 miles weekly and pull 3 loads per week<br><br>🔴 Pay<br>• Average weekly | annually: $3,000 weekly | $156,000 annually<br>• Additional Pay: $275 unload pay. $30 backhaul.<br><br>$1.44 per mile + fuel surcharge<br>$275 unload pay<br>$30 backhaul<br><br>🔴 Truck & Lease Info<br>• No money down | No credit check | Walkaway lease<br><br>• Current fleet mix is:<br>o 2022–2027 Freightliners<br>o 2022–2024 Kenworths<br>o 2026-2027 Kenworths<br>o 2025–2027 Volvos<br>o 2022-2023 trucks offer a mix of tractors with or without APUs. All 2024-2027 trucks do not have APUs.<br>• Lease terms: 2-5 years<br>• Up to 600,000 miles in maintenance coverage, subject to exclusions.<br>• ATBS Pre-Fund Call Required for contractors who choose the mileage contract<br>• Be prepared with current monthly expenses to build a cash-flow plan tailored to your business.<br>O Truck Pricing Summary: https://tinyurl.com/yyemactj<br>🔴 Costs<br>• Bobtail Coverage: $8.35/week per unit<br>• Bobtail Plus: $7.42/week per unit (deductible reduced to $250)<br>• Occupational Accident: $40.45/week per worker<br>• Physical Damage: $1.07 per $1,000 per week<br><br>🔴 Advantages<br>• Option for contractor to purchase lower-cost insurance coverage facilitated by U.S. Xpress.<br>• Become a trainer to increase compensation potential<br>• Pet policy: $500 pet fee, split into easy $50 weekly payments.<br><br>🔴Unload Account Videos:<br>https://vimeo.com/507100528/da4b42c25c     <br>https://vimeo.com/669499314<br><br>🔴Tagging<br>IC JOB: First Seat Driver<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: FD Front Royal ORIENTATION SITE: Closest Site (NO DALLAS) Updated 3.10.25]]></description>
