        <description><![CDATA[Independent Contractors<br><br>🔴 Key Requirements<br>• Must have 6 months of experience in the last 3 years<br>• NC residents: must carry workers’ compensation insurance. USX can facilitate this insurance coverage on the contractor’s behalf with a private insurer.<br>• Contractor brings gear to orientation; immediate route assignment provided<br>• Homeward redirection available if gear is left behind<br><br>🔴 Restrictions<br>• Hiring area excludes: CA, NY, IL, NJ, CT, WA, OR, MA, MD, PA<br>• Contractors do not receive orientation pay<br><br>🔴 Dedicated Account Details:<br>• Freight: Run a mix of dry and refrigerated no-touch grocery freight. Expect 1–3 routes per day with 1–3 stops per route.<br>• Mileage: Average 2,000–2,400 miles per week.<br>• Running Area: from the Walmart DC in Gordonsville, VA to store locations in MD, PA, WV, NC, and VA—all within 600 miles.<br>• Schedule: 24/7 operation with most runs scheduled overnight and on weekends/holidays that fall within your workweek.<br><br>🔴 Truck & Lease Info<br>• No money down | No credit check | Walkaway lease<br>• Current fleet mix is:<br>o 2022–2027 Freightliners<br>o 2022–2024 Kenworths<br>o 2026-2027 Kenworths<br>o 2025–2027 Volvos<br>o 2022-2023 trucks offer a mix of tractors with or without APUs. All 2024-2027 trucks do not have APUs.<br>• Lease terms: 2-5 years<br>• Up to 600,000 miles in maintenance coverage, subject to exclusions.<br>• ATBS Pre-Fund Call Required for contractors who choose the mileage contract<br>• Be prepared with current monthly expenses to build a cash-flow plan tailored to your business.<br>O Truck Pricing Summary: https://tinyurl.com/yyemactj<br>🔴 Costs<br>• Bobtail Coverage: $8.35/week per unit<br>• Bobtail Plus: $7.42/week per unit (deductible reduced to $250)<br>• Occupational Accident: $40.45/week per worker<br>• Physical Damage: $1.07 per $1,000 per week<br><br>🔴 Pay<br>• $1.00 per mile<br>• $20 per stop pay<br>• Walmart-provided fuel.<br><br>🔴 Advantages<br>• Option for contractor to purchase lower-cost insurance coverage facilitated by U.S. Xpress.<br>• Become a trainer to increase compensation potential<br>• Pet policy: $500 pet fee, split into easy $50 weekly payments.<br><br>🔴 Tagging<br>IC JOB: First Seat Driver<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Local<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Walmart Gordonsville]]></description>
