        <description><![CDATA[• Must have 6 months of experience in the last 3 years<br>• NC residents: must carry workers’ compensation insurance. USX can facilitate this insurance coverage on the contractor’s behalf with a private insurer.<br><br>🔴 Restrictions<br>• Contracting area excludes: CA, NY, IL, NJ, CT, WA, OR, MA, MD<br>• Owner Operators do not receive orientation pay<br><br>🔴 Truck & Lease Info<br>• No money down | No credit check | Walkaway lease<br>• Current fleet mix is:<br>o 2022–2027 Freightliners<br>o 2022–2024 Kenworths<br>o 2026-2027 Kenworths<br>o 2025–2027 Volvos<br>o 2022-2023 trucks offer a mix of tractors with or without APUs. All 2024-2027 trucks do not have APUs.<br>• Lease terms: 2-5 years<br>• Up to 600,000 miles in maintenance coverage, subject to exclusions.<br>O Truck Pricing Summary: https://tinyurl.com/yyemactj<br><br>🔴Insurance Costs if Owner Operator purchases facilitated private insurer coverage (O/O can choose to have own coverage as long as it meets the minimum requirements in contract)<br>Non-Trucking Liability: $8.35/week per unit<br>• Bobtail Plus: $7.42/week per unit (deductible reduced to $250)<br>• Occupational Accident: $40.45/week per worker<br>• Physical Damage: $1.07 per $1,000 per week<br><br>🔴 Job Details:<br>• Operations may include nights, weekends, and holidays based on customer demand.<br>• Freight: 100% No-Touch Refrigerated Freight delivering to Walmart & Sam’s Club stores.<br>• Service area includes routes in SC, NC, TN, and VA<br>• Estimated mileage is 1250 miles per week; actual miles may vary.<br>• Scheduling, home time, and days off are subject to customer needs and are not guaranteed.<br>• Schedule: Heavy freight days: Expect higher volumes on Wednesday, Thursday, Friday, and Saturday. Current schedule is a rotating schedule of 6 days worked/34-hour restart, then 5 days worked/2 days off.<br>• Additional workday assignments may be requested during peak or holiday periods.<br>• Start times and routes are typically assigned based on customer’s operational requirements.<br>• Must be flexible with work schedule and available to work weekends and holidays.<br><br><br>🔴 Advantages<br>• Fuel, tire and maintenance discounts.<br>• Option for Owner Operator to purchase lower-cost private insurance coverage facilitated by U.S. Xpress.<br>• Become a trainer to increase compensation potential.<br>• Pet policy: $500 pet fee, split into easy $50 weekly payments.<br>• Family-oriented atmosphere with an experienced staff.<br><br>🔴 Pay<br>Mileage: $1.00/mile<br>Stop/pickup: amount collected from customer not to exceed $22.50/stop<br>Loads/unloading $100.00 for full load/unload & $50.00 for driver assist<br>Detention: $85% of collected amount<br><br>🔴 Tagging<br>IC JOB: First Seat Driver<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Local<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Walmart Henderson]]></description>
