        <description><![CDATA[Owner Operators<br><br>🔴 Key Requirements<br>• Must have 6 months of experience in the last 3 years<br>• NC residents: must carry workers’ compensation insurance. USX can facilitate this insurance coverage on the contractor’s behalf with a private insurer.<br>• Owner Operator brings gear to orientation; immediate route assignment provided<br>• Homeward redirection available if gear is left behind<br><br>🔴 Restrictions<br>• Hiring area excludes: CA, NY, IL, NJ, CT, WA, OR, MA, MD<br>• No orientation pay<br><br>🔴 Truck & Lease Info<br>• No money down | No credit check | Walkaway lease<br>• Current fleet mix is:<br>o 2022–2027 Freightliners<br>o 2022–2024 Kenworths<br>o 2026-2027 Kenworths<br>o 2025–2027 Volvos<br>o 2022-2023 trucks offer a mix of tractors with or without APUs. All 2024-2027 trucks do not have APUs.<br>• Lease terms: 2-5 years<br>• Up to 600,000 miles in maintenance coverage, subject to exclusions.<br>• ATBS Pre-Fund Call Required<br>• Be prepared with current monthly expenses to build a cash-flow plan tailored to your business.<br><br><br>🔴 Costs<br>• Bobtail Coverage: $8.35/week per unit<br>• Bobtail Plus: $7.42/week per unit (deductible reduced to $250)<br>• Occupational Accident: $40.45/week per worker<br>• Physical Damage: $1.07 per $1,000 per week<br>• Average weekly payment: $535–$680 (based on miles, year, model)<br><br>🔴 Pay<br>• Mileage based compensation designed for owner operators<br>• Click below for Contract Pay Info:<br><br>o Mileage Revenue Contract Detail:<br>http://tiny.cc/vd62101<br><br>🔴 Operational Details<br>• Operates primarily in the 48 states, focus East of I-35<br>• Team markets available for West Coast & Southwest<br>• Freedom to accept or decline assigned loads<br>• Partnership that allows owners to build a profitable routine while also scheduling regular home time (often every few weeks) for themselves<br>• IC consultant ratio: 30–35 contractors per consultant<br><br>🔴 Advantages<br>• Option for owner operator to purchase lower-cost insurance coverage facilitated by U.S. Xpress.<br>• Become a trainer to increase compensation potential<br>• Pet policy: $500 pet fee, split into easy $50 weekly payments.<br><br>🔴 Tagging<br>IC Job: First Seat Driver (FSD)<br>Solo/Team: Solo/Team<br>Area: OTR<br>Acct: All accounts<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Phoenix<br>SIGN ON BONUS: N<br>ORIENTATION SITE: Closest Site<br>LEASE EQUIPMENT TYPE:<br>Contract Type: Mileage<br>Company: US Xpress 01<br>Updated 5.12.26]]></description>
