      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED Ollie’s Dedicated Tour Fleet
$4000 Sign On Bonus!</name>
        <description><![CDATA[🔴 Key Requirements<br>• Strong trip-planning skills are essential for success on this fleet.<br><br>🔴 Job Details<br>• $4000 Sign on Bonus<br>• Summary: The Ollie’s Dedicated Tour offers the consistency of a dedicated lane while operating under our OTR Division. Designed to get drivers home weekly for a 34-hour reset, balancing steady miles with reliable home time.<br>• Home Time: Weekly for a 34 hour reset<br>• Freight: 100% no-touch freight, pre-loaded, live unload. 1-3 stops per trailer. Average 3-5 loads per week<br>• Mileage: average 1,750 per week.<br>• Operating Area: IA, IL, IN, KY, MI, MO, NE, OH, WI<br>• Tractors: Late-model 2021 or newer Freightliner Cascadias or Kenworths<br><br>🔴 Pay<br>• Weekly Minimum Pay: $1,350 minimum or mileage, whichever is greater if you are available for 5.5 days to run. If not, you will revert to mileage pay for that week.<br>• Average Annual Earnings: $70,000<br>• Additional Pay: $12.50 per hour after the 2nd hour detention pay; $100/day layover and breakdown pay<br>• Performance Bonus: Earn up to an additional 3 CPM based on safety, mileage, and productivity, starting the first of the month following your hire date. Must be an active OTR driver at the time of bonus payout to qualify.<br><br>CPM Structure: https://usxpress.sharepoint.com/:b:/s/DriverRecruiting/IQDGz5K-lRuaQKNF-9kHJ9tVAWsA7QiIXJ3ygfIIRMfQAO8?e=fATo0P<br><br>🔴 Sign On Bonus<br>1st load $500.00<br>Month 1 $500.00<br>Month 2 $500.00<br>Month 3 $500.00<br>Month 4 $500.00<br>Month 5 $500.00<br>Month 6 $1,000.00<br>Total $4,000.00<br><br>🔴 Bonus Eligibility<br>• U.S. Xpress reserves the right to modify or cancel the Sign-on bonus at any time with appropriate notice under applicable law.<br>• Nothing in this Sign-on Bonus changes the at-will nature of your employment, meaning you and U.S. Xpress may terminate the employment relationship at any time, with or without cause.<br>• You must be an active company driver on the day the bonus is paid.<br><br>🔴 Benefits<br>• Support staff on site 24/7 to assist<br>• Paid Vacation<br><br>🔴Tagging<br>Orientation Site: Chicago<br>Job: First Seat Driver<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: OTR<br>Region: Ollie’s Tour<br>Dedicated Domicile: Chicago<br>South Florida: Y/N<br>Company: US Xpress 01<br>Sign On Bonus: Y]]></description>
