      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED Memphis Regional Fleet
$2000 Sign On Bonus!!</name>
        <description><![CDATA[🔴 Key Requirements<br>• Effective trip planning is essential<br><br>🔴 Job Details<br>• $2000 Sign on Bonus<br>• Home Time: Home weekly<br>• Freight: 100% no-touch freight, with 50-60% drop & hook and 40-50% live unload.<br>• Running Area: Our Memphis Regional Fleet plans routes that span multiple regions but are designed to get you back home for your 34 hour reset every week—balancing steady miles with consistent home time.<br>• Mileage: Average Weekly Miles: Drivers typically run 2,000 miles per week depending on Hours of Service (HOS) and availability. Average LOH is 300 miles.<br>• Tractors: 2021 or newer Freightliner Cascadias or Kenworths<br><br>🔴 Pay<br>• Average weekly: $1,100 - 1,200<br>• Additional Pay: $12.50 per hour detention pay after the second hour. $100 per day layover/breakdown pay.<br>• Performance Bonus: Earn up to an additional 3 CPM based on safety, mileage, and productivity, starting the first of the month following your hire date. Must be an active OTR driver at the time of bonus payout to qualify.<br>• Top 20% of our Regional Drivers at the Memphis Terminal earn $1550+ Weekly <br><br><br>CPM Structure: Experienced Based<br>https://tinyurl.com/3fe73c78<br><br>🔴 Sign On Bonus Payout<br>1st load $500.00<br>Month 1 $500.00<br>Month 2 $500.00<br>Month 3 $500.00<br>Total $2,000.00<br><br>🔴 Bonus Eligibility<br>• U.S. Xpress reserves the right to modify or cancel the Sign-on or Performance bonus at any time with appropriate notice under applicable law.<br>• Nothing in this Sign-on or Performance Bonus changes the at-will nature of your employment, meaning you and U.S. Xpress may terminate the employment relationship at any time, with or without cause.<br>• You must be an active company driver on the day the bonus is paid.<br><br>🔴 Benefits<br>• Support staff on site 24/7 to assist<br>• Paid Vacation:<br>o 1 week after 1 year of service<br>o 2 weeks after 3 years<br>o 3 weeks after 7 years<br>o 4 weeks after 15 years<br><br>🔴 Tagging<br>Orientation Site: Memphis, Dallas or THL Job: First Seat Driver<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: OTR<br>Region: Southwest<br>Dedicated Domicile: Memphis USX Terminal<br>South Florida: Y/N Sign On Bonus: Y/N<br>Company: US Xpress 01<br>Updated 3.20.26]]></description>
