      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED FD Duncan OK $1000 Sign On Bonus</name>
        <description><![CDATA[🔴 Key Requirements<br>• Patience & strong customer service skills are essential for this role<br>• Drivers must bring two weeks’ worth of supplies to orientation. 2 Shadow runs will be completed with current driver paid at $150 each run.<br>• Ability to drive nights, weekends, and holidays<br>• Ability to perform heavy physical labor—freight is unloaded box-by-box using rollers.<br>• Willing to operate in varying weather conditions.<br><br>🔴 Other Carriers On This Account<br>CR England<br><br>🔴 Job Details <br>• Home Time: Home weekly for a 34-hour reset—typically Saturday afternoon to Monday morning or Friday night to Sunday morning<br>• Freight: Dry van freight, 100% touch freight—live unload at Family Dollar and occasional Dollar Tree stores. Must complete 3 loads per week, with 1–7 stops per load.<br>• Running Area: Deliveries to TX, OK, AR, LA, MS<br>• Tractors: Internationals and Freightliners and Kenworths<br>• Schedule: All deliveries start at 5:00 AM—drivers must typically arrive by 7:00 PM the night before for a full 10-hour break. Routes may include nights, weekends, and holidays.<br><br>🔴 Pay<br>• Average weekly: $1,550+<br>• Top Performers: Top earners $2000 weekly • $80k-$100k+ Annually<br>• Additional Pay: $240 for full trailer load/unload. $25 stop pay. $50 backhaul.                                     All in Pay - $1.00 (CPM + accessorial pay + stop pay)<br><br>CPM Structure: Experience-Based Mileage Pay<br>0–6 months: $0.50/mile<br>6–12 months: $0.51/mile<br>12–18 months: $0.52/mile<br>18–24 months: $0.53/mile<br>24–36 months: $0.54/mile<br>36–48 months: $0.55/mile<br>48–60 months: $0.56/mile<br>60–72 months: $0.57/mile<br>72–84 months: $0.58/mile<br>84–96 months: $0.59/mile<br>96+ months: $0.60/mile<br><br>🔴 Sign On Bonus Payout <br>$1000 Total Payout<br>$500 after the first load<br>$500 after 30 days <br>🔴 Benefits<br>• Support staff on site 24/7 to assist<br>• Paid Vacation:<br>1 week after 1 year of service<br>2 weeks after 2 years<br>3 weeks after 7 years<br>4 weeks after 10 years<br><br>🔴Unload Account Videos<br>https://vimeo.com/507100528/da4b42c25c     <br>https://vimeo.com/669499314<br><br>🔴Tagging<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>Dedicated Domicile- Family Dollar Duncan<br>SIGN ON BONUS: Y/N<br>Orientation Site: Close<br>Company: US Xpress 01]]></description>
