      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED Southeast Regional- Jacksonville based. Home Weekly!</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Job Details:<br>• Regionalized Freight: Our Southeast Regional Fleet plans routes that span multiple regions but are designed to get you back home for your 34 hour reset every week—balancing steady miles with consistent home time.<br>• Excellent trip planning is a must to be successful on this fleet.<br>• Average Weekly Miles: Drivers typically run 1800 miles per week depending on Hours of Service (HOS) and availability.<br>• Average Weekly Pay: $1000-$1100 gross per week.<br>• Freight Type: 100% no-touch freight, with 50-60% drop & hook and 40-50% live unload.<br><br>Equipment and Support:<br>• Drive in 2021 or newer Freightliner Cascadias or Kenworths.<br>• Get 24/7 access to operations support—no matter the time or day.<br><br>Vacation Package:<br>• 1 year = 1 week<br>• 3 years = 2 weeks<br>• 7 years = 3 weeks<br>• 15 years = 4 weeks<br><br>Pay and Bonuses:<br>• Detention Pay: $12.50 per hour after the second hour.<br>• Layover/Breakdown Pay: $100 per day.<br>• Performance Bonus: Earn up to an additional 3 CPM based on safety, mileage, and productivity, starting the first of the month following your hire date. Must be an active OTR driver at the time of bonus payout to qualify.<br><br><br><br>For full pay details, click here: Pay Scale https://tinyurl.com/3fe73c78<br><br>*Tagging*<br>Orientation Site: Jacksonville, THL<br>Job: First Seat Driver<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: OTR<br>Region: Southeast<br>Dedicated Domicile: Jacksonville USX Terminal<br>South Florida: Y/N<br>Company: US Xpress 01<br>Updated 4.14.25]]></description>
