      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED STAPLES TERRE HAUTE IN.
$1500 Sign On Bonus! 2 Weeks out! Average gross $1450 per week! No touch freight! Will run OTR freight until full start up 2/1/26. ANY USA TRUCK DRIVER RUNNING ACCT NOT IN HIRING AREA REACH OUT TO DALTON DUNBAR FOR APPROVAL</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Restrictions<br>• High-earning, consistent-mileage opportunity with strong support and predictable home time<br><br>Job Details<br>• USX Dedicated Fleet: no-touch dry van freight, primarily paper products<br>• Consistent round-trip freight originating and ending in Terre Haute, IN<br>• Deliver near your home location, take your reset at home, then run a backhaul to Terre Haute<br>• Delivery states: Midwest, TX, FL, GA, TN, CO<br>• Streamlined operations: no trailer hunts or unloading delays<br>• Predictable lanes, great miles, and steady work<br>• Home every 2 weeks<br><br>Key Requirements<br>• Availability for all shift types: days, nights, weekends<br>• Ability to handle 2–3 stops per load, avg 30-minute unload time. No touch freight<br><br>Benefits<br>• 24/7 Dispatch Support<br><br><br>Pay Structure<br>• Average $1,450 per week<br>• Top earners $1,600+ per week<br>• Avg 2–3 loads per week, 2,000–2,500 miles/week<br>• Average annual pay $75k-$80k<br><br><br>Experience-Based Pay<br>• Consistent miles and dedicated freight provide potential for high weekly earnings<br>• 3–11 mo: $0.54 CPM<br>• 1 - 2 years: $0.56 CPM<br>• 3 - 5 years: $0.58 CPM<br>• 5+ years: $0.60 CPM<br><br>• Stop Pay $10 all stops<br><br>• Layover pay: $100 after 24 hours<br>• Detention pay: $15/hour after 2 hours<br><br><br>• Sign-On Bonus (SOB): $1500<br>1st Load $ 250<br>30 days $ 500<br>60 days $ 250<br>90 days $ 500<br>Bonus Eligibility<br>1. U.S. Xpress reserves the right to modify or cancel the Sign-on bonus at any time with appropriate notice under applicable law.<br>2. Nothing in this [Sign-on Bonus changes the at-will nature of your employment, meaning you and U.S. Xpress may terminate the employment relationship at any time, with or without cause.<br>3. You must be an active company driver on the day the bonus is paid.<br><br>• Tagging<br>Orientation Site – Dallas<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Staples Terre Haute<br>SIGN ON BONUS: Y/N<br>Company: US Xpress 01<br>Updated 1.15.26]]></description>
