        <description><![CDATA[Restrictions<br>• Must live within 150 miles of Martinsburg, WV<br>• Tanker endorsement required (but don’t worry—we’ll reimburse you, and you have 90 days to get it!)<br>• This is a high-earning, consistent-mileage opportunity with a strong support system and predictable home time<br>________________________________________<br>Job Details<br>Join the Quad Graphics dedicated fleet and enjoy steady miles and biweekly home time!<br>You’ll run no-touch, dry van freight including paper products and occasional ink loads.<br>• Average of $1400 per week<br>• Out 2 weeks, home 2 days<br>• All shift types – days, nights, and weekends<br>• Runs stay east of I-35<br>• Average 2000-2400 miles per week<br>• Average 3 loads per week<br>• Top earners averaging $1500-$1600 per week<br>• Average load and unload time is 1-2 hours<br>________________________________________<br>Key Requirements<br>• Willing to get a tanker endorsement within 90 days (we’ll cover the cost!)<br>________________________________________<br>Benefits<br>• Paid vacation:<br>o 1 week after 1 year<br>o 3 weeks after 3 years<br><br>________________________________________<br>Experience-Based Pay<br>• 0–1 year: $0.60 CPM<br>• 13 months–2 years: $0.62 CPM<br>• 25 months- 5 years: $0.63 CPM<br>•5+ years: $0.64 CPM<br><br>• Stop Pay $15 after 1st stop<br>• Layover pay: $100 after 24 hours<br>• Detention pay: $15/hour after 4 hours<br><br>• Average Gross: $1,400/week — over $72,000/year!<br><br>________________________________________<br><br><br>• Tagging<br>Orientation Site - Shippensburg PA<br>Job: Dedicated OTR DRIVER DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: OTR<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: Northeast<br>DED/Dom Term: Quad Graphics<br>SIGN ON BONUS: Y/N<br>Company: US Xpress 01<br>Updated 7.15.25]]></description>
