        <name>CLOSED OTR Teams SEASONAL BARR NUNN FREIGHT! $1750 WK/DRIVER. $5k Split Sign On Bonus!! Can hire anywhere we would bring in an OTR Team</name>
        <description><![CDATA[• Timeline: Teams should be ready to start running through Christmas hauling Barr Nunn freight.<br>• Pay: $250 per day per driver. Running 7 days per week equals $1,750 weekly per driver. That’s $3500 per week for the truck!<br>________________________________________<br>• Freight & Lanes:<br>o No set region; routes typically run Northeast to Ohio, with possible freight into Illinois and the Carolinas.<br>o Drop and Hook freight, often pre-stacked.<br>o No NYC deliveries.<br>________________________________________<br>• Customers: Freight may include Walmart, QVC, UPS, FedEx, and Sam’s Club.<br>• Length of Haul: Average 300–750 miles per trip, approximately 3,500 miles per week.<br>• Load Priority: Treat all loads as High-Value (HVP) and maintain consistent communication while under load.<br>• Holidays: Thanksgiving and Christmas are observed.<br>• Expectations: Strong focus on service and communication.<br>• Inclement Weather: Drivers will be paid if delayed while under a load due to weather conditions.<br>________________________________________<br>$5000 SOB ($2500 per driver)<br>• $500 after 1st load ($250 per driver)<br>• $500 at 30 days ($250 per driver)<br>• $500 at 3 months ($250 per driver)<br>• $1000 at 6 months ($500 per driver)<br>• $1000 at 9 months ($500 per driver)<br>• $1500 at 1 year ($750 per driver)<br><br><br>Bonus eligibility requirements:<br>o U.S. Xpress reserves the right to modify or cancel the Sign-On or Performance Bonus at any time with appropriate notice under applicable law.<br>o Nothing in this Sign-On or Performance Bonus changes the at-will nature of your employment, meaning you and U.S. Xpress may terminate the employment relationship at any time, with or without cause.<br>o You must be an active company driver on the day the bonus is paid.<br><br><br>Top-Tier Equipment & Benefits<br>• 2021 or Newer Freightliner Cascadia<br>• Medical, Dental, & Vision – Blue Cross Blue Shield<br>• 24/7 Support Team<br>• Rider & Pet Policy (Restrictions Apply)<br>• Need a Co-Driver? We’ll Match You!<br>• Want to team up with an internal driver? Let Driver Placement know!<br><br><br>*Tagging*<br>Orientation Site: Closest Terminal<br>Job: First Seat Driver<br>Solo/Team: Team<br>Area: OTR<br>Acct: OTR<br>Region: All<br>Dedicated Domicile: THL<br>Barr Nunn: YES<br>South Florida: Y/N<br>Company: US Xpress 01 Last Update 10.13.25]]></description>
