      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED PetSmart Ottawa, IL. Drivers must live within 75 miles of Ottawa, IL (61350). Home weekly. Average $1325 per week! $2000 Sign On Bonus!!!</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Restrictions<br>• Must live within 75 miles of Ottawa, IL (ZIP: 61350)<br>• Weekend and holiday work is expected<br>• Routes include nights, weekends, and holidays that fall within your work week<br>• 10-hour breaks typically occur on the road<br>________________________________________<br>Job Details<br>• Home Time: Weekly 34-hour reset (not guaranteed on weekends)<br>• Average Weekly Pay: $1,325<br>• Freight Type: Dry, No-Touch freight<br>• Deliveries: 100% live unloads at PetSmart stores<br>• Delivery States: IL, IN, MI, MO, IA, WI<br>• Miles: Average 1,500 miles per week<br>• Loads: Average 5-6 loads per week<br>• Stops: 2 to 5 stops per route<br>• Store Returns/Backhauls: Required after delivery; about 40% of loads include backhauls<br>________________________________________<br>Key Requirements<br>• Strong commitment to on-time service at both pick-up and delivery locations<br>• Ability to handle overnight runs and varying schedules<br>• We deliver Sunday-Friday<br>________________________________________<br>Benefits<br>• Vacation Pay:<br>o 1 week after 1 year<br>o 2 weeks after 2 years<br>o 3 weeks after 7 years<br>________________________________________<br>Experience-Based Pay<br>• 0–12 Months: $0.52 per mile<br>• 24 Months: $0.53 per mile<br>• 36 Months: $0.54 per mile<br>• 48 Months: $0.55 per mile<br>• 60 Months: $0.57 per mile<br>• 72 Months: $0.59 per mile<br>• 84 Months: $0.61 per mile<br>• 96 Months: $0.63 per mile<br>• 108 Months: $0.65 per mile<br>• 120 Months: $0.68 per mile<br><br>• Stop Pay: $25 per stop after the first<br>• Backhaul Pay: $25 per backhaul<br>• Minimum Load Pay: $50 per load<br>• Sign-On Bonus (SOB): $500 first load<br>$500 30 days<br>$1000 60 days<br>(must be active and seated at the time of bonus payout to qualify)                                                                                   <br>Tagging<br>Orientation Site - Chicago<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: PetSmart Ottawa<br>SIGN ON BONUS: Y/N<br>UPDATED 6.11.25]]></description>
