      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED OTR Teams COMPANY South Florida - 6 months Experience Required.   $12 K SIGN ON BONUS Split or $15K SIGN ON BONUS SPLIT! </name>
        <description><![CDATA[Requirements:<br>• Minimum 6 months’ experience required<br>• No drivers who need a team partner may be scheduled until one is located<br><br>Schedule & Home Time:<br>• 3 weeks out / 5 days home<br>• No loaded trailers can go home during home time<br>• Empty trailers can be taken home, but must remain hooked to the tractor at the driver’s residence<br><br>Miles & Freight:<br>• No-touch freight – 80% drop & hook<br>• 5,000+ miles/week on average<br><br>Sign-On Bonus – Split:<br>$12K Bonus (less than 1 year exp)<br>• $500 after 1st load<br>• Paid at $500 in monthly increments for 11 months<br><br>$15K Bonus (both drivers have 1+ year verifiable experience)<br>• $250 after 1st load<br>• $250 at 30 days<br>• $1,000 at 60 days<br>• $750 at 150 days<br>• Paid every 90 days after 150 days until $7,500 each ($15K total) at 2 years<br><br>Base Pay – Per Experience Level (CPM Split / Per Driver):<br>• 3 mo: 0.56 / 0.28<br>• 4–6 mo: 0.60 / 0.30<br>• 7–12 mo: 0.61 / 0.305<br>• 13–24 mo: 0.62 / 0.31<br>• 25–36 mo: 0.63 / 0.315<br>• 37–60 mo: 0.64 / 0.32<br>• 61–120 mo: 0.65 / 0.325<br>• 120+ mo: 0.66 / 0.33<br>• Hazmat Loads – $150 split ($75 per driver)<br>• Detention – $12.50/hr split (after 2 hrs)<br>• Layover & Breakdown – $100/day<br><br>Extra Pay: Earn More with Safety & Utilization Bonuses!<br><br>• Safety Bonus: Most teams qualify! Earn an extra 1 CPM for running safe miles and keeping an Event Recorder score of 20 or less!<br>• Utilization Bonus: Our top teams hit the top bonus level! That’s an extra 14 CPM split – every mile, every load!<br>20K–21,999 mi: +0.02 split / 0.01 each<br>22K–23,999 mi: +0.06 split / 0.03 each<br>24K–25,999 mi: +0.10 split / 0.05 each<br>26K+: +0.14 split / 0.07 each<br><br>https://usxpress.sharepoint.com/:x:/s/DriverRecruiting/EZcZOSGAziBFu60ARMjct8sBSpZuTMTkLpJCSPNxi9UOOw?e=yQ8YUE<br><br>Equipment & Benefits:<br>• 2021+ Freightliner Cascadias<br>• Rider & Pet Policy (restrictions apply)<br>• 24/7 Support Team<br><br>*Tagging*<br>Orientation Site: Closest Terminal<br>Job: First Seat Driver<br>Solo/Team: Team<br>Area: OTR<br>Acct: OTR<br>Region: All<br>Dedicated Domicile: THL<br>South Florida: Y<br>Company: US Xpress 01<br>Last Update 8.18.25]]></description>
