      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED MDI - $1000 Sign On Bonus!! 80 miles Hickory, NC. Drivers need 3 months of exp to qualify company drivers. HOME WEEKLY! Drivers must have personal transportation to and from the DC weekly. </name>
        <description><![CDATA[Restrictions<br>• Must live within 80 miles of Hickory, NC<br>• Must have personal transportation to and from the Distribution Center (DC) — trucks cannot be taken home<br>• Occasional Saturday loads required<br>• 50% of freight is live load/unload<br>• Night, weekend, and holiday work required based on route schedule<br>• Drivers averaging 1,550 miles and 3+ loads weekly typically earn $1,150–$1,200/week<br>• Annual earnings potential up to $60,000+<br><br>________________________________________<br>Job Details<br>• Freight Type: 100% no-touch freight, but 50% live load/unload at customer locations<br>• Average Miles: 1,550 per week<br>• Stops: 3–5 per day (excluding first/last, $15 per stop paid)<br>• Home Time: Minimum weekly, with 34-hour resets typically starting Saturday and ending Monday<br>• Orientation: One-day classroom orientation, paid $100<br>• Delivery Area: NC, SC, GA, TN, PA, WV, VA, OH<br>• Equipment: Mix of Internationals, Freightliners, Kenworths, and Volvos<br>________________________________________<br>Key Requirements<br>• Strong customer service skills and patience<br>• Willingness to drive early mornings and throughout the day<br>• Must meet physical requirements and be able to complete multiple stops daily<br>________________________________________<br>Benefits<br>• Weekly home time<br>• Paid vacation:<br>o 1 week after 1 year<br>o 2 weeks after 3 years<br>o 3 weeks after 7 years<br>o 4 weeks after 10 years<br>• Supportive and tenured dispatch and operations team<br>________________________________________<br>Pay Structure<br>• Mileage Pay (based on verified experience):<br>o <1 Year: $0.63 CPM<br>o 1 Year: $0.64 CPM<br>o 2 Years: $0.65 CPM<br>o 4+ Years: $0.66 CPM<br>• Stop Pay: $15 per stop (excluding first and last stop)<br>• Orientation Pay: $100 for one-day class<br>________________________________________<br>• Sign-On Bonus (SOB): $1000 total ($500 after the first load, $500 after 30 days) must be active and seated at the time of bonus payout to qualify.<br><br>Bonus Eligibility<br>1. U.S. Xpress reserves the right to modify or cancel the Sign-on bonus at any time with appropriate notice under applicable law.<br>2. Nothing in this [Sign-on Bonus changes the at-will nature of your employment, meaning you and U.S. Xpress may terminate the employment relationship at any time, with or without cause.<br>3. You must be an active company driver on the day the bonus is paid.<br><br>•Tagging: Orientation Site - Duncan<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: MDI HICKORY<br>SIGN ON BONUS: Y/N]]></description>
