      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED Quad Graphics - $1000 Sign On Bonus!! Home Every 2 Weeks! MUST LIVE WITHIN 150 MILES OF THE ROCK, GA. $1000 weekly minimum! Average gross around $1250 per week! No touch freight!! </name>
        <description><![CDATA[Restrictions<br>• Must live within 150 miles of The Rock, GA<br>• Tanker endorsement required (but don’t worry—we’ll reimburse you, and you have 90 days to get it!)<br>• This is a high-earning, consistent-mileage opportunity with a strong support system and predictable home time<br>________________________________________<br>Job Details<br>Join the Quad Graphics dedicated fleet and enjoy steady miles and biweekly home time!<br>You’ll run no-touch, dry van freight including paper products and occasional ink loads.<br>• Average of $1325 per week<br>• Out 2 weeks, home 2 days<br>• All shift types – days, nights, and weekends<br>• Runs stay east of I-35<br>________________________________________<br>Key Requirements<br>• Must be available 11 out of 14 days<br>• Willing to get a tanker endorsement within 90 days (we’ll cover the cost!)<br>________________________________________<br>Benefits<br>• Paid vacation:<br>o 1 week after 1 year<br>o 3 weeks after 3 years<br><br>________________________________________<br>Experience-Based Pay<br>• 0–1 year: $0.57 CPM<br>• 13 months–2 years: $0.58 CPM<br>• 25 months- 5 years: $0.59 CPM<br>•5+ years: $0.60 CPM<br><br>• Stop Pay $15 after 1st stop<br>• Layover pay: $100 after 24 hours<br>• Detention pay: $12.50/hour after 4 hours<br><br>• Average Gross: $1,325/week — over $68,000/year!<br>• Sign-On Bonus (SOB): $1000 total ($500 after the first load, $500 after 30 days) must be active and seated at the time of bonus payout to qualify.<br><br>Bonus Eligibility<br>1. U.S. Xpress reserves the right to modify or cancel the Sign-on bonus at any time with appropriate notice under applicable law.<br>2. Nothing in this [Sign-on Bonus changes the at-will nature of your employment, meaning you and U.S. Xpress may terminate the employment relationship at any time, with or without cause.<br>3. You must be an active company driver on the day the bonus is paid.________________________________________<br><br><br>• Tagging<br>Orientation Site - Ellenwood<br>Job: Dedicated OTR DRIVER DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: OTR<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Quad Graphics<br>SIGN ON BONUS: Y/N<br>Company: US Xpress 01<br>Updated 7.15.25]]></description>
