      <Placemark>
        <name><![CDATA[Closed Floor & Decor GA-Must live within 30 miles of Bloomingdale, GA. Home Daily! Personal Transportation Required to and from DC Daily. ]]></name>
        <description><![CDATA[Restrictions<br>• Must live within 30 miles of Bloomingdale, GA<br>• Minimum 3 months of CDL-A experience<br>• Personal transportation required to and from the Distribution Center (DC)<br>• Cannot take truck home<br>• Must be able to work nights, weekends, and holidays<br>________________________________________<br>Job Details<br>• Home Daily with Saturday as the main day off<br>o Due to the length of haul, exceptions may occur in the case of major delays.<br>• Night shifts starting between 3:00 PM–6:00 PM or 10:00 PM–Midnight<br>• 12–14 hour shifts, utilizing full Hours of Service<br>• Dry Van freight, preloaded at DC with live unload at Floor & Decor stores<br>• Average 500-mile routes delivering to Atlanta and surrounding areas<br>• No touch freight<br>• Day Cabs only<br>• Average $1350 weekly for drivers who run 2150 miles and 4-5 loads per week<br><br>________________________________________<br>Key Requirements<br>• 3+ months CDL-A experience<br>• Reliable transportation to the DC each week<br>• Able to commit to 2400 miles and 4–5 loads per week<br>________________________________________<br>Benefits<br>• Home daily<br>• Paid orientation – $100 for 1-day classroom training<br>• Vacation Time:<br>o 1 week after 1 year<br>o 2 weeks after 3 years<br>o 3 weeks after 7 years<br>o 4 weeks after 10 years<br>• Experienced support staff<br>________________________________________<br>Pay Structure<br>• $0.56 per mile <br>• Annual earnings up to $70,000<br><br>• Tagging<br>Orientation Site - Jacksonville<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Local<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Floor & Décor GA<br>SIGN ON BONUS: Y/N<br>Orientation Site: Closest Terminal<br>Company: US Xpress 01<br>Updated 4.24.25]]></description>
