      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED - Whirlpool McDonough (NC/OH) HOME WEEKLY! $1100 true up!! Need 2 drivers within 50 miles of Findlay, OH</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Account key selling points:<br>True-Up Pay: Drivers can earn $1100 weekly with true-up pay on this account. To be eligible, the driver must be available for the full week and have no service failures.<br>Home Weekly: Drivers on this account are home weekly. Drivers will get a 34-hour reset at home.<br>Consistent Cargo: Drivers haul production loads between NC-OH-NC or OH-NC-OH pending where the driver is domiciled.<br><br>Additional account details:<br>• Miles: Drivers on this account average 2400 to 2600 miles per week. Difference is based on picking up in Gastonia or Kinston, NC. Drivers are expected to run 2-loops per week minimum.<br>• On-time delivery: This freight is time sensitive, so on-time delivery is a must for this account.<br>• Availability requirements: Drivers on the Whirlpool McDonough account are expected to be available the full week to meet the customer’s needs. Your reset will happen on Friday, Saturday, or Sunday depending on the week’s deliveries. No set schedule.<br>• Regional, round-trip freight: Drivers will be expected to be on the road the full week prior to doing their 34-hour reset.<br>• If for any reason there may be low volume over the course of the week running the production loops, a driver may be moved into GA to deliver a load of finished goods back into the North Carolina market. Will travel in: GA, NC, OH, SC, VA, W.VA.<br>• Freight includes a mix of drop & hook and live unloads. Pay scale based on verified experience:<br>Verified Months of Experience CPM<br>0-6 $0.46<br>7-12 $0.47<br>12-23 $0.48<br>24-35 $0.49<br>36-47 $0.50<br>48-60 $0.51<br>61-72 $0.52<br>73-84 $0.53<br>85-96 $0.54<br>97+ $0.55<br><br>• TAGGING Orientation Site - Springfield<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Whirlpool GA                    Updated 4.15.25]]></description>
