      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED Whirlpool Bridgeton MO (TN/Tulsa) $1000 SIGN ON BONUS. 50 miles of Nashville/Smyrna TN. Need 4 drivers!</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Home Weekly: Drivers on this account are home weekly. 34-hour reset once per week.<br>Consistent Cargo: Main Freight Whirlpool production loads running between Tennessee and Oklahoma (Tulsa) with some returning freight back into Tennessee to reposition the driver.<br><br>Additional account details:<br>• Miles: Drivers on this account average 2000-2200 miles per week<br>• On-time delivery: This freight is time sensitive, on-time delivery is a must for this account.<br>• Availability requirements: Drivers on the Whirlpool Bridgeton account are expected to be available the full week to meet the customer’s needs. Your reset will happen on Friday/Saturday/Sunday depending on our customer’s weekly schedule.<br>• No set schedule: The customer’s needs for this account do not allow for a set schedule.<br>• Regional, round-trip freight: This is a regional account where drivers are expected to run the full week prior to going home for their reset. Pending on weekly freight volumes, drivers may also be utilized to pick up loads in Bridgeton, MO or McDonough, GA and deliver finished goods back into Tennessee to position for freight back into Tulsa, OK.<br>• Additional states a driver may travel in: AL, AR, FL(Pan Handle), GA, IL, KA, KY, MO, MS, TN.<br>• Freight includes a mix of drop & hook and live unloads.<br><br><br>PayScale Based On Verified Experience<br>0- 6 $0.58<br>7- 12 $0.59<br>12- 23 $0.60<br>24- 35 $0.61<br>36- 47 $0.62<br>48- 60 $0.63<br>61- 72 $0.64<br>73- 84 $0.65<br>85- 96 $0.66<br>97+ $0.67<br>$20 additional stop pay<br>$50 driver assist<br>• Sign-On Bonus (SOB): $1000 total ($500 after the first load, $500 after 30 days) must be active and seated at the time of bonus payout to qualify.<br><br>Bonus Eligibility<br>1. U.S. Xpress reserves the right to modify or cancel the Sign-on bonus at any time with appropriate notice under applicable law.<br>2. Nothing in this [Sign-on Bonus changes the at-will nature of your employment, meaning you and U.S. Xpress may terminate the employment relationship at any time, with or without cause.<br>3. You must be an active company driver on the day the bonus is paid.<br><br>• TAGGING Orientation Site - Chicago<br>Job: Dedicated OTR driver DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Whirlpool Bridgeton<br>SIGN ON BONUS: Y/N Orientation Site: Closest Terminal]]></description>
