      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED Whirlpool - 50 miles McDonough GA Drivers . HOME WEEKLY! $1100 true up!! </name>
        <description><![CDATA[Account key selling points:<br>True-Up Pay: Drivers can earn $1100 weekly with true-up pay on this account. To be eligible, the driver must be available for the full week and have no service failures.<br>Drive at Night: Night Driving is a requirement. Drivers will pick up their loads between 6 p.m. to 4 a.m. and drive overnight to meet morning delivery times.<br>Home Weekly: Drivers on this account are home weekly.<br>Consistent Cargo: Drivers haul finished appliances from GA to distribution centers in AL, TN, NC, FL, and GA. Additionally, driver will be delivering production loads for Whirlpool into OH and OK.<br><br>Additional account details:<br>• Miles: Drivers on this account average 2000 miles per week<br>• On-time delivery: This freight is time sensitive, so on-time delivery is a must for this account.<br>• Availability requirements: Drivers on the Whirlpool McDonough account are expected to be available the full week to meet the customer’s needs. Your reset will happen on Friday or Saturday depending on the week’s deliveries.<br>• No set schedule: The customer’s needs for this account do not allow for a set schedule.<br>• Regional, round-trip freight: This is a regional account where drivers are on the road at least 2-3 days at a time., and average 5 round-trip loads per week. While it’s possible that drivers may get home during the week, it’s not guaranteed.<br>• Freight includes a mix of drop & hook, live unloads and driver assist (less than 10% and mostly pallet jacking).<br><br>Pay scale based on verified experience:<br>Verified Months of Experience CPM<br>0-6 $0.46<br>7-12 $0.47<br>12-23 $0.48<br>24-35 $0.49<br>36-47 $0.50<br>48-60 $0.51<br>61-72 $0.52<br>73-84 $0.53<br>85-96 $0.54<br>97+ $0.55<br><br><br>• TAGGING Orientation Site - Ellenwood<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Whirlpool GA Updated 3.6.25]]></description>
