      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED FD Morehead KY $1000 SOB!!! - 3 mos exp. Home Weekly for a 34 hour reset! New hires assigned to tractors AFTER completing 1 week ride along time with current driver at $150 per day. Drivers WILL seat a truck with a current FD Driver</name>
        <description><![CDATA[**Cannot hire drivers CURRENTLY RUNNING THE ACCOUNT FROM: without going to another carrier first—<br>• Werner<br>• USA Truck (DB Schenker)<br><br>**If a driver is running another lane for these carriers or OTR for these carriers, they are good to hire*<br>Key Facts<br>Freight: 100% touch freight, live unload at Family Dollar store, box by box with rollers.<br>*Patience with Customer/Customer Service Skills Required*<br>*Not home daily or every weekend*<br><br>Key Selling Points<br>*Pay Package for the area is industry-leading*<br>*Drivers who run 1500 miles and 3 number of loads make an average of $1750 weekly*<br>*Tenured staff to support you*<br>*Minimum Home Weekly*<br>https://vimeo.com/507100528/da4b42c25c   <br>https://vimeo.com/669499314   <br><br>FAQ<br>*How hard is the driver unload?<br>It is a challenging hard job but is very financially rewarding and great exercise, it can take some time to acclimate to the unload. This is a very strenuous account with most trailers having more than 2500 cases. We will support you thought the whole process!<br>*What States do I deliver to<br>AL, GA, IN, IL, KY, NC, OH, SC, TN, VA, WV<br>*How much money will I make?<br>Drivers who run 1500 miles and 3 number of loads make an average of $1700 weekly<br>*When is my home time and 34 hour reset?<br>We get you home weekly<br>*What shift will I work?<br>With most FD deliveries starting in the early AM you will either be driving to your first stop the night before and taking a reset or driving in the early morning to make on tire delivery. From there you will deliver throughout the day to multiple FD stores. Our normal delivery days are Monday through Saturday.<br>*When can I take a Vacation?<br>After 1 year you will get 1 weeks vacation and after 2 years, you can take 2 weeks of vacation. And after 7 years, 3 weeks. This totals up to 4 weeks at 10 years!<br>*What kind of truck will I get?<br>Our fleet is comprised of Internationals, Freightliners and Kenworths<br>*What is a True-Up? How do I qualify for the True-Up?<br>Work as directed, be on-time, and be available for Dispatch as long as hours of service permits. Our normal delivery days are Monday through Saturday.<br><br>• Regional, Home Weekly for 34 Reset.<br>• Touch Freight: Yes,using rollers<br>• True Up pay of $1700 (after training) if available, no service issues, no time off<br>• Top Weekly Pay: $2300<br>• Pay Type: Mileage, unload pay and stop pay<br><br>As part of the Family Dollar Dedicated team, you’ll run dry touch freight to various Family Dollar locations in AL, GA, IN, IL, KY, NC, OH, SC, TN, VA, WV. All of the freight will be live unloaded at Family Dollar stores.<br><br>This account with Family Dollar is unique. It’s hard work and extremely physical. Unloading your truck lets you get the exercise that you need to stay healthy. too.<br><br>Runs will include nights, weekends, and holidays that fall within your workweek. Routes also typically require 3-7 stops on each load with the expectation of 3 loads per week. We do get you home for a 34-hour break each week. Our normal delivery days are Monday through Saturday.<br><br>If you choose to join the team, you’ll go through a short orientation to help get you started on the right foot. And you’ll get paid to do it. Then you’ll complete shadow training at $150 per day. The shadow training will get you ready to unload Family Dollar trailers on your own.<br><br><br>• Payscale Based On Verified Experience<br>0 Months $0.49<br>6 months $0.50<br>12 months $0.51<br>18 months $0.52<br>24 months $0.53<br>36 months $0.55<br>48 months $0.57<br>60 months $0.59<br>72 months $0.61<br>84 months $0.63<br>96 months $0.65<br>108 months $0.67<br>120 months $0.69<br><br>• Unload Pay $245<br>• Stop Pay $25.00<br>• Backhaul Pay $50<br>• $1700 weekly True Up if requirements are met (after training)<br>*SOB Pays $500 first load, $500 at 30 days**must be active and seated to qualify for the payout<br><br>• Tagging<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>Dedicated Domicile- Family Dollar Morehead<br>SIGN ON BONUS: Y/N<br>Company: US Xpress 01]]></description>
