      <Placemark>
        <name><![CDATA[CLOSED UPS TEAM- $1000 SIGN ON BONUS PER DRIVER! 3 mos exp required. 75 miles of Louisville KY Home weekly HAZMAT REQUIRED (if you have a team without hazmat please reach out to Sarah). WILL REIMBURSE FOR ENDORSEMENT. $1700 per week Need 1 TEAMS- please email driver placement & Team Rec when you have a team booked for this account. ]]></name>
        <description><![CDATA[Account key selling points<br>• Weekly minimum of $1700 if you are available for 6 days out of the week<br>• Hazmat is required, and the drivers will be pulling Linehaul LTL freight (no touch).<br>• Drivers will pick up Sunday evening from Louisville, KY and final Saturday afternoon in Louisville, KY<br><br>Additional account details<br>• One Team lane is from Louisville, KY-Cheektowaga,NY-Coraopolis, PA-Louisville, KY<br>•Total Miles = 3280 per week<br><br><br>Pay breakdown<br>Weekly minimum of $1700 per week per driver<br>• Sign-On Bonus (SOB): $1000 total ($500 after the first load, $500 after 30 days) must be active and seated at the time of bonus payout to qualify.<br><br>Bonus Eligibility<br>1. U.S. Xpress reserves the right to modify or cancel the Sign-on bonus at any time with appropriate notice under applicable law.<br>2. Nothing in this [Sign-on Bonus changes the at-will nature of your employment, meaning you and U.S. Xpress may terminate the employment relationship at any time, with or without cause.<br>3. You must be an active company driver on the day the bonus is paid.<br><br>• Tagging<br>Job: Dedicated OTR DRIVER<br>Solo/Team: TEAM<br>Area: REGIONAL<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: UPS LOUISVILLE KY Team Partner<br>Team Bonus<br>Pre-made Team                         ]]></description>
