      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED Formica SOLO - 100 miles Pittston PA HOME WEEKLY - EXP drivers ONLY NEED 2 DRIVERS!! EMAIL DRIVER PLACEMENT WHEN YOU HAVE A DRIVER SCHEDULED FOR THIS ACCOUNT</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Key Facts:<br>*Northeast congestion*<br><br>Key Selling Points:<br>*Home Weekly*<br>*Home Weekends*<br>*3 Loads per Week*<br>*Tenured staff to support you*<br>*Average $1050 gross weekly<br><br>FAQs:<br>* What will I be delivering?<br>Formica is a laminate company for countertops and cabinets. You will be delivering laminate and laminate products between Formica distribution centers and to their customers.<br>* Is it an unload account?<br>No. All live unloads on the Formica account will be unloaded by the personnel at the stores via forklift. Typical unload times will be 30 minutes or less.<br>* What days and shift will I work?<br>Formica is open Monday-Friday and will most of their customers are open from 07:00-16:00 so store deliveries must be made between these times.<br><br>If you live within 100 miles of Pittston, PA, you could be the perfect dedicated driver to add to our Formica team! Some of the best parts of being a dedicated driver are getting home WEEKLY and driving an average of 1700 miles per week. That’s around $1050 every week and up to $55k annually. In addition to mileage pay, you’ll earn $50 per load and $10 per stop (6-9 stops per week).<br><br>As part of the Formica dedicated team, you’ll run DRY, NO-TOUCH freight to PA, NJ, & MA. 100% of freight will be live unloaded.<br><br>Runs will include Monday through Friday and home every weekend with the possibility of being home a couple days through the week. Routes also typically require 6-9 stops per week.<br><br>But being a dedicated driver is no easy task. So, the way we see it, you deserve vacation time more than anyone. That’s why after a year on the account, you can take a week of paid vacation. After 1 year, you can take 1 week of vacation. And after 3 years, 2 weeks.<br><br><br>• Payscale Based On Verified Experience<br>$.48 per mile<br>$50 per load<br>$10 per stop<br><br><br>• Tagging:<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Formica Mt Beth]]></description>
