        <description><![CDATA[FREIGHTLINER LEASE INFO:<br>https://tinyurl.com/46c7nc7c<br>INTERNATIONAL LEASE INFO<br>https://tinyurl.com/yrhsfecz<br><br><br>Account key selling points<br>• This account operates in KY,VA,WV,OH,IN,TN, AL, GA, NC and SC.<br>• Drivers will get a full 34 hour reset based on the needs of the customer and delivery days and market<br>• Drivers can expect to average $2,150 per week gross, $103,000 annually and top earners can make $2,400 per week gross.<br><br>Additional account details<br>• Each driver can average 1175 miles per week and expect to pull at least 3 loads per week.<br>• Each load is multi stop and can have as many as 4 stops per trailer and loaded with average of 2900 pieces total load and is 100% driver touch unload.<br><br>Operational Support<br>• Industry leading driver training program<br>• Experienced Office Staff<br>• Tight Backing Areas<br>• Experience All Four Seasons<br>• Steady work<br>• Positive work environment<br><br><br><br>Pay breakdown<br>• IC/LP Drivers<br>$1.06 per mile + fuel surcharge<br>$275 unload pay<br>$40 backhaul<br><br><br><br><br><br>Tagging<br>IC Job: First Seat Driver (FSD)<br>Solo/Team: solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: FD Morehead<br>FD Morehead Location: Georgia<br>SIGN ON BONUS: N<br>LEASE EQUIPMENT TYPE:<br>Company: US Xpress 01]]></description>
