      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED Formica SOLO driver - Home weekly -OFF WEEKENDS - 100 miles of Indianapolis IN (ZIP 46140)- 3 mos experience. ONLY NEED 1 DRIVER PLEASE EMAIL DRIVER PLACEMENT WHEN A DRIVER IS BOOKED</name>
        <description><![CDATA[* Must live within 100 miles of Indianapolis.<br>* Monday-Friday. Typically Start around 05:00-06:30. Days are 10-12 hours *Average 1900 miles per week and 10 stops per week. <br>* Average pay is $1,000-$1,100 per week * Drivers are delivering laminate and counter top products to wood working shops in IN, OH, WI, and MN. No touch freight. All material will be unloaded via forklift by the personnel at the delivery locations. *Assigned Sleeper <br>* Pay Scale: .47 per mile $10 Per stop<br><br><br>• TAGGING<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver<br>Solo/Team: solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Formica IN ]]></description>
