      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED Kroger - Woodlawn  HOME DAILY!! Must live within 50 miles of Woodlawn (ZIP 45215) 3 mos exp required.</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Account key selling points<br>• Home daily with 2 days off per week.<br>• Average weekly pay $1350 <br>• You will pick up and deliver from various grocery DCs in the region (IN, OH and KY), mainly OH.<br>*Runs will include nights, weekends, and holidays that fall within your workweek. The week before a holiday is also mandatory*<br>Additional account details<br>• Schedule Info: Start time will be either 11am or noon depending on availability. 2 full non-weekend days off.<br>• All new drivers should expect to work weekends<br><br>• For Woodlawn, dry van trailers utilized, 80% drop and hook and 20% unloaded from trailer into back room of stores using electric pallet jacks. (Single stop loads are drop and hook / Multi stop loads are partial unloads where the stops are off loaded by the driver and the last stop of the load is Drop and Hook)<br>• Woodlawn will operate seven days a week, mainly during the afternoon-evening hours, and drivers start times are assigned and vary<br>• Drivers are required to shift between site locations from time to time to haul either reefer or dry van freight<br>drivers average 3 – 5 loads per day with an average of 5 – 7 stops and around 200 – 300 miles a day.<br>• Drivers are averaging 1000 – 1500 Miles per week.<br>• Drivers will be home most days, and will slip seat day cab trucks.<br>• Paid vacation is also included and start after the first year on account. Vacation will payout based on drivers 52 week average<br><br>To give you the best possible driving experience, the distribution center includes on-site staff during working hours and a safety representative.<br><br>Runs will include nights, weekends, and holidays that fall within your workweek<br><br>If you choose to join the team, you’ll go through a short training to help get you started on the right foot. And you’ll get paid to do it. You’ll do 2 days of ride-along training at $100 per day.<br><br>• Payscale Based On Verified Experience<br>0 Months 0.56<br>6 Months 0.57<br>1 Years 0.58<br>2 Years 0.59<br>3 Years 0.60<br>4 years .61<br>5+ years .62<br><br>$37 unload<br>$20.00 Stop<br>Backhaul $20<br>Ride along, trainer $50<br>Ride along, trainee $100<br>Recovery, mileage<br>Pallet restack $25.00<br>Clean inspection $25<br><br><br>Vacation<br>1 Year – 1 Week<br>3 Years – 2 Weeks<br>7 Years – 3 Weeks<br>15 Years – 4 Weeks <br><br>Tagging<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Local<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Kroger Woodlawn       ]]></description>
