            -84.1096745,40.7431599,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED Family Dollar Front Royal--DOUBLES DRIVERS. Please schedule ORT. in ATL for Doubles Class. New hires assigned to tractors AFTER completing 1 week ride along time with current driver at $150 per day (Training will last up to 5 days).  </name>
        <description><![CDATA[**If you live withing the Philadelphia, Pittsburg or Front Royal VA area, there may be an opportunity for more home time in addition to the 34 hour reset.<br><br>Key Facts<br>*Driver Manual Unload*<br>*Patience with Customer/Customer Service Skills Required*<br>*Hard backing*<br><br>Key Selling Points<br><br>*Industry-leading pay package for the area*<br>*Drivers who run 1500 miles and 3 loads to make an average of $1725 weekly*<br>*Top 10% Making $2,800*<br>*Tenured staff to support you*<br>*Weekly home time for 34 hour reset<br>https://vimeo.com/507100528/da4b42c25c       <br>https://vimeo.com/669499314 <br><br>If you live within our hiring area, you could be the perfect dedicated driver to add to our Family Dollar team! Some of the best parts of being a dedicated driver are getting home for a 34 hour reset each week, and driving an average of 1500 miles per week. In addition to mileage pay, you’ll earn $250 to unload all 48-53’ Family Dollar trailers and $125 per pup trailer plus doubles pay of $35 per set. As a bonus, you will receive $125 weekly, for the required three unloads. That’s around $1,725 per week every week and up to $126,000 annually.<br><br>As part of the Family Dollar dedicated team, you’ll run Family Dollar freight to various stores and hand unloading the trailer. A trailer can have anywhere between 1 -6 stops. Our delivery area includes VA, NC, DC, PA, NJ, MD, DE and WV – all within 700 miles of the Front Royal, VA distribution center. 100% of freight will be hand unloaded at Family Dollar stores.<br><br>To give you the best possible driving experience, the distribution center includes on-site staff and customer personnel. As well as 24/7 fleet coverage.<br><br>Runs will include nights, weekends, and holidays that fall within your workweek. We require a min of 3 loads a week.<br><br>But being a dedicated driver is no easy task. So, the way we see it, you deserve vacation time more than anyone. That’s why after a year on the account, you can take a week of paid vacation. After 2 years, you can take 2 weeks of vacation. And after 7 years, 3 weeks.<br><br>If you choose to join the team, you’ll go through a short orientation to help get you started on the right foot. And you’ll get paid to do it. You’ll attend at least 2 full shadow runs, to learn the unload process. This pays $150 per day.<br><br>• Payscale:<br>0 .60<br>12 .61<br>24 .63<br>36 .65<br>48 .70<br>60 .71<br>84 .72<br>120+ .73<br>Unload $125 per pup<br>Plus Doubles pay of $35 per set.<br><br>Account is offering an extra $125 weekly incentive as long as driver is avail for full work week!<br>Backhaul $35<br><br>• Tagging<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver – DLC<br>Orientation Site: Ellenwood USX Terminal<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>Dedicated Domicile- Family Dollar Front Royal<br>PST/EFA: Required<br>SIGN ON BONUS: Y/N]]></description>
