      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED Penske Dana Lima (Huber Heights)- 1 local driver needed 50 miles from Huber Heights, OH- NEED 1 driver please email driver placement when you have a driver booked!</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Key Facts:<br>*Customer wait times at loading*<br><br>Lane 2:<br>Schedule: Monday-Friday; 06:00 start time; 10-12 hours per day with 14-hour day possible; Home Daily<br>Pay: $250 per day; $1,250 per week<br>Location: Driver must live within 50 miles of Huber Heights, OH<br>Details: Mix of drop and hook and live load/live unload. Will be delivering to Springfield, OH and Lima, OH; ~300 miles per day; Will be assigned a day cab to use<br><br>Key Selling Points:<br>*Assigned a day cab to use every day*<br>*Weekly Salary*<br>*Home Daily & Weekends*<br>*Tenured staff to support you*<br>*Road Ready Promise*<br><br><br>If you live within 50 miles of Huber Heights, OH, you could be the perfect dedicated driver to add to our Dana Penske team! Some of the best parts of being a dedicated driver are getting home DAILY and on the WEEKENDS.<br>As part of the Dana Penske dedicated team, you’ll run car parts to various locations in IN, OH, & MI. 100% of freight will be live unloaded.<br><br><br>But being a dedicated driver is no easy task. So, the way we see it, you deserve vacation time more than anyone. That’s why after a year on the account, you can take a week of paid vacation. After 1 year, you can take 1 week of vacation. And after 3 years, 2 weeks.<br><br>If you choose to join the team, you’ll go through a short training to help get you started on the right foot. And you’ll get paid to do it. You’ll receive 1 day of ride-along training at $100 per day.<br><br><br><br>FAQs:<br>* What will I be delivering?<br>You will be delivering car parts for Dana to different locations in IN, OH, and MI. You will sometimes be asked to pick up parts from different locations and bring them back to the Dana plant in Lima.<br>* What days will I be working?<br>Dana runs Monday-Friday and are closed for all major holidays.<br>* Is there any way to make more money?<br>You can always work on one of your off days at one of our sister grocery sites to make extra money. The same goes for when the Dana plant is closed for a holiday. You can work at one of our sister grocery sites on the holidays since they will be open and have loads available.<br>* Where do I find an empty trailer if mine was taken overnight?<br>If you come in to work and find that your trailer was taken overnight, there are a few places you can find empty USX trailers. One is at the trailer shop down the street in Lima. We also have trailers at the P&G plant in Lima that we can check on as well. The third location we usually have trailers is the Lowe’s DC in Findlay, OH.<br><br>Pay Breakdown:<br>Flat daily pay of $250<br>10-12 hour days. Start time 0600<br>Driver will drive a day cab<br><br><br>• Tagging<br>Job: Local Driver<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Local<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Penske Dana<br>Sign on Bonus: Y/N]]></description>
