      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED OTR Team Sponsorship-COMPANY DRIVERS ONLY</name>
        <description><![CDATA[OTR Team Sponsorship-COMPANY DRIVERS ONLY<br>Who?<br>• Any person who is a current CDL holder and meets our current hiring guidelines.<br>o Can also be a current USX driver and bring on a student to “sponsor train” as long as they agree to team once training is complete.<br>• Must also meet our current standards to become a certified driver trainer.<br>• Please reach out to Khristyal Bradford for approval of T3 Class & Dates for trainer.<br>• Must also have a friend/relative that has completed driving school and will be team partner.<br>• Experienced driver’s orientation will need to be a Wed class, student’s orientation will need to be following Monday. CAN ONLY BE SCHEDULED FOR THL<br>• Experienced driver’s employment history must be Pre-Verified with a minimum total of 12 months experience<br>• Both drivers must agree to team for 6 months, once the 175 BTW hour training is complete.<br>Bonus Structure Payout?<br>• Once 175 BTW training hours are complete, and the student is now a First Seat Driver, the team may elect 1 of 2 Sign on Bonus plans:<br>o $12k Bonus – payout will start immediately, post upgrade<br>o $15k Bonus – payout will start once the team has reached 6 months employment with USX. (must still be in team status with each other). Payout is over a 24-month period.<br><br>**IC/LP teams are NOT included**<br><br>Experienced Driver Payscale paid for ALL truck Miles<br>PayScale:<br>56cpm<br><br>**IF THE CURRENT DRIVER IS DEDICATED, PLEASE MAKE SURE TO INCLUDE DRIVER PLACEMENT ON THE EMAIL.<br><br>**CLICK LINK BELOW FOR TEAMS SCRIPT & PAY FOR UPGRADED TEAM**<br>https://tinyurl.com/492kxv9z                                                                   <br>*Tag both Exp. & Students w/team tag*  CAN ONLY BE SCHEDULED FOR THL<br>• Tagging<br>Job: First Seat Driver/Driver Trainee<br>Solo/Team: Team<br>Area: OTR<br>Acct: OTR<br>Region: All<br>Dedicated Domicile: THL<br>Team Partner<br>Pre-made Team<br>Sponsorship Required: YES]]></description>
