      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED Kroger Woodlawn YARD JOCKEY—must live within 40 miles of Woodlawn, OH and have personal transportation to and from the yard daily. Position starts 2/4/24. Available to start orientations week 1/17/24.  7 per week</name>
        <description><![CDATA[**Position starts 2/4/24. Available to start orientations week 1/17/24**<br><br>Working at Kroger Woodlawn, OH – shuttling empty/loaded trailers around the yard as well as to and from dock doors with a yard jockey tractor. (USX Leased tractor / Kroger vans) Home daily.<br>- Safely and efficiently operate yard hostler equipment to move trailers and containers within the yard<br>- Perform pre-trip and post-trip inspections of the hostler equipment<br>- Communicate with dispatchers and other team members to coordinate the movement of trailers and containers<br>- Ensure that all trailers and containers are properly secured before transport<br>- Maintain accurate records of trailer and container movements<br><br>HOURS:<br>* Friday-Sunday<br>36 hours per week: Morning and Overnight Night shift available (Overnight: 5pm-5am or 6pm to 6am to be assigned by TM) <br>Average weekly pay $790-$936 per week depending on verified experience.<br><br><br>*Pay Breakdown:<br>Less than 24 months- $22 per hour<br>24+ Months- $26 per hour<br>Anything over 40 hours per week paid at overtime rate.<br><br>• Tagging<br>Job: Dedicated Local Yard Driver<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: LOCAL<br>Acct: Yard Driver<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Kroger Woodlawn<br>PST: Not Required<br>Shift Time: Morning, Mid, Afternoon, Overnight<br>Shift Days: Monday-Thursday or Friday-Sunday]]></description>
