      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED OTR COMPANY DRIVERS ONLY. CHICAGO BASED 18-3</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Key selling points:<br>• Out 18 days, home 3 full days<br>• OTR all 48 states – majority of freight is East of I-35 but we go where the freight goes<br>• Drivers average 2200+ miles per week<br>• ALL no touch freight<br>• 50-60% drop & hook<br>• 40-50% Live Unload<br>• No forced dispatch into NYC or its 5 boroughs<br><br>Additional details:<br>• 2021 or newer Cascadia Freightliners or KW’s<br>• Average length of haul is over 600 miles<br>• Operations specialist you can talk with whenever you need 24/7<br>• All shifts are empowered for your needs<br><br>Vacation Package<br>• 1 year = 1 week<br>• 3 years = 2 weeks<br>• 7 years = 3 weeks<br>• 15 years = 4 weeks<br><br>Click link for payscale: http://tinyurl.com/nwrr2sf4<br>• Detention Pay $12.50 per hour after 2nd hour<br>• Layover Pay/Breakdown Pay $100 per day Mileage bonus 3 CPM based on Safety, Mileage, & Productivity. Eligible on the 1st of the month following your hire date <br>*Tagging*<br>Orientation Site: Dallas<br>Job: First Seat Driver<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: OTR<br>Acct: OTR<br>Region: All<br>Dedicated Domicile: Chicago]]></description>
