      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED Dana Dry Ridge- Drivers must live within 50 miles of Dry Ridge, KY Home Daily. Need 2 Drivers. Please email driver placement when you have one on the schedule. Must have personal transportation to and from the DC daily</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Key Facts<br>*Night/weekend driving*<br><br>Key Selling Points:<br>*Pay Package is industry-leading*<br>*Home Daily*<br>*Tenured staff to support you*<br>*5-day work week w/2 days off (may not be the weekend)*<br>*Opportunity to help other surrounding accounts when plant is shut down*<br><br><br>FAQs:<br>1.	What will I be delivering and where will I deliver to?<br>You will be delivering truck axels to Jeffersonville, IN. <br>2.	What is required to qualify for load cancelation pay?<br>You must be available for your normal shift 5 days a week. You also must be available to run a second load even if you are only scheduled for 1 load. If a load is canceled, you must be available to run at our Kroger site if they need assistance, if no assistance is needed a load cancellation pay will be paid to the driver. If plant is shutdown you will need to call in to see if you are needed at Kroger to work while the plant is shut down.<br>3.	Are there any opportunities to make more money?<br>Yes. We are always using drivers to fill in for drivers who are off. If you are wanting to work one of your off days, just let us know and we will get you on the schedule if we have an opening. In addition, if we don’t have any work for you at Dry Ridge, we can always reach out to our sister site at Kroger to see if they need help and you can work there for the day.<br>4.	Can I change shifts?<br>If you are wanting to change shifts just let us know that you would like a different shift and we will get you on the waiting list. If we have a driver leave and have an opening, then we will start at the top of the list and work out way down to determine who wants the open spot.<br><br><br><br>If you live within 50 miles of Dry Ridge, KY, you could be the perfect dedicated driver to add to our Dana team! Some of the best parts of being a dedicated driver are getting home DAILY, and driving an average of 1900 miles per week. That’s around $1400 every week and up to $72k annually.<br> <br>As part of the Dana Dry Ridge dedicated team, you’ll run rear axle assemblies from Dry Ridge, KY, NO-TOUCH, to Jeffersonville, IN, then bring empty return racks back to the plant in Dry Ridge – all within 191 miles of the Dry Ridge distribution center. 100% of freight will be live unloaded.<br><br>Runs will include nights, weekends, and holidays that fall within your workweek. <br><br>But being a dedicated driver is no easy task. So, the way we see it, you deserve vacation time more than anyone. That’s why after a year on the account, you can take a week of paid vacation. After 3 years, you can take 2 weeks of vacation. And after 7 years, 3 weeks.<br><br>If you choose to join the team, you’ll go through a short training to help get you started on the right foot. And you’ll get paid to do it. You’ll receive 1 day of ride-along training at $100 per day.<br><br>If this sounds like a good fit for you & your career, here are a few other operational details.<br>•	Drive your personal vehicle to the plant each day. From there you will slip seat a newer model day cab or sleeper truck.<br>•	USX is responsible for 38 loads per day, and the load times vary every couple of hours throughout the day, so there will be different driver start times throughout the day/night. Plant runs 24/7.<br>•	Work schedule is based on a 5-day work week. The 2 days off per week will be the same but will depend on the time slot you are assigned.<br>•	Start time will be determined once hired. It will 100% depend on shift availability at the time of hire. We will do our best to accommodate shift preference, but it is not a guarantee.<br>•	Required to run 2 round trips per day.<br><br><br>Pay breakdown:<br>• Pay scale:<br>Pay is .73 CPM<br><br><br><br>• Tagging<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Local<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Dana Dry Ridge<br>SIGN ON BONUS: Y/N  ]]></description>
