      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED Whirlpool Bridgeton-   100 miles Bridgeton MO.   3 mos Experience drivers </name>
        <description><![CDATA[Account key selling points<br>• Drivers can earn a gross average of around $1400 or more weekly<br>• Drivers haul finished appliances from Bridgeton MO to distribution centers in TN and OK, MO, NE, OK<br>• Night Driving Required. Some routes pick up as early as 15:00pm and others can pick up as late as 2am and deliver straight through for AM deliveries.<br>• Drivers haul freight 7 days a week with resets around the weekend (not Saturday and Sunday specifically)<br><br>Additional account details<br>• Runs are still round trip<br>• We still have the loops in addition to new lanes that include, NE, KS, AR<br>• The lane was designed to deliver the freight bring the empty back and be ready for the next load<br>• Drivers are still running Sunday through Thursday with occasional weekend freight <br>• Drivers average 1800 or more miles depending on the backhaul assigned to the lane<br>• About 10% of the freight is touch freight. They must tailgate at the delivery<br><br>• Payscale Based On Verified Experience<br>0- 6 $0.58<br>7- 12 $0.59<br>12- 23 $0.60<br>24- 35 $0.61<br>36- 47 $0.62<br>48- 60 $0.63<br>61- 72 $0.64<br>73- 84 $0.65<br>85- 96 $0.66<br>97+ $0.67<br>Backhaul $20<br><br>• TAGGING<br>Job: Dedicated OTR driver DLC <br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Whirlpool Bridgeton<br> SIGN ON BONUS: Y/N                                                    Orientation Site: Closest Terminal                       ]]></description>
