      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED Bell Logistics- NEED 3 drivers - Home Weekends. Orientation must be attended in Springfield OH. Please email Driver Placement, Christina Vanhorn, and Max Bostwick if you book a driver for this fleet. </name>
        <description><![CDATA[Bell Logistics offers manual and automatic trucks.<br><br>We run the Midwest, Southeast, and parts of the Northeast. No NYC or Long Island loads.                Offer health, dental, vision, 401k, & vacation time.<br>These trucks would be running mostly USX freight but stay out regional to where the driver lives to make sure we get home on time.<br>Average 2500 miles per week <br>Average weekly pay $1300-$1400 per week <br><br>* Pay is percentage at 27% (Average .58-.59 per mile practical miles)<br><br>* Driver will be Xpress Consolidated Company 63—please reach out to Max Bostwick for details on health, dental, vision, 401k, and vacation time <br>* WORKLIST will be Independent Contractor-Agent<br><br>Tagging<br>IC Job: First Seat Driver <br>Company: Xpress Consolidated 63<br>Solo/Team: solo<br>Area: OTR<br>Acct: All accounts<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Bell Logistics<br>SIGN ON BONUS: N<br>ORIENTATION SITE: Springfield, OH]]></description>
