      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED Whirlpool Cleveland- NEED 1 Drivers. Home Daily. Must live within 50 miles of Cleveland, TN. MUST HAVE PERSONAL TRANSPORTATION. SLIP SEAT ACCOUNT.  Please email Driver Placement if you book a driver for this account.</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Key selling points<br>• Average weekly pay around $900-$1000 gross per week<br>• Driver will need to live within 40-50 miles of Cleveland, TN<br>• Slip seat—must have personal transportation to get to/from DC<br>• Home Daily<br>• Weekends off<br>Additional account details<br>Running various lanes with various start times based on need<br>Preloaded / drop and hook freight. No touch freight. This comes out to be 2700 miles a week. Home every night and off on Saturday Sunday<br><br>If you live within 50 miles of Cleveland, TN you could be the perfect dedicated driver to add to our Whirlpool team! Some of the best parts of being a dedicated driver on this account are getting home daily and being off Saturdays and Sundays. You’ll  be driving an average of 2700 miles per week. That’s around $900 – 1000 every week. <br> <br>But being a dedicated driver is no easy task. So, the way we see it, you deserve vacation time more than anyone. That’s why after a year on the account, you can take a week of paid vacation. After 2 years, you can take 2 weeks of vacation. And after 7 years, 3 weeks. This totals up to 4 weeks at 10 years!<br><br>Pay breakdown<br>Hourly Driver Pay Only- 19.00 per hour. Anything over 40 hours per week paid at overtime rate <br><br><br>• Tagging<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Local<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Whirlpool Cleveland]]></description>
