        <description><![CDATA[Account key selling points<br>• Average pay of $1050 per week after expenses<br>• TANKER ENDORSEMENT REQUIRED will have 90 days from start of account to get this if don’t have it. Tanker endorsement will be reimbursed for this account.<br>• Drivers will be running east of i35 on this account<br>• Drivers earn one day off for every 7 out, minimum 2 weeks out.<br><br>Additional account details<br>• Drivers average 2300 miles per week<br>• Drivers will run all shifts day and nights<br>• This account hauls newspaper inserts, magazines, roll stock paper and liquid ink to distribution centers east of the Mississippi river.<br>• Freight is 100% no touch.<br>• Drivers will receive a $100/wk bonus for maintaining a tanker endorsement.<br><br><br>Pay breakdown<br>• IC/LP Drivers<br><br>1.05 per mile<br><br>Stop $15.00<br>Tanker “Bonus” $100/wk<br><br><br><br>• Tagging<br>IC JOB: First Seat Driver<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: OTR<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Quad Graphics<br>Dedicated Tour Account: Quad Graphics]]></description>
