        <name>CLOSED DT Marengo OH-   Home weekly for 34 hour reset!  $2000 weekly true up! New hires assigned to tractors AFTER completing 1 week ride along time with current driver at $150 per day. Drivers must have secure parking location for truck and trailer.
</name>
        <description><![CDATA[**Cannot hire drivers running account currently or if they have departed from these carriers within the last 6 months without going to another carrier first—<br>•	USA Truck (DB Schenker)<br>•	Knight<br>                                                                                                                                                                               Key Facts<br>*Driver Manual Unload*<br>*Patience with Customer/Customer Service Skills Required*<br>*Not home daily or every weekend*<br>* $2000 weekly true up!                                             *Drivers need to have 2 weeks' worth of supplies when they arrive to orientation. Once they activate, they will be sent directly to Marengo OH to report for training.<br>                                                                                                                                                                                Key Selling Points<br>*Pay Package for the area is industry-leading*<br>*Drivers who run 3 loads make an average of $2000 weekly*<br>*Tenured staff to support you*<br>*Minimum Home Weekly*<br>https://vimeo.com/507100528/da4b42c25c<br> https://vimeo.com/669499314        <br><br>FAQ<br>*How hard is the driver unload?<br>It is a challenging hard job but is very financially rewarding and great exercise, it can take some time to acclimate to the unload. We will support you thought the whole process!<br>*What States do I deliver to<br>OH, PA, WV, IN, MI. KY <br>*How much money will I make?<br>Drivers who run 1300 miles and 3 number of loads make an average of $2000 weekly<br>When is my home time and 34 hour reset?<br>We get you home weekly<br>*What shift will I work?<br>With most DT deliveries starting in the early AM you will either be driving to your first stop the night before and taking a reset or driving in the early morning to make on tire delivery. From there you will deliver throughout the day to multiple DG stores. <br>*When can I take a Vacation?<br>After 1 year you will get 1 weeks vacation and after 2 years, you can take 2 weeks of vacation. And after 7 years, 3 weeks. This totals up to 4 weeks at 10 years!<br>*What kind of truck will I get?<br>Our fleet is comprised of Internationals, Freightliners and Kenworths<br>*What is a True-Up? How do I qualify for the True-Up? <br>Work as directed, be on-time, and be available for Dispatch M-S as long as hours of service permits.<br><br>If you live within our hiring area, you could be the perfect dedicated driver to add to our Dollar Tree Marengo team! Some of the best parts of being a dedicated driver are getting home weekly,  and driving an average of 1300 miles per week. That’s 2K every week and up to 104k annually. In addition to mileage pay, you’ll earn $240 per load inclusive for the unload at all stops and $240 for a Pup trailer.<br> <br>As part of the Dollar Tree dedicated team, you’ll run touch freight to various Dollar Tree locations in OH, PA, WV, IN, MI. KY – all within 300 miles of the Marengo distribution center. 100% of freight will be live unloaded at Dollar Tree stores.<br><br>Runs will include nights, weekends, and holidays that fall within your workweek. Routes also typically require 1-6 stops per day and potentially a 10-hour break on the road each week. <br><br>But being a dedicated driver is no easy task. So, the way we see it, you deserve vacation time more than anyone. That’s why after a year on the account, you can take a week of paid vacation. 1 week after 1 year, 2 weeks after 2 years, 3 weeks after 7 years and 4 weeks after 10 years<br><br>If you choose to join the team, you’ll go through a short orientation to help get you started on the right foot. And you’ll get paid to do it. You’ll attend 2 days of ride-along training at $150 per ride along.<br><br>• Payscale Based On Verified Experience<br>0 $0.52<br>6 $0.53<br>12 $0.54<br>18 $0.55<br>24 $0.56<br>36 $0.58<br>48 $0.60<br>60 $0.62<br>72 $0.64<br>84 $0.66<br>96 $0.68<br>108 $0.70<br>120 $0.72<br>132 $0.75<br><br>Driver Compensation<br>Unload Pay $240<br>Stop Pay $25<br>Backhaul Pay $50<br><br><br>• Tagging<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicate]]></description>
