      <Placemark>
        <name><![CDATA[CLOSED Sam's Club- Brownstown Charter Township 3 mos exp req. Drivers must live within 50 miles of Brownstowns Twp. MI LOCAL HOME DAILY - please email driver placement when you have one on the schedule. Need 1 driver!]]></name>
        <description><![CDATA[Key Facts<br>* 6 Day work weeks<br>* Weekend and holidays are regular workdays<br><br>Key Selling Points<br>* Home Daily!<br>* Preloaded/Drop and Hook freight<br>* Tenured staff to support you<br>* 34-hour resets on specific weekday<br><br>FAQ<br>* How hard is the driver unload?<br>This is a no touch freight account 100% drop and hook at Sam’s Clubs.<br>* What States do I deliver to<br>OH & MI<br>* How much money will I make?<br>Drivers do an average of 3 loads per day, 6 days per week for an estimated $1350 weekly. <br>* When is my home time and 34 hour reset?<br>Scheduled day off will be on Mondays.<br>* What shift will I work?<br>Start time will be Noon daily. No specific end time – until loads are all delivered or you start running out of HOS, whichever comes first! <br>* When can I take a Vacation?<br>After 1 year you receive 1 week of paid vacation, after 3 years you receive 2 weeks of paid vacation, and after 7 years you receive 3 weeks of paid vacation. <br>* What kind of truck will I get?<br>Our fleet is comprised of Internationals, Freightliners and Kenworths<br><br><br>If you live within 50 miles of Brownstown, MI you could be the perfect dedicated driver to add to our Sam’s team! Some of the best parts of being a dedicated driver are getting home daily and running an average of 18 local runs per week. That’s around $1350 every week and roughly $70,000 annually. In addition to local pay, you’ll earn an extra $15 per trailer move at the receivers, which adds up quickly!<br> <br>As part of the Sam’s dedicated team, you’ll run Dry, No-Touch freight to various Sam’s locations in MI and OH – all within 185 miles of the Brownstown distribution center. 100% of freight will be drop and hook at the Sam’s Clubs.<br><br>To give you the best possible driving experience, U.S. Xpress has a 24/7 support staff available to assist at all times. <br><br>Runs will include nights, weekends, and holidays that fall within your workweek. Workweek is 6 days/week with Monday as your off day.<br><br>But being a dedicated driver is no easy task. So, the way we see it, you deserve vacation time more than anyone. That’s why after a year on the account, you can take a week of paid vacation. After three years, you accrue 2 weeks of vacation, after 7 years you accrue 3 weeks of vacation and after 10 years you accrue 4 weeks of vacation yearly.<br><br>If you choose to join the team, we will pair you with an experienced company driver to get you started off on the right foot and make sure you have the necessary tools for success!<br><br>Pay Scale:<br>The loads pay $75 flat with the exception of 2 lanes which are longer lengths of hauls:<br>Brownstown MI to Columbus OH pays $200 flat<br>Brownstown MI to Port Huron MI pays $110 flat<br><br><br>Tagging:<br>Job- Dedicated OTR Driver<br>Solo or team- Solo<br>Area- Local<br>Account- dedicated<br>Ded or Dom term= Sams Brownstown MI <br>SIGN ON BONUS: N]]></description>
