      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED PetSmart Ottawa, IL. Drivers must live within 30 miles of St Louis MO  (63116). Home weekly. Average $1325 per week! </name>
        <description><![CDATA[Key Facts:<br>*Runs include nights, weekends, holidays that fall within your work week.<br>*Must live within 75 miles of Ottawa, IL or 30 miles of St Louis MO<br>*Routes require a minimum of 2 stops and a max of 4 stops per day.<br>*Average 1740 miles per week * Average 4 loads per week<br>* Store Returns – After each store delivery you are required to pick up store returns, seal the trailer, and return with seals intact to the Ottawa, IL DC. Full operation on August 1st. Driver will be used to move trailers and fill in as the previous company is moving out. Will try filling in down time with other local fleets.<br><br>Key Selling Points:<br>*Average weekly pay of $1325 per week<br>*Home weekly for 34 hour reset<br>* Dry No Touch freight delivering to stores in IL, IN, MI, MO, IA, WI. 100 % of freight will be live unloaded at PetSmart stores<br><br>If you live within miles of 75- miles of Ottawa, IL you could be the perfect dedicated driver to add to our PetSmart team!<br><br>Weekend and holiday work is expected, 34-hour reset weekly at home, but not necessarily on the weekends. Runs will include nights, weekends, and holidays that fall within your work week. Routes require a minimum of two stops and a maximum of four stops per day. Your 10-hour breaks typically occur on the road.<br><br>Average miles of 1740 with an average pay of $1325. In addition to mileage pay, you will earn $25 stop pay after the first stop with an Avg of 2 stops per week. With a minimum mile per load pay of $50. <br><br><br>As part of the PetSmart Dedicated team, you will run DRY, NO- touch freight to various PetSmart store locations. Stores are in IL, IN, MI, MO, IA, WI – all within 450 miles of the Ottawa, IL distribution center. 100 % of freight will be live unloaded at PetSmart stores. On time service is critical to the operation at pick up and at each delivery.<br><br>Store Returns – After each store delivery you are required to pick up store returns, seal the trailer, and return with seals intact to the Ottawa, IL DC.<br>Being a Dedicated driver is no easy task. So, the way we see it, you deserve vacation time more than anyone. That is why after a year on the account, you can take a week of paid vacation. After 2 years, you can take two weeks of vacation. After 7 years, you can take three weeks of vacation.<br><br>If you choose to join the team, you will go through a short orientation to help get you started on the right foot. And you will get paid to do it.<br><br>**Pay scale based on verified Experience<br>0-12 Months $0.52<br>24 Months $0.53<br>36 Months $0.54<br>48 Months $0.55<br>60 Months $0.57<br>72 Months $0.59<br>84 Months $0.61<br>96 Months $0.63<br>108 Months $0.65<br>120 Months $0.68                                                       $25 per stop after the first stop<br><br>Tagging<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Petsmart Ottawa<br>SIGN ON BONUS: Y/N]]></description>
