      <Placemark>
        <name><![CDATA[CLOSED DT Berwick, PA -  3 mos exp. Home Weekly for a 34 hour reset! $2k TRUE UP!!! Drivers need to have 2 weeks' worth of supplies when they arrive to orientation. Once they activate they will be sent directly to Berwick, PA to report for training. New hires assigned to tractors AFTER completing 1 week ride along time with current driver at $150 per day. ]]></name>
        <description><![CDATA[**Cannot hire drivers running account currently or if they have departed from these carriers within the last 6 months without going to another carrier first—<br>• Swift<br>• Werner<br><br>Job Description: Dedicated Driver for Dollar Tree with manual unload duties, delivering to various locations in PA, MD, NY, NJ, DE (no NYC), with the potential to earn up to $2000 true up per week. Drivers need to have 2 weeks' worth of supplies when they arrive to orientation. Once they activate, they will be sent directly to Berwick, PA to report for training.<br><br>Key Selling Points:<br>•	Industry-leading pay package for the area<br>•	Minimum home time weekly<br>•	Tenured staff for support<br>•	Paid vacation time<br><br>FAQ:<br>•	How hard is the driver unload? It can be challenging but financially rewarding, and we offer support throughout the process.<br>•	What states do I deliver to? PA, NY (no NYC), NJ, DE, MD.<br>•	When is my home time and 34 hour reset? It usually includes a weekend day, but it could be any day of the week due to HOS or customer needs. We get you home weekly.<br>•	What shift will I work? Most deliveries start early in the morning, and you will deliver throughout the day to multiple DT stores.<br>•	When can I take a vacation? After 1 year, you get 1 week of vacation, after 2 years, you can take 2 weeks, after 7 years, 3 weeks. After 10 years, you get 4 weeks.<br>•	What kind of truck will I get? Our fleet is comprised of Internationals, Freightliners, and Kenworths.<br>•	https://vimeo.com/507100528/da4b42c25c   <br> https://vimeo.com/669499314  <br><br>Pay:<br>•	Pay scale based on verified experience<br>• 3 months .61<br>• 6 months .62<br>• 12 months .63<br>• 24 months .64<br>• 36 months .65<br>• 48 months.66<br>• 60 months .67<br>• 72 months .68<br>• 84 months .69<br>• 96 months .70<br>• 108 months .71<br>• 120 months .72<br><br>•	Unload $240, Backhaul $80<br>•	True up of up to $2000 per week<br><br>Note:<br>•	Drivers must be available for their full workweek, and not reject any loads given to them.<br>•	Drivers must be on time to the first store for every load.<br>•	Drivers must communicate any delays to the office.<br>•	Drivers may not go home between loads without permission.<br>•	Breakdowns are handled differently depending on the reason.<br><br>• Tagging<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>Ded or Dom Term: Dollar Tree Berwick<br>PST: Required<br>SIGN ON BONUS: Y/N]]></description>
