      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED PetSmart- 100 miles Newnan, GA Drivers. NEED 3 DRIVERS!! HOME WEEKLY.  If within 50 miles should be able to get through house a couple times per week. Day and night driving. Must be able to do both. 2000 miles per week. Please email Driver Placement if you book a driver for this account. </name>
        <description><![CDATA[Key Facts<br>* Home weekly for 34 hour reset<br>* Runs include nights, weekend, and holidays<br>* Dry, no touch freight<br>* Average $1200-$1400 per week depending on Exp<br>* Average 2100 miles per week<br>* Delivers in Al, GA, FL—all within 50-650 miles of Newnan, GA<br>* 100% of freight live unloaded at stores                                                      <br>If you live within miles of 100 Newnan GA, you could be the perfect dedicated driver to add to our PetSmart team! Some of the best parts of being a dedicated driver are getting home WEEKLY and driving an average of 2100 miles per week. That’s around $1200-$ 1400 every week. In addition to mileage pay, you’ll earn $25.00 stop pay after the first stop. Avg 2-3 stop paying per week. Average 2.5 loads per week Drivers will average 2100 MPW. Guarantee 2000 miles per week (must be available to work for the guarantee) <br>.<br>If you live within 50 miles you could be able to get through the house a couple times a week. Weekend and holiday work is expected, 34-hour reset is home weekly, but not necessarily on the weekends. Runs will include nights, weekends, and holidays that fall within your workweek. Routes also typically require 2-4 stops per DAY and with a 10-hour break on the road each week. <br> <br>As part of the PetSmart dedicated team, you’ll run DRY NO- touch freight to various PetSmart store locations in AL, GA, FL – all within 50-650 miles of the Newnan, GA distribution center. 100 % of freight will be live unloaded at PetSmart stores. Pick-ups and deliveries will be 24/7 and must be picked up on time and delivered on time.<br><br>Backhauls and Store Returns – Some backhauls drop and hook or live loads and unloads. Clean dropped trailers are required. All drivers will have a backhaul or dunnage to return to Newnan, GA or the Atlanta area.<br>But being a dedicated driver is no easy task. So, the way we see it, you deserve vacation time more than anyone. That’s why after a year on the account, you can take a week of paid vacation. After 2 years, you can take 2] weeks of vacation. And after 7 years, 3 weeks.<br><br>If you choose to join the team, you’ll go through a short orientation to help get you started on the right foot. And you’ll get paid to do it. <br><br><br>• Payscale Based On Verified Experience<br>3-6 months .50<br>7-12 months .51<br>13-24 months .52<br>25-36 months .53<br>37-48 months .54<br>49-60 months .55<br>61-72 months .56<br>73-84 months .57<br>85-96 months .58<br>97- 108 months .59<br>109 months + .60<br><br>$50 backhaul pay<br>$25 stop pay after first stop. Average 3-4 paying stops per week<br><br><br>• TAGGING<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: PetSmart Newnan <br>SIGN ON BONUS: Y/N]]></description>
