      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED - Variant - OTR COMPANY DRIVERS ONLY. MUST LIVE WITHIN 20 MILES OF EL PASO, TX OR WITHIN 20 MILES OF I-20. 21 DAYS OUT 3 DAYS HOME. DALLAS BASED  DALLAS BASED (TX, OK, AZ, NM, UT, NV, CA, ID, WA, OR, MT, CO, WY)</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Key selling points:<br>• Out 21 days, home 3 days home<br>• OTR all 48 states – majority of freight is East of I-35 but we go where the freight goes<br>• Drivers average 2500+ miles per week<br>• ALL no touch freight<br>• 50-60% drop & hook<br>• 40-50% Live Unload<br>• No forced dispatch into NYC or its 5 boroughs<br><br>Additional details:<br>• 2021 or newer Cascadia Freightliners or KW’s<br>• Optimized loads plan to maximize your miles and your money<br>• Average length of haul is over 600 miles<br>• Operations specialist you can talk with whenever you need 24/7<br>• All shifts are empowered for your needs<br><br>Vacation Package<br>• 1 year = 1 week<br>• 3 years = 2 weeks<br>• 7 years = 3 weeks<br>• 15 years = 4 weeks<br><br>PayScale:<br>3 – 23 MOE: 56cpm<br>24+ MOE: 60cpm<br><br>• Detention Pay $12.50 per hour after 2nd hour<br>• Layover Pay/Breakdown Pay $100 per day EXCLUDING Sundays <br>*Tagging*<br>Orientation Site: Dallas<br>Job: Variant Driver VDR<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: OTR<br>Acct: Variant<br>Region: All<br>Dedicated Domicile: Dallas<br>South Florida: Y/N<br>PST/EFA: Not Required <br><br>For more info check out their website and/or YouTube page!<br><br>https://www.drivevariant.com/<br>https://youtu.be/ICX9hiW5r40]]></description>
