      <Placemark>
        <name><![CDATA[CLOSED DT Warrensburg, MO Lease - Mileage Pay $1.20 + FSC $275 unload ***NO IL DRIVERS*** You can expect to average $3600 per week gross, $187,000 annually while being home weekly for a 34-hour reset. 1 week ride along time with current driver at $150 per day. Must have 6 months experience in the last 3 years. LP'S DO NOT RECEIVE ORIENTATION PAY.]]></name>
        <description><![CDATA[Account key selling points <br>• This account operates in MO, AR, KS, IA,NE,CO,WY,MN,SD,ND, IN, IL, WI, TN<br>• Drivers will get a full 34 hour reset based on the needs of the customer, delivery days, and market.<br>• Drivers can expect to average $3600 per week gross, $187,000 annually <br><br>Additional account details <br>• Each driver can average 1700 miles per week and expect to pull at least 3 loads per week.<br>• Each load is multi stop and can have as many as 4 stops per trailer and loaded with average of 3500 pieces total load and is 100% driver touch unload.<br><br>Operational Support<br>• Industry leading driver training program<br>• Experienced Office Staff<br>• Tight Backing Areas<br>• Experience All Four Seasons<br>• Steady work<br>• Positive work environment<br><br><br><br>Pay breakdown <br>• IC/LP Drivers<br>$1.20 per mile + fuel surcharge<br>$275 unload pay<br>$25 stop pay<br>$50 backhaul<br><br><br><br>• Tagging<br>IC JOB: First Seat Driver<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: DT Warrensburg                             PST/EFA: Required                                                     Orientation Site: Closest Terminal]]></description>
