        <name>CLOSED Michaels Jacksonville FL -3 mos exp req, home weekly for 34 hour reset. MUST LIVE WITHIN 75 MILES OF JACKSONVILLE, FL (ZIP 32201)  $1100 Weekly Minimum!! NEED 2 DRIVERS. PLEASE EMAIL DRIVER PLACEMENT WHEN YOU BOOK A DRIVER FOR THIS ACCOUNT</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Key Facts<br>* Regional, Home Weekly for 34 Resets<br>* No Touch Freight<br>* $1100 Weekly True Up if all requirements are met<br>* Consistent Routes<br><br>Key Selling Points<br>* Deliveries start between Midnight and 0600.<br>* Drivers average 1500-1900 miles per week.<br>* Drivers average 3-4 loads per week.<br>* Drivers will service Michaels Store deliveries out of their DC located in Jacksonville FL covering the following states: SC, GA, AL, FL, MS.<br><br>If you live within 75 miles of Jacksonville, FL, you could be the perfect dedicated driver to add to our Dedicated Michaels team! Some of the best parts of being a dedicated driver are getting home weekly, and driving an average of 1500-1900 miles per week. That’s around $1150 every week and up to $60,000 annually. Top earners can make up to $1450 every week and up to $75,000 annually.<br><br>As part of the Michaels dedicated team, you’ll run Dry No-Touch freight to various Michaels Store locations in SC, GA, AL, MS, and FL – all within 550-miles of the Jacksonville distribution center. 100% of freight will be live unloaded at Michaels stores.<br><br>To give you the best possible driving experience, our dedicated staff provides 24/7 availability, including safety support and a U.S. Xpress shop.<br><br>Each driver plays a key role in providing exceptional on time service to our dedicated customer (Expectation is 100% on time Service). Runs will include nights, weekends, and holidays that fall within your workweek. Routes also typically require 2-4 stops per load and 10-hour break behind the 1st delivery store prior to offload.<br><br>But being a dedicated driver is no easy task. So, the way we see it, you deserve vacation time more than anyone. That’s why after a year on the account, you can take a week of paid vacation. After 3 years, you can take 2 weeks of vacation. And after 7 years, 3 weeks.<br><br>• Payscale Based On Verified Experience<br>0 Months $0.46/mi<br>6 Months $0.47/mi<br>12 Months $0.48/mi<br>24 Months $0.49/mi<br>36 Months $0.50/mi<br>48 Months $0.51/mi<br>60 Months $0.52/mi<br>72 Months $0.53/mi<br>84 Months $0.54/mi<br>96 Months $0.55/mi<br>108 Months $0.56/mi<br>120 Months $0.57/mi<br><br>Stop Pay $35.00/stop<br>Load Pay $20.00/Load<br>Weekly Minimum Pay: $1100 (Valid for every stop after the 1st Stop)<br><br>• Tagging<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Michaels (MFL)<br>Sign On Bonus: Y/N]]></description>
