      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED TSC COLONIE NY MIXING CENTER SHUTTLE DRIVER--Need 1 drivers. Must live within 40 miles of Colonie, NY. Must have personal transportation to and from DC daily. PLEASE EMAIL DRIVER PLACEMENT IF YOU BOOK A DRIVER FOR THIS ACCOUNT. </name>
        <description><![CDATA[HOURS:M-F 0800-1700 with opportunity to run Saturday’s for additional bonus<br>HOME NIGHTLY! <br>NO TOUCH! <br>PRELOADED/ DROP AND HOOK<br><br>Starting at Colonie, NY your day will consist of taking empty trailers to either Guilderland Center or Albany NY. From each site you will pick up a specified preloaded trailer then drop and hook in Colonie , NY.  Usually, 5 round trips per day but could be 6. <br><br>Equipment will consist of a USX Day Cab and USX Dry Van Trailers. <br><br>Pay Breakdown <br>Pay per Shuttle 	$50<br>Shuttles per Day MIN 4 = $200<br>Avg Shuttles per day 5 = 250<br>Avg 5 day WW = $1250<br>Avg 6 day WW = $1500<br>Annual Pay 5 day WW $65,000<br>Annual Pay 6 day WW $78,000<br>                                                                                         • Tagging<br>Job: lOCAL Driver<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: LOCAL<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: TSC Colonie]]></description>
