        <name>CLOSED Dana- Drivers must live within 50 miles of Louisville, KY Home Daily.  1 Driver Needed. Please email driver placement when you have one on the schedule. </name>
        <description><![CDATA[• Dana drivers will be taking 4 shuttles from Louisville KY to Jeffersonville IN.<br>• Average weekly pay is $1400 gross<br>• Currently set as live load and live unload. No touch.<br>• The driver will then bring empty return racks back to the plant in Louisville. This is 42 miles round trip. Driver are expected to run 4 round trips per shift.<br>•Shift: Monday-Friday; Start time is 08:00. Last load picks up at 17:30, day typically ends between 19:00-20:00<br>• In the event of production issues or operational issues, the driver may be redirected to help at another dedicated facility (Kroger, Meijer etc.)<br>• Drivers need to live within 50 miles of Louisville KY<br>• Slip seat day cab operation. Driver will need to drive their POV to work everyday                                               <br>• Payscale:<br>Driver pay is $280 per day $1400 per week<br>                                                                                       <br>• Paid vacation is offered: Taken one week at a time and will pay out at a rate based on the driver’s prior 52-week average pay. Drivers will accrue more vacation time based on tenure:<br>• 1 Year Tenure: 1 Week of Vacation<br>• 3 Years Tenure: 2 Weeks of Vacation<br>• 7 Years Tenure: 3 Weeks of Vacation<br>• 15 Years Tenure: 4 Weeks of Vacation<br>                                             <br>• Tagging<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Local<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Dana Dry Ridge]]></description>
