      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED Michaels - 100 miles from Hazelton PA HOME weekly -3 mos experience req- $1300 weekly minimum! 7 drivers needed</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Key Facts<br>•	Regional Freight, Home weekly for 34-hour Resets<br>•	No Touch Freight<br>•	Consistent Routes<br>•	Average Weekly Pay $1400 based on experience<br>•	Top earners can earn up to $100k per year<br>•	City pay bonus for running loads into Long Island<br><br>Key Selling Points<br>•	Drivers average 3-4 routes per week.<br>•	Drivers average 1730 miles per week within the following states: Maine, Vermont, new Hampshire, Massachusetts, New York (No NYC Loads), Pennsylvania, Ohio. <br>•	No deliveries in any of the 5 boroughs of NYC including Long Island, Queens, Brooklyn, and Staten Island.<br>•	Store Deliveries start between midnight and 0600. Trailers consist of 2-4 stops, pending time of year. <br>•	Service Orientated Account – Drivers are expected to follow dispatch times for pick up and deliveries. Drivers are required to take his/her 10-hour break behind stop #1 prior to offload<br>•	Drivers are expected to be available 5.5 days per week, 34-hour rests are done on Saturdays pending customer’s demand but not guaranteed<br>•	No Touch Freight and Drivers must live within 100-mi of DC.<br>•	True Up Pay $1300/week if all account objectives are met<br>If you live within 100 miles of the Hazleton, PA, you could be the perfect dedicated driver to add to our Dedicated Michaels team! Some of the best parts of being a dedicated driver are getting home weekly and driving an average of 1730 miles per week. That’s around $1500 every week and up to $78,000 annually. Top earners can make $100,000 annually. <br>As part of the Michaels dedicated team, you’ll run Dry No-touch Freight to various Michaels store locations as far north as Maine, out to the Indiana/Ohio line, and no further south than as far south as Virginia – all within 600-miles of the Hazleton distribution center. 100% of freight will be live unload at the Michaels stores.<br>To give you the best possible driving experience, our dedicated staff provides 24/7 availability, including safety support and a U.S. Xpress shop.<br>Each driver plays a key role in providing exceptional on time service to our dedicated customer (Expectation is 100% on time Service). Runs will include nights, weekends, and holidays that fall within your workweek. Routes also typically require 1-4 stops per load and 10-hour break behind the 1st delivery store prior to offload.<br>But being a dedicated driver is no easy task. So, the way we see it, you deserve vacation time more than anyone. That’s why after a year on the account, you can take a week of paid vacation. After 3 years, you can take 2 weeks of vacation. And after 7 years, 3 weeks.<br><br>Pay Scale – Based on Verifiable Experience –<br>•	0 Months - $0.54/mi<br>•	6 Months - $0.55/mi<br>•	12 Months - $0.56/mi<br>•	24 Months - $0.57/mi<br>•	36 Months - $0.58/mi<br>•	48 Months - $0.59/mi<br>•	60 Months - $0.60/mi<br>•	72 Months - $0.62/mi<br>•	84 Months - $0.64/mi<br>•	96 Months - $0.66/mi<br>•	108 Months - $0.68/mi<br>•	120 Months - $0.70/mi<br><br>Stop Pay $35.00/stop (Valid for every stop after the 1st Stop)<br>Load Pay $50.00/load<br>Weekly True Up Pay: $1300<br>Vacation Pay – Company Standards<br>•	1 year = 1 week<br>•	3 years = 2 weeks<br>•	7 years = 3 weeks<br>•	15 years = 4 weeks<br><br>• Tagging<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Michaels Hazleton PA<br>SIGN ON BONUS: Y/N]]></description>
