      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED Whirlpool - 50 miles McDonough  GA Drivers . HOME WEEKLY! $1100 true up!! Need 10 drivers! </name>
        <description><![CDATA[Account key selling points<br>• Drivers can earn a true up of $1100 per week if available for full week.<br>• Night Driving Required. Drivers will usually pick up after 6 pm to 4 am and deliver straight through for AM deliveries.<br>• . Drivers on this account are home weekly<br>• Drivers haul finished appliances from GA to distribution centers in AL,TN ,NC, FL, GA, OH, <br><br>Additional account details<br>• Drivers average 2000 MPW.<br>• About 10% of the freight is touch freight. They must tailgate at the delivery. They use a pallet jack to pull to the end of the trailer and the customer takes off the freight.<br>• All runs are round trip average 5 loads per week based on customer volume. <br><br><br>• Payscale Based On Verified Experience<br>0- 6 $0.46<br>7 -12 $0.47<br>12- 23 $0.48<br>24- 35 $0.49<br>36- 47 $0.50<br>48- 60 $0.51<br>61- 72 $0.52<br>73- 84 $0.53<br>85- 96 $0.54<br>97+ $0.55<br><br>True-up $1,100<br>Backhaul $20<br><br><br>• TAGGING<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Whirlpool GA]]></description>
