      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED Kroger Shelbyville IN LEASE- Local account 60 miles of Shelbyville </name>
        <description><![CDATA[*Driver will work weekends and nights* <br>*Freight will need to be unloaded from trailer into back room of stores using power jack. *<br>*Kroger is a 24/7 operation and drivers will operate on various schedules and start days.*<br>*2000-2500 miles per week* <br>*Drivers are home weekly *<br>*This account delivers dry and refrigerated groceries to Kroger stores in OH, IN & IL, and will support other sites in the region as needed *<br>* What is the average length of workday?<br>10-12 hours are the average but always be prepared to use you full 14.<br>* Is it piece by piece unload?<br>No, all freight is palletized and unloaded by motorized pallet jack.<br><br>As part of the Kroger dedicated team, you’ll run dry and refrigerated TOUCH freight to various Kroger locations in OH, IN & IL. 100% of freight will be driver unload with pallet jacks at Kroger stores.<br>Runs will include nights, weekends, and holidays that fall within your workweek. Routes also typically require 2-5 stops per route, with possibly running multiple routes per day.<br><br>$1.29 per mile<br>$25 per stop<br>Fuel on site at Kroger]]></description>
