      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED CH Robinson Tour-$1000 Per Week Weekly Minimum!! 3 months Exp. 3 Drivers Per Week! </name>
        <description><![CDATA[Key Facts<br>18 days out, 3 days home<br>Run locations: 48 contiguous states	<br>$1000 Weekly True Up<br>	Average weekly pay $1100-$1200                                                                                                                                       <br>Key Selling Points<br>Great home time <br>Tenured staff to support you<br>No Touch Freight<br>Competitive Mileage Pay<br><br><br>If you live within our hiring area, you could be the perfect dedicated driver to add to our CH Robinson Tour team! Some of the best parts of being a dedicated driver are getting home 3 days after 18 days out and driving an average of 2200-2400 miles per week. That is around $1100-$1200 every week and up to 55k-81k annually. This fleet pays a weekly true up of $1000 per week.<br><br>As part of the CH Robinson dedicated team, you’ll run dry no touch freight within the contiguous 48 states. Deliveries are no touch live unloaded at our customer destinations<br><br>To give you the best possible driving experience, the CHR Robinson operational team includes 24/7 coverage. Success depends on teamwork and communication. Service to the customer with on time delivery of each load is of the utmost importance.<br><br>Being a dedicated driver is no easy task. So, the way we see it, you deserve vacation time more than anyone. That’s why after a year with US Xpress, you can take a week of paid vacation. After 3 years, you can take 2 weeks of vacation. And after 7 years, 3 weeks.<br><br>If you choose to join the team, you’ll go through a short orientation to help get you started on the right foot. And you’ll get paid to do it. After orientation you will have an onboarding call with your fleet manager to include all account specific info.<br><br>Does this sound like something you’d be interested in?<br><br>Pay breakdown<br><br>• PayScale<br><br>0 Months 0.54<br>12 Months 0.56<br>24 Months 0.58<br>36 Months 0.60<br>48 Months 0.62<br>60 Months 0.64<br>72 Months 0.66<br>84 Months 0.68<br>96 Months 0.70<br>108 Months 0.72<br>120+ Months 0.74<br><br>• Tagging<br>Job: Dedicated OTR DRIVER DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: OTR<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: CH Robinson <br>SIGN ON BONUS: Y/N]]></description>
