      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED COMPANY OTR TAG TEAM</name>
        <description><![CDATA[CHECK OUT OUR BRAND-NEW TAG TEAM PROGRAM <br>https://tinyurl.com/7j2c3j3r                                          Teams Can Earn $150,000+ Every Year!<br>Earn up to .80 CPM<br>Starting CPM + High Mileage Incentive Pay = Average Annual Salary<br>If a Team comes in that has 1 year verifiable experience driving together, they will be eligible for the $30,000!<br><br><br>Benefits:<br>● Avg. 5,000 miles weekly or more<br>● Always drive the newest trucks 2018-2020<br>● Top Shop Priority<br>● Teams get top priority on all loads<br>● Mileage incentive up to an additional 14 CPM<br>● Scheduled and/or designated routes available<br>● Hazmat Teams earn $150 Extra per Hazmat load<br><br>● Dental, vision & 401K match<br>● Full Ride college tuition program<br>● Stock purchase plan<br>● Paid orientation<br>● 1,250 watt inverter in every U.S. Xpress Truck<br>You are also eligible for tuition reimbursement X faster up to $7,000 for being part of the Team Max fleet. Teams specialize in expedited freight and haul some of the highest profiled freight in the company, customers such as Fed Ex, Amazon and L- Brands. Team Freight is -80 % + drop and hook.<br><br>If you need a Team Partner, you can use our Max Match. We’ll help you find the best team driving partner for you. We’ll compare your personal driving preferences for all the other drivers in our growing database. Using this criteria, we narrow the list down to help you find the perfect teammate.<br><br><br>Click the link below for the full Pay Scale:<br>https://goo.gl/yeHzN9   <br><br>If a Team Driver/ Team comes in under a year (or that needs to be matched), they are eligible for the $12k split Sign on bonus.<br>$12K payout:<br>each driver is paid $500 paid after 1st load, $500 paid at 30 days, $1,000 paid out monthly for 5 months<br><br>If a Team comes in that has 1 year verifiable experience driving together, they will be eligible for the $30,000 Sign on Bonus<br>• All Pre-Made team with 1 year verifiable experience: 30k sign-on bonus split, each team partner bonus installments are listed below:<br><br>• $500 paid after 1st load<br>• $500 paid at 30 days<br>• $2,000 paid at 60 days $3k each @ 2 Months!<br>• $1,500 paid at 150 days<br>• $1,500 paid at 240 days<br>• $1,500 paid at 330 days<br>• $1500 paid at 365 days $9k each @ 1 year!<br>• $1.500 paid at 455 days<br>• $1,500 paid at 545 days<br>• $1,500 paid at 635 days<br>• $1,500 paid at 725 days $15k each @ 2 years!<br><br>•Vacation Package<br>• 1 year = 1 week<br>• 3 years = 2 weeks<br>• 7 years = 3 weeks<br>• 15 years = 4 weeks                                                                                                                                              • Tagging<br>Job: First Seat Driver<br>Solo/Team: Team<br>Area: OTR<br>Acct: All Accounts<br>Region: All<br>Dedicated Domicile: THL<br>Team Partner<br>Team Bonus<br>Pre-made Team]]></description>
