        <name><![CDATA[CLOSED DG Zanesville, OH Mileage Pay $1.20  + FSC •Dedicated 6 MOS EXP REQUIRED ONLY 5 PER WEEK New hire training pay and ride along time ($150 per load and 5 days with driver-deferral offered) Must have 6 months experience in the last 3 years. LP'S DO NOT RECEIVE ORIENTATION PAY.
]]></name>
        <description><![CDATA[Account key selling points <br>• This account operates in OH, KY, WV, PA, and NY.<br>• Drivers will get a full 34 hour reset based on the needs of the customer and delivery days and market<br>• Drivers can expect to average $2,685 per week gross, $140,000 annually and top earners can make $3,140 per week gross. Average weekly take home after expenses is $1900 per week for lease purchase drivers<br><br>Additional account details <br>• Each driver can average 1250 miles per week and expect to pull at 3- 5 loads per week.<br>• Each load is multi stop and can have as many as 6 stops per trailer and is 100% driver touch.<br>• Each trailer is loaded with up to 52 rolltainers and some loose freight on top (mostly lightweight items such as paper goods etc.)<br>• Loaded rolltainers at times can weight up to 1000 / 1400 pounds. Ninety percent of the outbound loads will have a backhaul.<br><br>Operational Support<br>• Industry leading driver training program<br>• Experienced Office Staff<br>• Tight Backing Areas<br>• Experience All Four Seasons<br>• Steady work<br>• Positive work environment<br><br><br><br>Pay breakdown <br>• IC/LP Drivers<br>$1.20 per mile + fuel surcharge<br>$120 unload pay<br>$25 stop pay<br><br><br><br><br>• Tagging<br>IC JOB: First Seat Driver<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: DG Zanesville                                  PST/EFA: Required]]></description>
