        <description><![CDATA[Account key selling points<br><br>• This account operates in PA, NJ, NY, DE, MD, (no NYC).<br>• Drivers can expect to average $3900 per week gross, $202,000+ annually and top earners can make $4760 gross per week<br>• New drivers begin on a Tuesday through Saturday delivery schedule<br>• Drivers can move to a Monday through Friday schedule when those spots become available<br><br>Additional account details<br>• Drivers will average 1100 miles per week pulling a minimum of 3 loads per week.<br>• Drivers may be required to run OTR freight if customer freight is not available. Will run a week at a time out and will keep on normal home time schedule<br>• Each load is multi-stop and can have as many as 4 stops per trailer.<br>• Each trailer averages 4000 pieces total and is 100% touch freight, with the driver manually unloading all freight.<br><br>Operational Support<br>• Industry leading driver training program<br>• Experienced Office Staff<br>• Tight Backing Areas<br>• Experience All Four Seasons<br>• Steady work<br>• Positive work environment<br>• Round trip loads<br><br><br>Pay breakdown<br>• IC/LP Drivers<br>$1.44 per mile + fuel surcharge<br>$300 unload pay<br>$40 backhaul<br><br><br><br>• Tagging<br>IC JOB: First Seat Driver<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: DT BERWICK<br>PST/EFA: Required ]]></description>
