        <description><![CDATA[Account key selling points<br>• Night Driving Required. Drivers will usually pick up after 6 pm to 4 am and deliver straight through for AM deliveries.<br>• Drivers on this account are home weekly<br>• Drivers haul finished appliances from  GA to distribution centers in AL,TN ,NC, FL, GA, OH, PA<br><br>Additional account details<br>• Drivers average 2000 MPW.<br>• About 10% of the freight is touch freight. They must tailgate at the delivery<br>• All runs are round trip average 5 loads per week based upon customer volume                                         <br>Pay Scale<br>$1.12 per mile<br><br>• TAGGING<br>IC Job: First Seat Driver<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Whirlpool GA]]></description>
