      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED Hobby Lobby TEAM - 3 mos exp req - . $12K SOB SPLIT ($6K each driver) or $30K SOB SPLIT ($15K each driver)!! 
</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Account key selling points <br>• If drivers live within 150 miles of the DC in Oklahoma City OK then they can be home weekly for a 34 hour reset.<br>• Drivers that live outside the 150 miles from OKC stay out 4 weeks then they go home- 4 days.<br>• Average $1690 per week gross per driver ( depending on experience ) $88,000 per year<br>• Drivers haul Hobby Lobby freight all over the US<br><br>Additional account details <br>• Home Time request must be sent in 7 days in advance: We will then work with Hobby Lobby to get a load that goes to the house: (This way they can load it on an EMPTY USX trailer)<br>• NOTE: When Recruiting for Hobby Lobby out of OKC, please refrain from hiring from these carriers as they are also working for Hobby Lobby. (Midcon, Stevens, Western Flyer Express, Hobby Lobby)<br>• Any other locations we recruit out of for this account will be free game, just not out of OKC.<br>• Trailers are preloaded at the shipper and live unload at store/customer locations<br>• Drivers will not be required to touch freight.<br>• Drivers can look to average 4800 -5000+ MPW<br><br>Pay breakdown<br>• Pay Scale based on EACH drivers experience<br>• 3-24 Months .75 split<br>• 25-48 Months .76 split<br>• 49-72 Months .77 split<br>• 73+ months .78 split<br><br>• Extra Pay (Per Driver)<br>Stop 1 $ 10.00<br>Stop 2 $ 17.50<br>Stop 3 $ 25.00<br>• Layover Per Diem $ 50.00<br>• Breakdown Per Diem $50.00<br>• Long Island $ 75.00<br><br>If a Team Driver/ Team comes in under a year (or that needs to be matched), they are eligible for the $12k split Sign on bonus.<br>$12K payout:<br>each driver is paid $500 paid after 1st load, $500 paid at 30 days, $1,000 paid out monthly for 5 months<br>If a Team comes in that has 1 year verifiable experience driving together, they will be eligible for the $30,000 Sign on Bonus<br>• All Pre-Made team with 1 year verifiable experience: 30k sign-on bonus split, each team partner bonus installments are listed below:<br><br>• $500 paid after 1st load<br>• $500 paid at 30 days<br>• $2,000 paid at 60 days $3k each @ 2 Months!<br>• $1,500 paid at 150 days<br>• $1,500 paid at 240 days<br>• $1,500 paid at 330 days<br>• $1500 paid at 365 days $9k each @ 1 year!<br>• $1.500 paid at 455 days<br>• $1,500 paid at 545 days<br>• $1,500 paid at 635 days<br>• $1,500 paid at 725 days $15k each @ 2 years!<br><br>• Tagging<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver DLC<br>Solo/Team: Team<br>Area: OTR<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Hobby Lobby Tour<br>Ded Tour: HOBBY LOBBY OKC                                  Team Partner<br>Team Bonus<br>Pre-made Team<br> ]]></description>
