        <description><![CDATA[Account key selling points<br>• Runs are in the state of Florida from Gainesville south to Sarasota and from the Gulf of Mexico east to and including Orlando<br>• Drivers can expect to earn on average of $2100.00 gross per week or $109,000 annually based on a minimum of 4 loads per week. <br>• Top earning drivers can expect to earn on average $2600 gross per week or $135,000 annually based on a minimum of 5 loads per week<br><br>Additional account details<br>• Each driver can average 900 miles per week and expect to pull at least 4 loads per week.<br>• Each load is multi stop and can have as many as 5 stops per trailer with 3 being the average per trailer<br>• The average piece count per loaded trailer is 4200 but can be as high as 5300<br>• This account is 100% driver touch which means you will be touching every single case on the trailer.<br>• In addition to the mileage pay, the drivers will earn and additional $250 per load inclusive for the unload and $40 for backhauls<br><br>Operational Support<br>• Industry leading driver training program<br>• Experienced Office Staff<br>• Tight Backing Areas<br>• Experience All Four Seasons<br>• Steady work<br>• Positive work environment<br><br><br><br>Pay breakdown<br>• SOLO IC/LP Drivers<br>$1.12 per mile + fuel surcharge<br>$250 unload pay<br>$40 backhaul<br><br><br>• Tagging<br>IC JOB: First Seat Driver<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: Regional<br>DED/DOM Term: Dollar Tree Ocala<br>PST/EFA: Required ]]></description>
