</name>
        <description><![CDATA[• Pay is 0.64 split .32 per mile per driver. average $1500-$1600 a week per driver<br>• $10 per stop<br>• Most of these loads are drop and hook.<br>• Drivers leave Sunday evening-Friday night. Home for Saturday and Sunday until Sunday evening. <br>• Can live within 100 miles of Indianapolis, IN<br>• Weekly miles – 4100<br>• Drivers haul countertops, laminate and other material for building shelving and cabinets<br>                                                                                      If a Team Driver/ Team comes in under a year (or that needs to be matched), they are eligible for the $12k split. <br>$12K payout:<br>each driver is paid $500 paid after 1st load, $500 paid at 30 days, $1,000 paid out monthly for 5 months <br><br> If a Team comes in that has 1 year verifiable experience driving together, they will be eligible for the $30,000 Sign on Bonus <br>• All Pre-Made team with 1 year verifiable experience: 30k sign-on bonus split, each team partner bonus installments are listed below:<br><br>• $500 paid after 1st load<br>• $500 paid at 30 days<br>• $2,000 paid at 60 days $3k each @ 2 Months!<br>• $1,500 paid at 150 days<br>• $1,500 paid at 240 days<br>• $1,500 paid at 330 days<br>• $1500 paid at 365 days $9k each @ 1 year!<br>• $1.500 paid at 455 days<br>• $1,500 paid at 545 days<br>• $1,500 paid at 635 days<br>• $1,500 paid at 725 days $15k each @ 2 years!<br><br>                                        <br>•	Tagging<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Team<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Formica                                           Team Partner<br>Team Bonus<br>Pre-made Team]]></description>
