        <description><![CDATA[Account key selling points <br>• Drivers can expect to average $2,363 per week gross, $123,000 + annually and top earners can make $2,740 gross per week.<br>• Drivers will get a full 34 hour reset based on the needs of the customer.<br>•This account operates in SC, VA, WVA, NC, GA, AL, TN, KY, OH<br>Additional account details <br>• Each driver can average 1,300 miles per week and expect to pull at least 3 loads per week.<br>• Each load is multi stop and can have as many as 6 stops per trailer and loaded with average of 3500 pieces total load and is 100% driver touch unload.<br><br>Operational Support<br>• Industry leading driver training program<br>• Experienced Office Staff<br>• Tight Backing Areas<br>• Experience All Four Seasons<br>• Steady work<br>• Positive work environment<br><br><br><br>Pay breakdown <br>• IC/LP Drivers<br>$1.35 per mile + fuel surcharge<br>$280 unload pay<br>$65 backhaul<br>**NEW** Drivers who deliver 3 Dollar Tree store delivery loads each week are now eligible for a $250 incentive!!!<br><br><br><br>• Tagging<br>IC JOB: First Seat Driver<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: DT Cowpens                                   PST/EFA: Required]]></description>
