        <name>CLOSED Whirlpool Teams -  within 120 miles of McDonough GA - 3 months exp required.   $56,000 per year -  teams home weekly NEED 1 TEAMS  $12K SOB SPLIT ($6K each driver) or $30K SOB SPLIT ($15K each driver)!! </name>
        <description><![CDATA[• Average pay around $1000 per week per driver<br>• Route days are typically Sunday Night to Friday. Can vary due to customer demand.<br>• Whirlpool drivers run from McDonough GA to Points in the Southeast Region and OH.<br>• Drivers leave from McDonough GA to Southeast delivery region or McDonough to Charlotte Metro to Gastonia OH.<br>• Average 4000 miles per week (5- 800 mile round trips)<br><br><br>• PAY SCALE<br>50 CPM $20 load pay/ SPLIT <br><br>• Bonus Payout<br>If a Team Driver/ Team comes in under a year (or that needs to be matched), they are eligible for the $12k split Sign on bonus.<br>$12K payout:<br>each driver is paid $500 paid after 1st load, $500 paid at 30 days, $1,000 paid out monthly for 5 months<br><br>If a Team comes in that has 1 year verifiable experience driving together, they will be eligible for the $30,000 Sign on Bonus<br>• All Pre-Made team with 1 year verifiable experience: 30k sign-on bonus split, each team partner bonus installments are listed below:<br><br>• $500 paid after 1st load<br>• $500 paid at 30 days<br>• $2,000 paid at 60 days $3k each @ 2 Months!<br>• $1,500 paid at 150 days<br>• $1,500 paid at 240 days<br>• $1,500 paid at 330 days<br>• $1500 paid at 365 days $9k each @ 1 year!<br>• $1.500 paid at 455 days<br>• $1,500 paid at 545 days<br>• $1,500 paid at 635 days<br>• $1,500 paid at 725 days $15k each @ 2 y<br><br>     <br><br>•	Tagging<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Team<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Whirlpool Teams" <br>Team Partner<br>Team Bonus<br>Pre-made Team<br>                                     ]]></description>
