        <name>CLOSED Formica SOLO - 50 miles of Cincinnati OH - HOME DAILY. Need 1 driver! Email Driver Placement if you book a driver for this account</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Pay: 20/hr. Plus time and a half for any amount over 40 hours each week.<br>Average hours per week is 50. So an average of 10 hours of overtime per week.<br>Average weekly pay is $1,100<br><br>Schedule: Monday-Friday 0600-1600/1700. Home daily account<br><br>Route: Running material from Cincinnati to Indianapolis and back each day.<br><br>Hiring Radius: Drivers can live within 50 Miles of Indianapolis, IN or Cincinnati, OH. We can make either location work for the account.                                                                                                                 Tagging<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Local<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Formica Indianapolis]]></description>
