      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED UPS TX Team - 75 miles of Dallas - GREAT HOMETIME - $1593 per week per driver. Hazmat Required $12K SOB SPLIT ($6K each driver) or $30K SOB SPLIT ($15K each driver)!! NEED 1TEAM ONLY PLEASE EMAIL DRIVER PLACEMENT WHEN YOU HAVE A TEAM BOOKED </name>
        <description><![CDATA[• Drivers will split .73 CPM or $1593 per week .<br>• Drivers need to live within 75 miles of Dallas TX. Hazmat required!<br>• Every other week, the teams will get nearly 3 full days scheduled off and on the opposite week there is time for a reset in CA after del on Mon (between legs 6 and 7).<br>• Drivers will haul UPS freight Dallas TX to CO and back as well as Dallas, TX to CA and back.<br>• The turn between the delivery in Dallas on leg 4 and the pickup on leg 5 is tight and technically overlaps 20 minutes.<br>• Home time will be Sunday 0745 to Wednesday 0500<br>• Home Time Sun 0745 Wed 0500<br>• 8729 TOTAL WEEKLY MILES<br><br>1) Dallas, TX to Aurora, CO Wed 0500 Wed 2130 (772 miles)<br>2)Aurora, CO to Dallas, TX Thu 0400 Fri 0130 (772 miles)<br>3) Dallas, TX to Aurora, CO Fri 0500 Fri 2130 (772 miles)<br>4) Aurora, CO to Dallas, TX Sun 0400 Sun 2220 (772 miles)<br>5) Dallas, TX to Albuquerque, NM Sun 2200 Mon 0900 (641 miles)<br>6) Albuquerque, NM to Inglewood, CA Mon 0930 Mon 2230 (800 miles can reset between loads)<br>7) Inglewood, CA to Dallas, TX Tue 2300 Thu 0300 (1398 miles)<br>8) Dallas, TX to El Paso, TX Thu 0400 Thu 1500 (615 miles<br>9) El Paso, TX to Inglewood, CA Thu 1600 Fri 0700 (789 miles some downtime between loads)<br>10) Inglewood, CA to Dallas, TX Fri 2230 Sun 0745 (1398 miles Start time off after del in Dallas)<br>      <br>If a Team Driver/ Team comes in under a year (or that needs to be matched), they are eligible for the $12k split Sign on bonus.<br>$12K payout:<br>each driver is paid $500 paid after 1st load, $500 paid at 30 days, $1,000 paid out monthly for 5 months<br><br>If a Team comes in that has 1 year verifiable experience driving together, they will be eligible for the $30,000 Sign on Bonus<br>• All Pre-Made team with 1 year verifiable experience: 30k sign-on bonus split, each team partner bonus installments are listed below:<br><br>• $500 paid after 1st load<br>• $500 paid at 30 days<br>• $2,000 paid at 60 days $3k each @ 2 Months!<br>• $1,500 paid at 150 days<br>• $1,500 paid at 240 days<br>• $1,500 paid at 330 days<br>• $1500 paid at 365 days $9k each @ 1 year!<br>• $1.500 paid at 455 days<br>• $1,500 paid at 545 days<br>• $1,500 paid at 635 days<br>• $1,500 paid at 725 days $15k each @ 2 years!    <br>• Tagging<br>Dvr - Dedicated OTR Driver DLC<br>Solo/Team: Team<br>Area: OTR<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: UPS TX UTX                                    Team Partner<br>Team Bonus<br>Pre-made Team]]></description>
