        <description><![CDATA[Account key selling points <br>• Average weekly pay around $900-$1000 gross per week<br>• Driver will need to live within 40-50 miles of Cleveland, TN<br>• Slip seat—must have personal transportation to get to/from DC<br>• Home Daily<br>• Weekends off<br><br>Additional account details <br>Tullahoma / Smyrna<br>For Monday through Thursday – starting around 1230 -1330, run Cleveland to Tullahoma TN and then back to Cleveland. Then run Cleveland to Smyrna TN and back to Cleveland. <br>For Friday – just run the Cleveland to Smyrna back to Cleveland load.<br><br>Preloaded / drop and hook freight. No touch freight. This comes out to be 2400-2700 miles a week. Home every night and off on Saturday Sunday<br>Pay breakdown <br>Pay- 0.45 cpm<br><br><br><br>• Tagging<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Local<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Whirlpool Cleveland]]></description>
