Can Earn $46k to $71k based on experience. NEED 1 DRIVER. EMAIL DRIVER PLACEMENT WHEN YOU BOOK A DRIVER FOR THIS ACCOUNT

</name>
        <description><![CDATA[DC ADDRESS: 5210 16th Avenue South, Tampa, FL 33619<br><br>Key Facts<br>Need personal transportation to and from DC daily. Slip seat account<br>Drivers will be on a set schedule, paid hourly with overtime, and home daily<br>Key Selling Points<br>*Pay Package for the area is industry-leading*<br>*Tenured staff to support you*<br>*** Home daily***<br><br>FAQ<br>* How hard is the driver unload?<br>No touch freight, drop and hook shuttle runs.<br>* What States do I deliver to<br>FL <br>* When is my home time and 34 hour reset?<br>Home daily and 2 days off.<br>* What shift will I work?<br>6pm-6am nights and weekends<br>* When can I take a Vacation?<br>After one year: 1 year one week, 3 years 2 weeks, 7 years 3 weeks and 15 years 4 weeks.<br>* What kind of truck will I get?<br>Slip seat account <br>* What is a True-Up? How do I qualify for the True-Up? <br>No true up on account<br><br>If you live within 50 miles of TAMPA FL, you could be the perfect dedicated driver to add to our REFRESCO team! Some of the best parts of being a dedicated driver are getting home DAILY, receiving a An hourly rate based on credited experience. That’s around $1,100 every week and up to $58,500 annually. <br><br>As part of the REFRESCO dedicated team, you’ll run DRY TOUCH, NO-TOUCH freight to various REFRESCO locations in FL – all within 15 miles of the REFRESCO distribution center. Drop and hook shuttle deliveries. <br><br>Runs will include nights, weekends, and holidays that fall within your workweek. Your work-day will include 12 hour days 4-5 days per week. Shifts are nights and weekends 6pm-6am with the chance to transfer to days if the opportunity presents itself. There is a lot of in and out of the tractor with doing 15-35 trailer moves per shift.<br><br>But being a dedicated driver is no easy task. So, the way we see it, you deserve vacation time more than anyone. That’s why after a year on the account, you can take a week of paid vacation. After 1 year one week, 3 years 2 weeks, 7 years 3 weeks and 15 years 4 weeks.<br><br><br>Payscale per hour<br>0 months- $18.00<br>12 months- $18.25<br>24 months $18.50<br>36 months $18.75<br>48 months $19.00<br>60 months $19.25<br>72 months- $19.50<br>84 months- $19.75<br>96 months- $20.00<br>108 months- $20.25<br>120 months- $20.50<br><br>Job- Local Driver<br>Solo or Team- Solo<br>Area- Local<br>Region- All<br>Accounts- Dedicated<br>Ded or Dom term- Refresco Tampa<br>Sign on Bonus: Y/N]]></description>
