        <name><![CDATA[CLOSED - M & M Industries- 3 mos exp. Home daily. Must live within 30 miles of Chattanooga, TN. Need 1 driver! EMAIL DRIVER PLACEMENT IF YOU BOOK A DRIVER FOR THIS ACCOUNT.]]></name>
        <description><![CDATA[Key Selling Points<br>Home daily and weekend!<br>Tenured staff to support you<br>No Touch Freight<br>Steady Weekly pay based on availability	<br><br><br>If you live within 30 miles of Chattanooga,TN you could be the perfect dedicated driver to add to our M&M Dedicated team! Some of the best parts of being a dedicated driver are getting home Daily as well as weekends. There will be occasional Saturday work. You will be driving an average of 800-1400 miles per week. This account has daily rate based on availability of $200 per day. That comes out to $1000 weekly pay and $52,000 annual potential while home daily!<br><br>As part of the M&M dedicated team, you’ll run dry no touch freight within the greater Chattanooga/Cleveland TN area. There will be the occasional run to Atlanta. <br><br>To give you the best possible driving experience, the M&M operational team includes 24/7 coverage. Success depends on teamwork and communication. Service to the customer with on time delivery of each load is of the utmost importance.<br><br>Being a dedicated driver is no easy task. So, the way we see it, you deserve vacation time more than anyone. That’s why after a year with USXpress, you can take a week of paid vacation. After 3 years, you can take 2 weeks of vacation. And after 7 years, 3 weeks.<br><br>If you choose to join the team, you’ll go through a short orientation to help get you started on the right foot. And you’ll get paid to do it. After orientation you will have an onboarding call with your fleet manager to include all account specific info.<br><br>Does this sound like something you’d be interested in?<br><br>Pay breakdown<br><br><br>Pay breakdown is as follows: $200 Daily rate based on availability. $1,000 weekly potential.<br><br>**Any days the driver is unavailable i.e. sickness, pto, then a deduction of 1/5th of their base salary will be deducted for each day not available<br><br>• Tagging<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Local<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: M & M Industries<br>SIGN ON BONUS: Y/N]]></description>
