      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED!! Builders First. Home Daily. Night Driving. Must live within 25 miles of Houston, TX. $6k SOB!! NEED 1 DRIVER ONLY. EMAIL DRIVER PLACEMENT WHEN YOU SCHEDULE A DRIVER FOR THIS ACCOUNT. Parking at shipper if needed</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Key Facts<br>* Night Driving required<br><br>Key Selling Points<br>* Home Daily!<br>* 5 Day Work Week<br>* Preloaded/Drop and hook freight<br>* Tenured staff to support you<br><br>FAQ<br>* How hard is the driver unload?<br>This is a no touch freight account, 100% preloaded at the shipper and 100% drop and hook at the receivers. <br>* What States do I deliver to<br>TX – Carrollton and San Antonio<br>* How much money will I make?<br>Drivers average roughly 2000-2500 miles per week, for an estimated $1050 - $1300 weekly<br>* When is my home time and 34 hour reset?<br>Friday and Saturday nights off weekly<br>* What shift will I work?<br>Freight is ready in the evenings, once you deliver to either San Antonio or Carrollton TX then return back to Houston, you’re done!<br>* When can I take a Vacation?<br>After 1 year you receive 1 week of paid vacation, after 3 years you receive 2 weeks of paid vacation, and after 7 years you receive 3 weeks of paid vacation. <br>* What kind of truck will I get?<br>Our fleet is comprised of Internationals, Freightliners and Kenworths<br><br><br>If you live within 50 miles of Houston, TX you could be the perfect dedicated driver to add to our BFS team! Some of the best parts of being a dedicated driver are getting home daily and running roughly 2000 - 2500 miles per week. That’s around $1050 - $1300 every week and roughly $54,600 - $67,600 annually. <br> <br>As part of the BFS dedicated team, you’ll run Dry, No-Touch freight to two different BFS facilities, either San Antonio or Carrollton TX – all within 260 miles of the Houston distribution center. 100% of freight will be preloaded at the shipper and drop and hook at the BFS receivers.<br><br>To give you the best possible driving experience, U.S. Xpress has a 24/7 support staff available to assist at all times. <br><br>Runs will include nights and holidays that fall within your workweek. Workweek is 5 nights/week beginning Sunday evenings and running nightly thru Thursday evenings.<br><br>But being a dedicated driver is no easy task. So, the way we see it, you deserve vacation time more than anyone. That’s why after a year on the account, you can take a week of paid vacation. After three years, you accrue 2 weeks of vacation, after 7 years you accrue 3 weeks of vacation and after 10 years you accrue 4 weeks of vacation yearly.<br><br>If you choose to join the team, we will pair you with an experienced company driver to get you started off on the right foot and make sure you have the necessary tools for success!<br><br><br>Pay scale<br>0-11 $0.50<br>12-23 $0.51<br>24-35 $0.52<br>36-47 $0.53<br>48-59 $0.54<br>5+ years $0.55<br><br>$6k sign-on bonus -$500 paid after 1st load, $500 paid at 30 days, $1,000 paid out monthly for 5 months<br><br><br>•Tagging<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Local<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED Dom Term: BLDRS 1ST SOURCE HOUSTON]]></description>
