        <name>CLOSED Tractor Supply - Home Daily -3 mos req.  Monday - Friday - NO touch DAYCAB position, must live within 40 miles of Hagerstown MD or Shippensburg, PA </name>
        <description><![CDATA[•	TSC is committed to be the most dependable supplier of basic maintenance products to farm, ranch & rural customer. <br>•	Drivers need to live within 40 miles of Shippensburg PA or Hagerstown MD. <br>•	Drivers will deliver freight from the DC to other stores and also will also be required to haul freight back to the DC from venders. <br>•	Drivers pay is as follows: 1st outbound load pay is $230 Any load after that including Trailer moves is $50. So they could make $230 a day or more<br>•	24/7 operation , Monday - Friday , <br>•	various start times. will be EARLY morning, majority of DC deliveries are 0500/0700 so will require starting early enough to p/u your load and make it to the final delivery on time, load vary in length of haul from 0-200 miles so must be able to plan accordingly. <br>•	3 months exp required. <br>•	Drivers must have their own transportation to and from work." <br><br> Tag as a OTR driver - this is not a dedicated account                                                                              TAGGING:<br>JOB- Local driver LOC <br> SOLO OR TEAM- Solo <br>AREA- local <br>ACCOUNT- all accounts <br>REGION- Northeast <br>DED/DOM TERM- Tractor Supply Hagerstown MD <br>                                                                                    updated 8.13.20]]></description>
