Home weekly. NEED 1 DRIVER. EMAIL DRIVER PLACEMENT WHEN YOU BOOK A DRIVER FOR THIS ACCOUNT.  LP'S DO NOT RECEIVE ORIENTATION PAY.]]></name>
        <description><![CDATA[• Drivers on this account can get home every week for a 34 hour reset and a minimum of once per week if within 60 miles<br>• Runs 2400 miles <br>• Loads are drop and hook<br>• Drivers will be doing outbound deliveries from the DC in Pooler, GA and will be returning with back hauls to DC which will be live loads<br>• Delivers to  AL, FL, VA<br>• Drivers may be required to run OTR freight if customer freight is not available. Will run a week at a time out and will keep on normal home time schedule<br><br>IC Pay Scale<br>$1.15 cpm<br>$100 per backhaul<br><br>Tagging<br>IC Job: First Seat Driver<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Account: Dedicated<br>Area: Regional<br>Dedicated or Domicile Terminal: Ferguson Pooler GA]]></description>
