      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED Shippensburg Recovery - Monday – Friday 8am – 8pm Recovery may require overnight trips. Must have at least 3 mos exp. Must live within 50 miles of Shippensburg, PA. Need 1 DRIVER. Email Driver Placement if you have a driver for this position.</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Shippensburg Recover Position<br>• Northeast OTR Pay + $75 per Day<br>• 10 Hour Day Monday – Friday<br>• Average Miles 1835<br>• Starting Average Pay of $1000 per week (See Pay Scale)<br>o $52,000 per year average<br><br>Job Description<br>• Report to Work 8 am Monday – Friday.<br>• Normal work day is 10 hrs per day recovery may require overnight trips<br>• Recover company equipment from various locations (500 mile Radius) and Return Equipment to Service Center.<br>• May Drive shuttle van around local area and bring drivers to retrieve equipment or on work related errands.<br>• Operate a tractor trailer over the roads, highways and interstates. Obey all traffic laws and drive with caution while operating the motor vehicle.<br>• Immediately report damage or other claim issues that arise to customers or rail yards while on site and then to USX Claims Department. Immediately report any damage to tractors, trailers or third parties to the USX Claims Department.<br>• May Drive shuttle van around local area and bring drivers to retrieve equipment or on work related errands.<br>• Road test vehicles that have been repaired in the shops, or vehicles that may require repair.<br>• May conduct road examinations with student drivers<br>• Must have vision to see clearly during night time hours.<br>• Maintain a clean and neat physical appearance.<br>• Maintain a clean vehicle.<br>• May include other duties as assigned by Management.<br>• May drive equipment to dealer for dealer/warranty repairs<br>• May be asked to help with moving equipment around the yard for maintenance department.<br>Pay Scale<br>Northeast Mileage Rate AVG per Week Average Salary<br>3-6 mths - 0.34 - $ 999 - $ 51,943<br>6-9 mths - 0.38 - $ 1,072 - $ 55,760<br>9-12 mths - 0.39 - $ 1,091 - $ 56,714<br>1-2 yrs - 0.40 - $ 1,109 - $ 57,668<br>2-3 yrs - 0.41 - $ 1,127 - $ 58,622<br>3-4 yrs - 0.42 - $ 1,146 - $ 59,576 <br>$75 PER DAY                                                                           <br> • TAGGING<br>Job: LOCAL DRIVER<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Local<br>Acct: all accounts]]></description>
