        <name>CLOSED - Costco College Park, GA - Drivers must live within 50 miles of College Park, GA. Home weekly for a 34hr reset ! Earn $1100-$1500 per week!! Weekly Minimum $1100 per week!!  Can Earn $47k-$75k based on experience. Need 2 drivers
</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Key Facts<br>* Home Weekly for 34 hour reset<br>* On Time Service a must<br>* Preloaded trailers at shipper, live unload at delivery<br>* $1100 gross weekly minimum if available for  5.5 days with opportunity to earn more<br>* Night driving required<br>* Deliver to locations in GA, FL, AL, TN, NC, SC. <br><br><br>• Drivers on this account can get home for a 34-hour reset<br>• Account runs in Fl, GA, AL, TN, NC, SC <br>•Majority of freight picking up between 2200 to 0600 – require night driving<br>•Trucks will be sleeper trucks and can be taken home for hometime.  <br>• Loads are a mixture of D/H and live unload.<br>• Drivers will be doing outbound deliveries from the DC in College Park, GA on round trip loads – Returns could be brought back, these are based on a schedule. <br>• Drivers may be required to run OTR freight if customer freight as a backhaul from delivery. Doing so results in an extra $100. OTR freight may also be assigned when customer freight is low. This is would be straight mileage pay. <br>• Average miles per week range between 1500-2000<br>• Must be available for the full work week to be approved weekly minimum                                                                         <br>• Payscale Based On Verified Experience<br>Total Experience Pay/Mile Weekly Minimum<br>0 Month $0.58 $1,100.00<br>12 Months $0.59 $1,100.00<br>24 Months $0.60 $1,100.00<br>36 Months $0.61 $1,100.00<br>48 Months $0.62 $1,100.00<br>60 Months $0.63 $1,100.00<br>72 Months $0.64 $1,100.00<br>84 Months $0.66 $1,100.00<br>96 Months $0.68 $1,100.00<br>108 Months $0.70 $1,100.00<br>120 Months $0.72 $1,100.00<br><br>Backhaul: $100 (any third party loads)<br><br><br>Vacation:<br>1 year – 1 week off paid at the minimum<br>3 years- 2 Weeks off paid at the minimum<br>7 years- 3 weeks off paid at the minimum<br>15 years- 4 weeks off paid at the minimum  <br><br>• Tagging <br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC <br>Solo/Team: Solo <br>Area: Regional <br>Acct: Dedicated <br>Region: All <br>DED/Dom Term: Costco College Park<br>Sign On Bonus: Y/N]]></description>
