        <name><![CDATA[CLOSED BJ'S Jacksonville-Must live within 50 miles of Jacksonville, FL $1200 Weekly True Up]]></name>
        <description><![CDATA[If you live within 50 miles of Florida, you could be the perfect dedicated driver to add to our BJs team! Some of the best parts of being a dedicated BJs driver are getting home daily or weekly, depending on where you live, driving an average of 1900 miles per week. $1200 Weekly True UP<br><br>As part of the BJs dedicated team, you’ll run dry, no touch freight to various BJs locations in Florida – all within 300 miles of the Jacksonville distribution center. 50% of freight will be live unloaded at Bjs stores, the other 50% will be drop/hook.<br><br>To give you the best possible driving experience, the account includes 24/7 office staff, including safety support and a U.S. Xpress shop located in Jacksonville.<br><br>Runs will include nights, weekends, and holidays that fall within your workweek. Routes also typically require 1 stop per day and potentially a 10-hour break on the road each day, a few times per week.<br><br>But being a dedicated driver is no easy task. So, the way we see it, you deserve vacation time more than anyone. That’s why after a year on the account, you can take a week of paid vacation.<br><br>If you choose to join the team, you’ll go through a short orientation to help get you started on the right foot.<br>0 Months .58<br>12 Months .59<br>24 Months .60<br>36 Months .61<br>48 Months .62<br>60 Months .63<br>72 Months .64<br>84 Months .66<br>96 Months .68<br>108 Months .70<br>120 Months .72<br><br>$1200 Weekly True Up<br><br>• Tagging<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: BJS Jacksonville<br>SIGN ON BONUS: Y/N]]></description>
