        <name>CLOSED! Walmart Hammond LP</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GzWgRVtHjGWWmShsMxAhOe5yO5u1it0A8Ce2XkWvDIis9fzAc3Sa_ztUk4nlxUyNBnkNJmn-iJKe8snOL0xRbOPo0B32oD83wLajrcRGo2IiMmer6W9f8ap78cd0-h-aIthmNZB21oIUY7QhW1JEnvJZfGp4h4HJ1TS3pULBrJ6U3wRj5aX702iIq7VNKbVJ81EBdP0e4-bGuvpctIycdVBPB0pYqryQTwzolQWWRNTgJ_f3loqUgyOKEI?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>• Run a mixture of DRY and REFRIGERATED NO-TOUCH grocery freight to various Walmart and Sam’s store locations in LA, TX, MS, AL & FL <br>• 90% of freight will be live unloaded at Walmart stores.<br>• Runs will include nights, weekends, and holidays that fall within your workweek. A typical workday will include 1-3 routes per day, with 1-3 stops each<br>• Walmart is a 24/7 operation, with driving schedules day and night. Primarily night driving<br><br>Pay Info<br>• 1.00 per mile plus fuel surcharge<br>• $22.50 per stop after 1st stop]]></description>
