      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED Campbells McDonough-3 mos exp required. Must live within 100 miles of McDonough, GA. Home Weekly. Need 2 drivers. PLEASE EMAIL DRIVER PLACEMENT IF YOU BOOK A DRIVER FOR THIS ACCOUNT.</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Account key selling points<br>• Drivers average over $1500 per week.<br>• Drivers will haul freight between SC,GA,TN,NC,FL, and AL.<br>• Home weekly for 34 hour rest running Monday - Saturday<br><br>Additional account details<br>• Campbell’s acquired Pepperidge Farms in 1961 which includes product lines such as “Goldfish” snack crackers, “Milano” cookies, Swirl bread and a host of other fresh bakery items.<br>• Driver will be required to hand unload. Could be pallet moves with a pallet jack or box by box unload. <br>• Opportunity to run outside freight and have backhauls is available <br><br><br>• Payscale Based On Verified Experience<br>0 Month	$0.40 <br>12 Months	$0.41 <br>24 Months	$0.42 <br>36 Months	$0.43 <br>48 + Months	$0.45 <br><br>	<br>Stop Pay Current	$45.00 <br>Load Pay	$90.00 <br><br><br><br>• TAGGING<br>Job: DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Campbells Mechanicsburg<br>SIGN ON BONUS: Y/N                                                 PST/EFA: Y]]></description>
