      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED Home Depot Baytown Regional--Home Weekly! Must live within 60 miles of Baytown, TX and have personal transportation to and from the DC. Need 2 drivers! Email Driver Placement if you book a driver for this account.</name>
        <description><![CDATA[If you live within 60 miles of Baytown, TX, you could be the perfect dedicated driver to add to our Home Depot Dedicated team! Some of the best parts of being a dedicated driver are getting home WEEKLY and sometimes during the week, and driving an average of 1600 miles per week. That is a salary of $1211.53 every week and $63k annually.<br><br>As part of the Home Depot Dedicated team, you’ll run a mixture of DRY NO-TOUCH freight to various Home Depot store locations in the San Antonio & Austin areas – all within 375 miles of the Home Depot Baytown distribution center. 90% of freight will be live unloaded at Home Depot stores.<br><br>To give you the best possible driving experience, the distribution center includes on-site daytime staff.<br><br>Runs will include daytime weekdays, Monday through Friday, and holidays that fall within your workweek. A typical workday will include 1-2 routes per day, with 1-2 stops each, and 10-hour breaks on the road.<br><br>But being a dedicated driver is no easy task. So, the way we see it, you deserve vacation time more than anyone. That’s why after a year on the account, you can take a week of paid vacation. After 3 years, you can take 2 weeks of vacation. And after 7 years, 3 weeks.<br><br>If this sounds like a good fit for you & your career, here are a few other operational details.<br>• Drive your personal vehicle to the DC each week. From there you will seat a newer model sleeper truck.<br>• Home Depot is Monday through Friday, however there is opportunity to work surrounding accounts on the weekends for additional pay.<br>• Daily start times are between 3AM – 6AM.<br>• If a long length-of-haul load is not available, you will run 2-3 short loads to make your maximum pay for the day.<br>• Additional days will be paid at a rate of $150 per day.<br>• If a driver does not work one of the 5 scheduled workdays due to absence, $242.31 per day will be deducted from the weekly salary. No salary will be deducted if the driver is available to work but no loads are available<br><br><br>• Tagging<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Account: Dedicated<br>Dedicated or Domicile Terminal: Home Depot Baytown TX]]></description>
