      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED UPS SOLO-75 Miles of Dallas, TX HAZMAT REQUIRED. NEED ONE DRIVER. SALARY OF $1055 PER WEEK! Email Driver Placement if you book a driver for this account. </name>
        <description><![CDATA[• Hazmat Endorsement Required<br>• Salary of $1055 per week<br>• Live load/live unload<br>• Driver alternates between 2 lanes every other week<br>• Lane 1- 1444 miles will get home on Friday and pick up on Monday<br>• Lane 2- 2166 miles will get home on Saturday and pick up on Tuesday<br>• Runs Dallas-Wichita-Dallas<br>• Home weekly<br><br>• Lane Info:<br>Monday schedule is as follows: <br>Pick Monday from dallas 0030 – delivers Monday in Wichita at 0750<br>Pick from Wichita Monday 2000 – delivers in dallas Tuesday 0225<br>Pick Wednesday from dallas 0230 – delivers to Wichita Wednesday 0850<br>Pick Wednesday from Wichita 2000 – delivers to dallas Thursday 0225<br>Pick Friday from dallas 0230 - delivers to Wichita Friday 0850<br>Pick Friday from Wichita 2000 – delivers to dallas Saturday 0225<br><br>Tuesday schedule alternates the picks out of dallas the other driver is off<br>Pick Tuesday from dallas 0230 – delivers to Wichita Tuesday 0850<br>Pick Tuesday from Wichita 2000 - delivers to dallas Wednesday 0225<br>Pick Thursday from dallas 0230 – delivers to Wichita Thursday 0850<br>Pick Thursday from Wichita 2000 - delivers to dallas Friday 0225<br><br><br><br>• Tagging<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: UPS Dallas TX (UTX)]]></description>
