        <name>CLOSED Walmart Gordonsville LEASE</name>
        <description><![CDATA[• Run a mixture of DRY and REFRIGERATED NO-TOUCH grocery freight to various Walmart store locations in MD, PA, WV, NC, & VA – all within 600 miles of the Walmart Gordonsville distribution center.<br>• Walmart is a 24/7 operation, with driving schedules primarily at night and includes weekends<br>• Estimated 2000-2400 miles per week and $1300-$1500 per week take home<br>• We recommend spending at least 12 days out at a time to be profitable<br>• Runs will include nights, weekends, and holidays that fall within your workweek. A typical workday will include 1-3 routes per day, with 1-3 stops each,<br><br>• Payscale:<br>$1.00/mi + $20 stop pay<br>• Walmart-provided fuel.<br><br><br>• Tagging<br>IC JOB: First Seat Driver<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Walmart Gordonsville]]></description>
