      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED Ferguson-Pooler- Drivers must live within 50 miles of Pooler, GA. Home weekly $1100-$1300 Minimum Salary! Can Earn $62K-$80K yearly Salary based on experience NEED 4 COMPANY DRIVERS. EMAIL DRIVER PLACEMENT WHEN YOU SCHEDULE A DRIVER FOR THIS ACCOUNT
</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Key Facts<br>*Not home daily or every weekend*<br><br>Key Selling Points<br>*Pay Package for the area is industry-leading*<br>***Guaranteed paid if available 5.5 days a week***<br>*Tenured staff to support you*<br>*Minimum Home Weekly*<br><br>FAQ<br>* How hard is the driver unload?<br>Drop and hook and random live no touch unloads<br>* What States do I deliver to<br>GA, OH, VA and AL, Coxsackie, NY <br>* How much money will I make?<br>Guaranteed pay if available 5.5 days per week based on experience.<br>* When is my home time and 34 hour reset?<br>95% of the time it will be on the weekend but due to HOS or customer needs it could be any day of the week, we do get you home weekly.<br>* What shift will I work?<br>Varies depending on hours but preferably taking 10hr breaks at night.<br>* When can I take a Vacation?<br>After 1 year you will get 1 weeks vacation and after 3 years, you can take 2 weeks of vacation. And after 7 years, 3 weeks. This totals up to 4 weeks at 15 years!<br>* What kind of truck will I get?<br>Our fleet is comprised of Internationals, Freightliners and Kenworths<br>* What is a True-Up? How do I qualify for the True-Up? <br>Guaranteed pay if available 5.5 days based on experience. <br><br><br>If you live within 50 miles of Pooler GA, you could be the perfect dedicated driver to add to our Ferguson Pooler team! Some of the best parts of being a dedicated driver are getting home WEEKLY. Ferguson Pooler for company drivers is a salaried account where drivers are paid based on credited experience:<br><br><br> You do have to be available 5.5 days to ensure you are paid the minimum. IF unavailable your pay could be deducted.<br><br>As part of the Ferguson Pooler dedicated team, you’ll run DRY, NO TOUCH freight to various Ferguson Pooler locations in GA, AL, VA and OH – all within 800 miles of the Ferguson Pooler distribution center. All dedicated freight from Ferguson Pooler is drop and hook but backhauls are a requirement of the account and can be live no touch unloads or drop and hooks.<br><br>Runs will include nights, weekends, and holidays that fall within your workweek. <br><br>But being a dedicated driver is no easy task. So, the way we see it, you deserve vacation time more than anyone. That’s why after a year on the account, you can take a week of paid vacation. After 1 year, you can take 1 week of vacation. And after 3 years, 3 weeks, 7 years 3 weeks and 15 years 4 weeks.<br><br>Weekly Minimums<br>0-11 months 	$1100<br>12-23 months 	$1125<br>24-35 months 	$1150<br>36-57 months	$1175 <br>48-59 months	$1200<br>60-83 months	$1225<br>84-119 months	$1250<br>120+ months	$1300<br><br> Tagging<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Account: Dedicated                                                    Area: Regional<br>Dedicated or Domicile Terminal: Ferguson Pooler <br>SIGN ON BONUS: Y/N]]></description>
