      <Placemark>
        <name><![CDATA[CLOSED DG Marion, IN LP,  Mileage Pay $1.20 •	Dedicated 6 mos exp req for LP only 5 per week. New hire training pay and ride along time ($150 per load and 5 days with driver-deferral offered) Must have 6 months experience in the last 3 years. LP'S DO NOT RECEIVE ORIENTATION PAY.
]]></name>
        <description><![CDATA[Account key selling points <br>• This account operates in OH, IN, KY, IL, MI, WI and IA<br>• Drivers will get a full 34 hour reset based on the needs of the customer, delivery days, and market.<br>• Drivers can expect to average $3,170 per week gross, $164,800 annually and top earners can make $3,550 per week gross. Average weekly take home after expenses is around $1700 weekly for lease purchase drivers<br><br>Additional account details <br>• Each driver can average 1600 miles per week and expect to pull 3-5 loads per week. <br>• Each load is multi stop and can have as many as 6 stops per trailer and is 100% driver touch. <br>• Each trailer is loaded with up to 52 rolltainers with some loose freight on top (mostly lightweight items such as paper goods etc.) Loaded rolltainers at times can weight up to 1000 / 1400 pounds. Ninety percent of the outbound loads will have a backhaul.<br><br>Operational Support<br>• Industry leading driver training program<br>• Experienced Office Staff<br>• Tight Backing Areas<br>• Experience All Four Seasons<br>• Steady work<br>• Positive work environment<br><br><br><br>Pay breakdown <br>• IC/LP Drivers<br>$1.20 per mile + fuel surcharge<br>$120 unload pay<br>$25 stop pay<br><br><br><br><br>• Tagging<br>IC JOB: First Seat Driver<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: DG Marion                                       PST/EFA: Required]]></description>
