      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED Campbells-Lancaster. 3 MOS EXP Required. NO SOB. ONLY NEED 2 DRIVER. PLEASE EMAIL DRIVER PLACEMENT WHEN YOU SCHEDULE A DRIVER FOR THIS ACCOUNT. Must live within 50 miles of Mechanicsburg, PA or Lancaster, PA</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Account key selling points <br>• Drivers average over $1100 per week.<br>• Drivers will haul freight between NY and PA (no NYC)<br>• Home weekly for 34 hour rest running Sunday through Thursday<br><br>Additional account details <br>• Campbell’s acquired Pepperidge Farms in 1961 which includes product lines such as “Goldfish” snack crackers, “Milano” cookies, Swirl bread and a host of other fresh bakery items.<br>• Drivers will run freight to unmanned warehouses, remove pallets w/ pallet jack and place pallets in appropriate places in warehouse.<br>• This is a 24/7 operation so there will be various start times.<br>• Hand unload<br>• This account offers a paid vacation of 1 week after 1 year, 2 weeks after 2 years, 3 weeks after 7 years and 4 weeks after 10 years.<br><br>• Payscale Based On Verified Experience<br>3 months -11 months .40cpm<br>1 year -2 years .41 cpm<br>2 years – 3 years .42 cpm<br>3 years - 4 years .43 cpm<br>4 years - 5.years 44 cpm<br>5 years+ .45 cpm<br><br><br>Extra Pay<br>Stop Pay $45.00 every stop<br>Load Pay: $90.00<br>Detention starts after 1st hr = $18.00 hr Tagging<br><br>Tagging<br>Site: SHP<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Campbells PA   ]]></description>
