      <Placemark>
        <name><![CDATA[CLOSED Floor & Decor- Pasadena, TX. Drivers must live within 50 miles of Pasadena, TX! - Home at least every other night. The average LOH is over 500 miles. Evening and overnight driving. NEED 2 DRIVERS!!! Email Driver Placement when you book a driver for this fleet. ]]></name>
        <description><![CDATA[Key Facts<br>* Night Driving required<br>* Strict Live Unload appointments<br><br>Key Selling Points<br>* Home Daily!<br>* 5 Day Work Week<br>* Preloaded at the shipper<br>* Tenured staff to support you<br><br>FAQ<br>* How hard is the driver unload?<br>This is a no touch freight account, 100% preloaded at the shipper and 100% Live unloads at receivers<br>* What States do I deliver to<br>TX<br>* How much money will I make?<br>Drivers average roughly 575 miles per day, for an estimated $1400 weekly.<br>* When is my home time and 34 hour reset?<br>Friday and Saturday nights off weekly<br>* What shift will I work?<br>Freight is ready in the evenings, we deliver between 2200 and 0300 to the Dallas area, when you get back to Baytown, you’re done!<br>When can I take a Vacation?<br>* After 1 year you receive 1 week of paid vacation, after 3 years you receive 2 weeks of paid vacation, and after 7 years you receive 3 weeks of paid vacation. <br>* What kind of truck will I get?<br>Our fleet is comprised of Internationals, Freightliners and Kenworths                                                                      <br>If you live within 50 miles of Pasadena, TX you could be the perfect dedicated driver to add to our Floor and Décor team! Some of the best parts of being a dedicated driver are getting home daily and running 2500-2800 miles per week. That’s around $1250 - $1400 every week and roughly $65,000 - $72,000 annually. <br> <br>As part of the Floor and Décor dedicated team, you’ll run Dry, No-Touch freight to various Floor and Décor locations in the Dallas, TX area – all within 310 miles of the Baytown distribution center. 100% of freight will be preloaded at the shipper and live unloaded at the Floor and Décor stores.<br><br>To give you the best possible driving experience, U.S. Xpress has a 24/7 support staff available to assist at all times. <br><br>Runs will include nights and holidays that fall within your workweek. Workweek is 5 nights/week beginning Sunday evenings and running nightly thru Thursday evenings.<br><br>But being a dedicated driver is no easy task. So, the way we see it, you deserve vacation time more than anyone. That’s why after a year on the account, you can take a week of paid vacation. After three years, you accrue 2 weeks of vacation, after 7 years you accrue 3 weeks of vacation and after 10 years you accrue 4 weeks of vacation yearly.<br><br>If you choose to join the team, we will pair you with an experienced company driver to get you started off on the right foot and make sure you have the necessary tools for success!<br><br>Pay Scale:<br>3-12 months - .52<br>13-23 months .53<br>24-35 months .54<br>36-47 months .55<br>48-59 months .56<br>60-71 months .57<br>72-83 months .58<br>84-95 months .59<br>96-105 months .60<br>106 months+ .61 <br><br><br>Tagging<br>Job- Dedicated OTR Driver<br>Solo or team- Solo<br>Area- regional<br>Account- Dedicated<br>Ded or Dom term= Floor & Decor Pasadena <br>SIGN ON BONUS: Y/N]]></description>
