      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED Tractor Supply- 3 mos exp required. 50 miles out of Camp Hill PA -home every weekend! average pay is $1200 per week. need 2 drivers</name>
        <description><![CDATA[• TSC is committed to be the most dependable supplier of basic maintenance products to farm, ranch & rural customer.<br>• Drivers need to live within 50 miles of Camp Hill, PA<br>• Drivers will deliver freight from the DC to other stores and also will also be required to haul freight back to the DC from vendors. will Run in PA, NY, MD, NJ, DE, VA, WV<br>• Drivers pay is as follows: 1st outbound load pay’s $200 Any load after that including Trailer Moves is $30. So they could make $230 a day or more<br>• 24/7 operation Monday thru Friday , drivers are home on weekends. but can work weekends if they want to. In sleeper trucks, can take home truck or leave at Shippensburg terminal. <br>• various start times.<br><br>TAGGING:                                                                      JOB- Local driver                                                        SOLO OR TEAM-  Solo                                                AREA- regional                                                              ACCOUNT- all accounts                                                REGION- Northeast                                                  DED/DOM TERM- Tractor Supply Hagerstown MD                                                                                      7.6.20]]></description>
