      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED Quad Graphics - $1000 weekly minimum! Average gross around $1250 per week! No touch freight!! If outside the hiring area please reach out for approval</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Key Facts<br>*Runs include all shifts day and night*<br>*Out 2 weeks, home 2 days*<br><br><br>Key Selling Points:<br>*Minimum pay of $1000 per week with average pay around $1250 per week*<br>*TANKER ENDORSEMENT REQUIRED – Will have 90 days from start of account to get this if you don’t have it. Tanker endorsement will be reimbursed by USX!*<br>*Runs are east of I35 on this account*<br>*USX Tenured-Driver mentors available*<br><br><br>FAQs:<br>* What is the hometime policy on the account?<br>The Quad hometime policy is out two weeks and home two days, out 3 weeks home 3 days, etc.<br>* How much is true up and how do I qualify for True-Up?<br>True-up is $1,000 per week that pays out over two weeks. In order to qualify for true-up you must be available to work 11 days out of a 14-day period. If you are available for at least 11 days in that period and make less than $2,000 then you will receive true-up.<br>* Why do I need my tanker endorsement?<br>Your tanker endorsement is needed because every now and then you may pull a load of ink. These ink loads are loaded onto a normal USX trailer but because of the amount of ink a tanker endorsement is needed.<br>* What will I be hauling and where will I be delivering?<br>Quad is a paper marketing company so you will be delivering paper, paper pamphlets, and occasionally ink. Quad has plants in WI, IL, WV, GA, and NY. You will be delivering From MN to the northeast in the north and from Atlanta to Dallas in the south. You will be delivering to Quad plants, Post Offices, and occasionally newspapers.<br><br><br>If you live within our hiring area, you could be the perfect dedicated driver to add to our Quadgraphics team! Some of the best parts of being a dedicated driver are getting home biweekly and driving an average of 2200 miles per week. That’s around $1250 every week and up to $65k annually.<br><br>As part of the Quadgraphics dedicated team, you’ll run dry, no-touch freight to various distribution center locations east of the Mississippi river. 100% of freight will be live unloaded.<br><br>Runs will include days, nights, & weekends, and that fall within your workweek.<br><br>But being a dedicated driver is no easy task. So, the way we see it, you deserve vacation time more than anyone. That’s why after a year on the account, you can take a week of paid vacation. After 1 year, you can take 1 week of vacation. And after 3 years, 3 weeks.<br><br><br>0-6 months - .53<br>7-12 months - .54<br>12+ months - .55<br><br><br>• Tagging<br>Job: Dedicated OTR DRIVER DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: OTR<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Quad Graphics<br>Dedicated Tour Acct: Quad Graphics<br>SIGN ON BONUS: Y/N]]></description>
