      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED Walmart New Caney LP</name>
        <description><![CDATA[• Run a mixture of DRY and REFRIGERATED NO-TOUCH grocery freight to various Walmart and Sam’s store locations in TX & LA<br>• 90% of freight will be live unloaded at Walmart stores.<br>• Runs will include nights, weekends, and holidays that fall within your workweek. A typical workday will include 1-3 routes per day, with 1-3 stops each<br>• Walmart is a 24/7 operation, with driving schedules day and night. Primarily night driving<br><br>Pay Info<br>• 1.00 per mile plus fuel surcharge<br>• $22.50 per stop after 1st stop                                $50 load minimum     ]]></description>
