      <Placemark>
        <name><![CDATA[CLOSED Hobby Lobby - LP Hobby Lobby TEAM  - please send DRIVER PLACEMENT an email when you have a team booked for this account. NO NY LP! Must have 6 months experience in the last 3 years. LP'S DO NOT RECEIVE ORIENTATION PAY.]]></name>
        <description><![CDATA[Account key selling points <br>• If drivers live within 150 miles of the DC in Oklahoma City OK then they can be home weekly for a 34 hour reset.<br>• Drivers that live outside 150 will be planned home every other week to do 34 hour reset at home.<br>• Drivers haul Hobby Lobby freight all over the US<br>• As an LP you are able to refuse freight, but Hobby lobby plans the loads that we run for them. These are time sensitive loads. IF we are able to swap to another load we can, but there will be some cases that we will not be able to.<br><br>Additional account details <br>• If extra time off is needed past the 34 hour reset a time off request will need to be entered at minimum of 7 days in advance. We will work with hobby lobby to accommodate those additional days to get the team planned to the house on a USX trailer<br>• Teams average 4800-5000 + MPW<br>• NOTE: When Recruiting for Hobby Lobby out of OKC, please refrain from hiring from these carriers as they are also working for Hobby Lobby. (Midcon, Stevens, Western Flyer Express, Hobby Lobby)<br>• Any other locations we recruit out of for this account will be free game, just not out of OKC.<br>• Trailers are preloaded at the shipper and live unload at store/customer locations<br>• Drivers will not be required to touch freight.<br><br>Pay breakdown <br>• IC/LP Drivers<br><br>Length of Haul Rate Per Mile<br>0-200 $2.00<br>200-400 $1.15<br>401 + $1.00<br><br>•Stop Pay $35<br>•Detention/ layover is 70% of the amount collected for tractor detention or layover compensation upon receipt of same from customer provided that amount not exceed $400 per 24 hr period. IC will not receive any compensation related to trailer detention pay<br><br><br><br>• Tagging<br>ICJob: FSD<br>Solo/Team: Team<br>Area: OTR<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Hobby Lobby Tour<br>Ded Tour: HOBBY LOBBY     ]]></description>
