      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED COMPANY OTR DRIVER</name>
        <description><![CDATA[EXCELLENT OPPORTUNITY<br>Home every other weekend.<br><br>• Average miles per week is anywhere between 2,200-2,500 but if you are available, you can earn more.<br>• Primary running area will be I-35 east, but there could be times when you will run west of I-35 depending on customer and freight requirements<br>• OTR Fleet Manager to Driver Ratio is 30:1<br>• Drive Newer Equipment- average age of our equipment is less than 2 years old<br>• Earn a safe driving bonus .05 with 12 months of safe driving<br>• USX provides a 1250 watt inverter in every truck.<br>• Detention Pay $12.50 per hour after 2nd hour<br>• Layover Pay/Breakdown Pay $50 per day EXCLUDING Sundays<br>• Also, if you a have student loan, you may qualify for tuition reimbursement up to $7,000<br>• You can become a trainer and earn up $110,000<br> <br>•Vacation Package<br>• 1 year = 1 week<br>• 3 years = 2 weeks<br>• 7 years = 3 weeks<br>• 15 years = 4 weeks<br>  <br><br>Click the link below for the payscale:<br>https://goo.gl/NxYYEy                                            <br><br> • Tagging<br>Job: First Seat Driver<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: OTR<br>Acct: All Accounts<br>Region: All<br>Dedicated Domicile- Home Terminal                        SIGN ON BONUS: N <br>                                                                                                                                               ]]></description>
