      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED USX Automotive Services Division need 12 months of experience</name>
        <description><![CDATA[USX Automotive Services Division need 12 months of experience.<br>• 1 yr experience for AP drivers<br>• Must have 6 mo in LP truck before they will be concidered                                                                                                                                                             Hometime - If they live in IL, IN, OH, KY, MI or MO they will be 2 week out and 2 days home. Any other location will be 3 weeks out and 3 days home.<br><br>This Division specializes in expedited freight, particularly the automotive arena. We do work for Ford, GM, Honda, Toyota, Chrysler, Nissan, and Mercedes.<br><br>The Automotive Services Division can run all 48 states but is primarily focused in the eastern part of the country.<br><br>O/O and LP get 67% of the line haul plus 100% of the fuel surcharge paid by the customer. LP and O/O are responsible for tolls/ezpass<br><br>This account is 100% no touch and a large percentage of the hauls are automotive parts.<br><br>This is a top paying account for USX<br><br><br> • Tagging<br>IC Job: First Seat Driver<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: OTR<br>Acct: All Accounts<br>Region: All<br>Dedicated Domicile: Chattanooga Expedited Updated 3.16.21]]></description>
