      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED OTR Teams - Earn UP to .80 cpm! 2 weeks out minimum for 2 days at home. 3 mos Exp Required.   $12 K SOB Split  or $30K SOB SPLIT! </name>
        <description><![CDATA[Teams Can Earn up to $150,000+ Every Year!<br>Earn up to .80 CPM<br>Starting CPM + High Mileage Incentive Pay = Average Annual Salary<br>If a Team comes in that has 1 year verifiable experience driving together, they will be eligible for the $30,000!<br><br>Here are some examples to show you how teams can earn top pay:<br><br>(Scenario 1 Example)<br>Bill and Mary are a husband and wife team with 10 months’ experience. With Straight Pay, they’ll start out at 0.61 CPM. If they only run 5,000 miles per week, that will put them over 20K miles and give them an extra 2 CPM on every mile they run that month. At that rate, they will take home $146,400/split. With Straight Pay, we reward you for the miles you run. It’s just that simple.<br><br><br>(Scenario 2 example)<br>John and Jeff are brothers who have 2 years’ experience. With Straight Pay, their base rate will be 62 CPM. Averaging 5,500 miles per week will put them over 22K miles per month, which will increase their rate to .68 CPM. At that rate, their average take home salary will be $179, 520/split. With Straight Pay, the more miles you run, the more money you’ll make.<br><br>(Scenario 3)<br>CHECK OUT OUR BRAND-NEW TAG TEAM PROGRAM<br>https://tinyurl.com/7j2c3j3r<br><br>Benefits:<br>● Avg. 5,000 miles weekly or more<br>● Always drive the newest trucks 2020-2021<br>● Top Shop Priority<br>● Mileage incentive up to an additional 14 CPM<br>● Scheduled and/or designated routes available<br>● Hazmat Teams earn $150 Extra per Hazmat load<br><br>● Dental, vision & 401K match<br>● Full Ride college tuition program<br>● Stock purchase plan<br>● Paid orientation<br>● 1,250 watt inverter in every U.S. Xpress Truck<br><br>● TRAVEL VOUCHER PROGRAM!!!<br>Don’t have a partner? We can find one, that works best for you, REGARDLESS of where you live.<br>Must live at least 350 miles from your partner<br>Must live within 50 miles of a major airport<br>Will get a $250 bonus on their check the first week of every month for travel purposes for hometime.<br>Drivers will leave truck at one of our terminals, book a flight/rent a car, go home, and do the same to get back to the truck, post hometime.<br>USX can help secure flights/rental cars to save drivers money!! You are also eligible for tuition reimbursement X faster up to $7,000 for being part of the Team Max fleet. Teams specialize in expedited freight and haul some of the highest profiled freight in the company, customers such as Fed Ex, Amazon and L- Brands. Team Freight is -80 % + drop and hook.<br><br>● If you need a Team Partner, you can use our Max Match. We’ll help you find the best team driving partner for you. We’ll compare your personal driving preferences for all the other drivers in our growing database. Using this criteria, we narrow the list down to help you find the perfect teammate.<br><br>● Home time:<br>2 weeks out minimum for 2 days at home. for every week they are out, that accrues 1 day at home - with a max of 7 days off.<br><br>Click the link below for the full Pay Scale:<br>https://tinyurl.com/r283ustv<br><br>If a Team Driver/ Team comes in under a year (or that needs to be matched), they are eligible for the $12k split Sign on bonus.<br>$12K payout:<br>each driver is paid $500 paid after 1st load, $500 paid at 30 days, $1,000 paid out monthly for 5 months<br><br>If a Team comes in that has 1 year verifiable experience driving together, they will be eligible for the $30,000 Sign on Bonus<br>• All Pre-Made team with 1 year verifiable experience: 30k sign-on bonus split, each team partner bonus installments are listed below:<br><br>• $500 paid after 1st load<br>• $500 paid at 30 days<br>• $2,000 paid at 60 days $3k each @ 2 Months!<br>• $1,500 paid at 150 days<br>• $1,500 paid at 240 days<br>• $1,500 paid at 330 days<br>• $1500 paid at 365 days $9k each @ 1 year!<br>• $1.500 paid at 455 days<br>• $1,500 paid at 545 days<br>• $1,500 paid at 635 days<br>• $1,500 paid at 725 days $15k each @ 2 years!<br><br>•Vacation Package<br>• 1 year = 1 week<br>• 3 years = 2 weeks<br>• 7 years = 3 weeks<br>• 15 years = 4 weeks<br><br><br>• Tagging<br>Job: First Seat Driver<br>Solo/Team: Team<br>Area: OTR<br>Acct: All Accounts<br>Region: All<br>Dedicated Domicile: Home Terminal<br>Team Partner<br>Team Bonus<br>Pre-made Team]]></description>
