      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED - Costco Ocala, FL - Drivers must live within 100 miles of Ocala, FL. Home at least TWICE PER WEEK and stay within FL! Earn $1100-$1500 per week!! Weekly minimum of $900 per week! Can Earn $47k-$75k based on experience </name>
        <description><![CDATA[• Drivers on this account can get home for a 34 hour reset and at least twice through the week<br>Tuesday to Sunday – 5.5 day work week<br>Option to move to Monday through Saturday as schedules become available <br>• Trucks will be sleeper trucks and can be taken home for hometime.  <br>• Loads are predominantly drop and hook with periodic live unloads<br>• Drivers will be doing outbound deliveries from the DC in Ocala, FL and will be returning with back hauls to DC which will be live loads<br>• Drivers may be required to run OTR freight if customer freight is not available.<br>• Average miles per week range between 1500-2000<br>• Must be available for the full week of work to weekly minimum    <br><br>We also know drivers want a clean truck that is ready to run. The Road Ready Promise is the program we’re implementing to make sure that happens and we’re excited to offer it to our drivers on our dedicated accounts. Here’s how it works:<br><br>We’re investing in the Road Ready Promise in three ways:<br><br>Our Shops: Trucks will receive a pre-seat 6-point inspection and cleaning before new Dedicated drivers are seated after completing orientation.<br>Road Ready Crew: We have a Road Ready Crew that will clean and inspect trucks at slip seat locations weekly.<br>You: We’re asking slip seat drivers to do their part by making sure their slip seat truck is clean at the end of their shift. We offer free college for company drivers and their children<br><br>With our full ride program, we will pay 100% of the college tuition for two family members at a time, either 2 dependent children or the driver and one dependent.<br>Learn more at usxfullride.com<br>Pay Scale w/ Weekly Minimum<br>Total Experience Pay/Mile Weekly Minimum<br>0 Month $0.58 $900.00<br>12 Months $0.59 $900.00<br>24 Months $0.60 $900.00<br>36 Months $0.61 $900.00<br>48 Months $0.62 $900.00<br>60 Months $0.63 $1,000.00<br>72 Months $0.64 $1,000.00<br>84 Months $0.66 $1,000.00<br>96 Months $0.68 $1,100.00<br>108 Months $0.70 $1,100.00<br>120 Months $0.72 $1,100.00<br><br>Backhaul: $100<br><br><br>Vacation:<br>1 year – 1 week off paid at the minimum<br>2 years- 2 Weeks off paid at the minimum<br>5 years- 3 weeks off paid at the minimum<br>7 years- 4 weeks off paid at the minimum  <br><br> <br> <br>• Tagging <br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC  <br>Solo/Team: Solo <br>Area: Regional <br>Acct: Dedicated <br>Region: All <br>DED/Dom Term: Costco Ocala]]></description>
