      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED-Alder Creek - Boonville NY - Average $1000 per week - Home weekly</name>
        <description><![CDATA[• NO TOUCH freight<br>• Beverages ( water) in the northeast region (NO NYC)<br>• Monday through Friday with options for weekend runs<br>• Driver will run 2-5 loads a week there will be backhauls .<br>• .Delivery locations will vary in the northeast region and could consist of VA, PA, NJ, NY (NO NYC), MD, MA, CT, ME, NH, VT.<br>• Drivers run 400-600 miles a day (2000-3000) on a 5 day week.<br>• Average pay $ 1000 per week <br>• Pay Scale Experience RPM<br>0-6 months $ 0.42<br>7-12 months $ 0.43<br>13-18 months $ 0.44<br>19-24 months $ 0.45<br>2-3 years $ 0.46<br>3-4 years $ 0.47<br>5-7 years $ 0.48<br>7+ years $ 0.49<br><br><br>• Stops $ 25.00<br><br>• Per load $ 50.00<br>• 12.17.19]]></description>
