      <Placemark>
        <name><![CDATA[CLOSED P&G - local account - must live within 60 miles of Shippensburg, PA and have personal transportation to and from the DC daily. New hire drivers pay and training time -$100 per day 1-2 day ride along.  Please email Driver Placement if you book a driver for this account. NEED 1 DRIVER]]></name>
        <description><![CDATA[Key Facts<br>* Local, Home Daily<br>* No Touch Freight<br>* Average Weekly Pay: $1200<br>* Top Earners making up to $1700 per week<br>* Pay Type: Mileage pay with Load pays for each loaded trailer<br>* 0300 start time with Tues/Wed off<br> <br>If you live within 60 miles of Shippensburg, you could be the perfect dedicated driver to add to our P&G Dedicated team! Some of the best parts of being a dedicated driver are getting home Daily and driving an average of 1600 miles per week.<br><br>As part of the P&G dedicated team, you’ll run NO TOUCH freight to various DC’s and Customer locations in PA, NJ, DE, MD, WV, VA, – all within 250 miles of the Shippensburg, PA distribution center. We do a Mixture of Live unload and Drop and hook loads delivering to our customers.<br><br>To give you the best possible driving experience, the P&G Dedicated account includes 24/7 staff, including safety support. Each driver has a designated start time on this Slip seat account. (Reach out to Paul Randolph or Tyler Frederick for available start times)<br><br>Runs will include nights, weekends, and holidays that fall within your workweek. A typical shift could consist of between 1 and 4 loads depending on the length of routes available.<br><br>But being a dedicated driver is no easy task. So, the way we see it, you deserve vacation time more than anyone. That’s why after a year on the account, you can take a week of paid vacation. After 2 years, you can take 2 weeks of vacation. After 7 years, 3 weeks. After 10 years, 4 weeks.<br><br>If you choose to join the team, you’ll go through a short orientation to help get you started on the right foot. And you’ll get paid to do it. You’ll will be paid $100 per day while in orientation. Once hired, you can request 1-2 days of ride-along training at $100 per day subject to driver availability.<br>Pay Breakdown:<br><br>PayScale:<br>0-12 months - .41 cpm<br>1-2 years - .42 cpm<br>2-3 years - .43 cpm<br>3-4 years - .44 cpm<br>4-5 years - .45 cpm<br>5-6 years - .46 cpm<br>6-7 years - .47 cpm<br>7-8 years - .48 cpm<br>8-9 years - .49 cpm<br>9-10 years - .50 cpm<br>10+ years - .51 cpm<br>Live Unload $75<br>Drop & Hook $45<br><br>Tagging:<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Local<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Proctor & Gamble PA]]></description>
