      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name><![CDATA[CLOSED P&G - local account - exp drivers only must live within 50 miles of Tunkhannock, PA New hire drivers pay and training time -$100 per day 1-2 day ride along. $12k SOB!!! ]]></name>
        <description><![CDATA[• Drivers average $1100 per week with a average of 1600 / 1700 mpw.<br>• Drivers need to live within 50 miles of Tunkhannock, PA and must have their own transportation to and from the terminal<br>• Drivers are home daily. Will not have weekends off<br>• Slip Seat account.<br>• Drivers deliver within a 250 mile radius of the DC hauling freight all over the northeast region.<br>• This is a 24/7 operation so there will be various start times.<br>• Driver may be asked to assist in some unloading using a pallet jack and are paid $40 more if asked to. (only happens 20% of the time)<br>• Proctor and Gamble is a company that specialize in beauty products, baby, family and home care.<br>• This account offers a paid vacation of 1 week after 1 year, 2 weeks after 2 years, 3 weeks after 7 years and 4 weeks after 10 years. <br><br>•Payscale<br>0-12 mos = 37 cpm<br>1 year = 38 cpm<br>2 years = 39 cpm<br>3 years = 40 cpm<br>4 years = 41 cpm<br>5 years = 42 cpm<br><br>Live Unload-$70<br>Drop & Hook- $45<br><br>                                                                                           • SOB PAYOUT:<br>1st load- $500<br>30 Days- $500<br>$1000 monthly for 11 months<br>                                                                                      <br>• Tagging<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Local<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: P&G Shippensburg, PA" "Site: SHP<br>10.28.20]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-503-009D57</styleUrl>
