      <Placemark>
        <name>CLOSED DG Zanesville,OH -   Average $100k-$150k per year! Average of $1.10-$1.60 cpm ($0.55-$0.65 mileage + $155 unload + $25 stop) New hire training pay and ride along time ($150 per day and 5 days with driver. $1700 WEEKLY TRUE UP!!!</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Job Description: We are looking for a Dedicated Driver to join our team in Zanesville, OH. As part of the Dollar General Dedicated team, you will be responsible for running DRY/100% TOUCH freight to various Dollar General locations in OH, WV, KY, PA, and Upstate NY. You will be home weekly for a 34-hour reset and can earn an average weekly pay of $1,950 and top weekly pay potential of $2,800.<br><br>Key Selling Points:<br>•	Home weekly for 34-hour reset<br>•	Touch freight with rolltainers and topper freight<br>•	Average weekly pay of $1,950 and top weekly pay potential of $2,800<br>•	$1,700 true up after training if requirements are met<br>•	Pay type: Mileage/Trailer/Stop<br><br>FAQ:<br>1.	What is the average weekly pay for this position?<br>•	The average weekly pay is $1,950.<br>2.	Is there a true up after training?<br>•	Yes, there is a true up of $1,700 after training if requirements are met.<br>3.	What is the pay type for this position?<br>•	The pay type is mileage/trailer/stop.<br>4.	What is the home time for this position?<br>•	You will be home weekly for a 34-hour reset.<br>5.	What kind of freight will I be hauling?<br>•	You will be hauling DRY/TOUCH freight with rolltainers and topper freight.<br>•	https://vimeo.com/646033145/ef84bb525c<br><br>Pay:<br>• Payscale Based On Verified Experience<br><br>0 Months $0.55<br>1 year $0.56<br>2 years $0.57<br>3 years $0.58<br>4 years $0.59<br>5 years $0.60<br>6 years $0.61<br>7 years $0.62<br>8 years $0.63<br>9 years $0.64<br>10 years $0.65<br><br><br>• Unload Pay $155 per outbound trailer (4-6 loads per week)<br>• Stop Pay $25.00<br>• $1700 weekly True Up if requirements are met <br><br><br>• Tagging<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: DG ZANESVILLE, OH<br>PST: Required<br>SIGN ON BONUS: Y/N ]]></description>
