        <description><![CDATA[Key Facts<br>*Delivery locations are to unmanned locations*<br>*Multi stop deliveries*<br>* Pallets are unloaded with a pallet jack and lift gate trailer*<br>*Delivery days are Sun - Wed *<br>*Drivers average $57,200 per year or $1100 per week <br><br><br>Key Selling Points<br>*Weekly Home for 34 *<br>* Delivery days are Sun - Wed *<br>*Tenured staff to support you*<br><br>FAQ<br>* What States do I deliver to<br>KS & MO<br>* How much money will I make?<br>$0.038/mile and $33.00/load incorporated into a weekly minimum pay of $1100/week based on availability and true up SOP<br>* What shift will I work?<br>Days <br><br>* When can I take a Vacation?<br>After 1 year you will get 1 week of vacation and after 2 years, you can take 2 weeks of vacation. And after 7 years, 3 weeks. This totals up to 4 weeks at 10 years!<br><br>* What kind of truck will I get?<br>Our fleet is comprised of Internationals, Freightliners and Kenworths.<br><br><br>Drivers MUST successfully pass company PST test due to driver unload.<br>Payscale<br>38 CPM<br>$33 flat rate per load<br>$1100 true-up per week if availability and service obligations are met                                                                                                                                                <br>Tagging<br>Job: Dedicated OTR Driver - DLC<br>Solo/Team: Solo<br>Area: Regional<br>Acct: Dedicated<br>Region: All<br>DED/Dom Term: Snyder Lance Hanover PA<br>SIGN ON BONUS: Y/N<br>PST:Required]]></description>
